18.18: naaiq teij scvb Kuq Eei xq penj meib Eei, Navq Zunq kiv fovg hxg liud Eei lx'g Ywav xq Zauj Byaaug mcvj zaub zwib penj meib Eei.
18.8: zyruq kxvq Buaj aa-lon, “yia kanb pun meib kruj fovg hxg pun yia Eei ka'naaiq. i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg pun yia Eei Euvb Euvg Zivb Revg ka'naaiq yia Jiu pun meib Zauj meib Eei zeib fun weig zruj meib Bua yetg liud tu'q Eei pwrng.
18.3: ninb Bua xij zu'g ei Jyenq meib Bua Paaiq Eei waag zruj, yaag zruj Dopg liub Eei Euvb Euvg kov. mq paag ninb Bua Zinb maang maiq tuvq nitq fatq sivj ting Eei Jaab sig fai ziab txvb. Riaj ninb Bua Zauj Jyenq meib Bua zu'g taig.
18.32: meib Bua zx'q kaub lovj Jiaj Eei pwrng fovg hxg meib zyrug maiq zu'g weig naaiq teij ka'naaiq Daam haiq Euvg zwid. maiq tuvq zruj pun i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg naaiq teij Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq maaib wij, meib Bua zyrug maiq zu'g taig a'q.’+”
18.21: “i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq ka'naaiq yia Jiu pun le-wi myenb zruj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng, winb ninb Bua yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub fub suj, zruj Eei kov.
18.14: “yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv fuvj tavj pun zyruq Eei pwrng yetg zuvq penj meib Eei mig a'q.
18.23: yavb naaiq mivb, Kuvj le-wi myenb xij zu'g zruj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kov yaag Daam zruj txvg Dopg liub Eei zwid. naaiq se zruj meib Bua txig Jiaj txig yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj yaag maiq maaib ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
18.6: yia kanb kinq meib Bua Eei kxb yrud, le-wi myenb, yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq taaib zruj zivb Eeig pun meib Bua, yaag fuvj pun zyruq weig zruj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kov.
18.2: xij zu'g txb meib Eei kxb yrud Bua, se meib Eei ovb Taaij Eei fivj, le-wi myenb, taaib Zauj meib kapq Jyenq. meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua yem lcvd vcvg waag Eei Dopg liub Ra'Myen fub suj Eei zyavb hog ninb Bua xij zu'g Tevj meib Bua.
18.20: zyruq kxvq Buaj aa-lon, “meib yem i-saa-laa-en teib puv maiq maaib meib Ripg Eei pwrng. yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj yaag maiq maaib meib pun Gxi Eei pwrng. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj yia kanb zruj meib pun Gxi Eei pwrng yaag penj meib Ripg Eei pwrng.
18.24: taauj Rwrnj, i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg pun zyruq zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq ka'naaiq yia Jiu pun le-wi myenb zruj ninb Bua Eei pwrng. weig naaiq yia Zivj taaib kxvq, yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj maiq maaib ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.”
18.28: Navq naaig, yem i-saa-laa-en myenb zipq taaib zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq, meib Bua xij zu'g cvj zx'q Zwrtq zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq pun zyruq.  zyruq Eei pwrng xij zu'g Jiu pun aa-lon sai myenb.
18.7: mq paag Kuvj meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua haib zruj ziab txvb Zauj Bc'g kcvb Dia ka'Euad Eei yetg zuvq kov. yia zx'q sai myenb Eei kov zruj zivb Eeig fuvj pun meib Bua. Zwrtq liud meib Bua, haiq taub taaib fatq, xij zu'g taig.”
18.29: yem Jiu pun meib Bua Eei Euvb Euvg xij zu'g zx'q Zwrtq kaub lovj Jiaj, kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei, weig zruj zyruq Eei pwrng.’
18.19: “i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg pun yia Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq yia Jiu pun meib Zauj meib Eei naamb Erud zruj yetg liud tu'q Eei pwrng. se Navq lovg Rauq yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen lyepg Jiad yetg liud lovg Eei vcvg waag weig meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei zeib fun.”
18.17: “mq paag taaub Txi vovb fai pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb maiq tuvq zua'g weig zu'g penj Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq. xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua Eei Ryaamq fu'q ziab txvb kub vwaaig, zx'q scvb Kuq Eei Mei lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
18.31: zevg Fiag uaq teij, meib Bua Zauj meib Bua Eei pyauq zov myenb yem haaij Eang yaag tu'q Eei. se meib Bua Eei finb Kruq weig meib Bua yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj Eei kov.
18.30: “xij zu'g Buaj le-wi myenb, ‘meib Bua zx'q kaub lovj Jiaj Eei pwrng taaib fovg hxg zyrug funj Navq yem Bx'q Byaub Eei Zyavq fai Eweib a'vung pyruq Eei zxvb Zwrtq taaib Eei nx.
18.27: Navq naaiq fovg hxg se funj Navq yem Bx'q Byaub Zyavq Eei laavb zi'g, yaag Navq yem Eweib a'vung pyruq Eei zxvb Eei uam fovg hxg Eei pwrng.
18.11: “naaiq teij yaag penj meib Bua Eei. i-saa-laa-en myenb Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq penj meib Bua Eei. yia Jiu pun meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua, meib Eei sia'q Bua yetg liud tu'q Eei pwrng. yem meib Bua Eei pyauq zov myenb, ta'faanb Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij Eei myenb, Eang tu'q Eei.
18.5: “meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua xij zu'g liug leid sivj ting Zauj ziab txvb. Navq naaig i-saa-laa-en myenb Zivj maiq zu'g yia cvj nrud a'q.
18.9: txb taaib fovg hxg kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, tovb maiq puaq ziag uaq teij, xij zu'g penj meib Bua Eei pwrng. txb taaib fovg hxg pun yia Eei yetg zuvq Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, maiq kunq ziag Eei laavb zi'g, fai ziag weig fi'q zwid, fai ziag weig fi'q zruj txvg Eei zwid, naaiq teij ka'naaiq se penj meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua Eei pwrng.
18.16: pwavq Laaj xij zu'g zua'g. xij zu'g weig yetg taub Zwrtq yetg luvd faamb zinb Eaanb ziuj sivj ting tivg taaib Eei Niab taaub.
18.4: ninb Bua xij zu'g Zauj meib Bua kapq Jyenq liug leid wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, zruj Dopg liub Eei yetg zuvq kov. yaag maiq tuvq pun ka'Len myenb taaib nitq fatq meib Bua yem Eei txvj.
18.10: xij zu'g yem nxm Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei txvj Eang. Kuvj mJavg txn maaib leid Eang Navq. xij zu'g funj penj Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq.
18.22: yavb naaiq Jiaj, i-saa-laa-en myenb maiq Kub mivb fatq wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub. mivb fatq nx, zyrug zu'g Daam kanb Eei zwid zu'g taig.
18.12: “txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei yetg zuvq taaub Txvj laavb zi'g, tovb kaub lovj Jiaj Eei ka'lanq yrub Zauj kaub lovj Jiaj Eei syavb a'vung tiuq Zauj laavb zi'g, yia Jiu pun meib Bua.
18.15: “txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq, lyemb myenb, lyemb scvb Kuq, ta'faanb taaub Txi penj meib Eei mig a'q. mq paag zwavj myenb Eei taaub taub txn zuvq xij zu'g zua'g. maaib wij Eei scvb Kuq Eei taaub taub txn yaag xij zu'g zua'g.
18.13: ta'faanb uaq nxm teib puv Eei Dau Zwrtq Eei taaub Txvj ka'naaiq, myenb txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq zyrug penj meib Eei. yem meib Eei pyauq zov, ta'faanb Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij Eei myenb nx, Eang tu'q Eei.
18.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj aa-lon, “meib Zauj meib Eei txn Bua, cvj Zauj meib Bua Jwavg le-wi fivj Eei myenb yetg zuvq xij zu'g Daam paamd sivj ting Eei zwid. meib kanb Zauj meib Eei txn Bua xij zu'g Daam paamd sai myenb Eei kov Eei zwid.
18.26: “xij zu'g kxvq Buaj le-wi myenb, ‘i-saa-laa-en myenb fovg hxg zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq ka'naaiq yia Jiu pun meib Bua weib meib Bua Ripg Eei pwrng. meib Bua zipq taaib meib Bua yaag xij zu'g yem naaiq teij zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq zx'q Zwrtq zyepg kruq Eei yetg kruq fovg hxg pun zyruq.

8.18: yia yaag kinq le-wi myenb tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj txnb la'kauq.
8.8: xij zu'g pun ninb Bua txb taub vovb kruq txn Zauj ziag Eei laavb zi'g yetg Fiag ziag, se lovg Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq yrub. meib xij zu'g cvj kanb lovg taub vovb kruq txn ziag fi'q zwid.
8.3: aa-lon zyrug Navq naaiq nx zruj. ninb zx'q tavb zaanq an Jyenq tavb Jaaj pun ziuj Ra'Myen mcvj, Navq zyruq Paaiq mo-se nx.
8.21: le-wi myenb zyrug saaj kanb Zivb Revg, cvj Roj Revg lwib hruj. aa-lon zyrug fuvj pun zyruq Navq penj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. aa-lon yaag Tevj ninb Bua fi'q zwid, saaj wij.
8.14: Navq naaiq nx zruj liud, meib pun le-wi myenb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib zyrug penj yia Eei mig a'q.
8.6: “xij zu'g pun Gxi le-wi myenb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq taaib yaag Tevj ninb Bua saaj wij.
8.2: “xij zu'g Buaj aa-lon, ‘zx'q uaq teij siag nxm tavb zaanq an Jyenq tavb Jaaj Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g pun tav ziuj Fav tavb Jaaj Eei Ra'Myen mcvj.’+”
8.20: mo-se, aa-lon Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb zyrug ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se Eei waag txb le-wi myenb ei Jyenq zruj Revg.
8.24: “naaiq teij Jauq kxvq le-wi myenb. yem Eig zyepg Mmd Havj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj kov.
8.7: xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx Tevj saaj wij. xij zu'g lovg saaj wij Eei uam fu'q ninb Bua, cvj pun ninb Bua Teij Revg zyavb sin, Roj Revg ninb Bua Eei lwib hruj, zyrug pun ninb Bua kanb Zivb Revg.
8.19: yia yaag zx'q le-wi myenb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib fuvj pun aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua txvj i-saa-laa-en myenb yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj kov. ninb Bua yaag Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb saaj wij weig pun i-saa-laa-en myenb mivb nitq fatq sivj ting uaq zang maiq zu'g tomb ze'g naang hxig.”
8.17: i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj txnb la'kauq, lyemb yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Eei taaub taub txn, yia kinq taaib penj yia Eei mig a'q. yem i-yipq teib puv yia taij yetg zuvq txnb la'kauq uaq Nxi, yia kinq Zwrtq penj yia Eei mig a'q.
8.11: aa-lon yaag xij zu'g zx'q le-wi myenb fuvj pun zyruq weig zruj i-saa-laa-en myenb Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. Navq naaiq zruj liud, ninb Bua zyrug haib zruj kov fub suj zyruq.
8.9: xij zu'g txb le-wi myenb taaib yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei Ra'Myen mcvj, cvj heug i-saa-laa-en Eei yetg zuvq myenb taaib zunq.
8.16: naaiq teij myenb yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib fuvj pun yia, penj Revg yia Eei myenb tiq txnb la'kauq, tovb i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei yetg zuvq msia'q txn yuvd Eei taaub taub txn.
8.4: naaiq nxm tav Navq naaiq nx zruj taaib. zyavb nxm tav lovg Jyem taaq taaib yem ka'Diaq tavb Tx'q Tauj kub vwaaig Eei pyavb. ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei Euvg zeiq zruj zyavj Revg.
8.10: txb le-wi myenb taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq zang, i-saa-laa-en myenb xij zu'g lovg puad maan Jyenq ninb Bua.
8.22: Ga'haaq le-wi myenb yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj ninb Bua Eei kov yem aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Eei puab Diaq. ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se, ninb Bua txb le-wi myenb ei Jyenq zruj Revg.
8.12: “le-wi myenb txb puad maan Jyenq naaiq teij i taub vovb kruq txn Eei mGxvq liud, xij zu'g lovg taub ziag pun zyruq weig fi'q zwid. cvj lovg taub puaq ziag weig saaj le-wi myenb Eei wij.
8.15: “meib Tevj le-wi myenb saaj wij cvj zx'q ninb Bua Zunq kiv fovg hxg liud, ninb Bua xij zu'g taaib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj ninb Bua Eei kov a'q.
8.13: xij zu'g pun le-wi myenb sruq Jyenq aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Eei Ra'Myen, zyrug zx'q ninb Bua fuvj pun zyruq, Navq zruj Zunq kiv fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq nx.
8.26: ninb Bua haib Tevj ninb Bua Eei kxb yrud yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj kov mq paag maiq zeid ninb Bua kanb zruj Revg. meib xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx Paaiq le-wi myenb zruj kov.”
8.25: Havb Jeiq pwavq Mmd zyepg Havj uaq teij, xij zu'g tivb ninb Bua Eei pwrng kov, maiq zruj a'q.

33.18: yem haa-se-lotq swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem litq-maa.
33.45: yem i-ye-aa-Baa-lim swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Di-Bon-kaatg.
33.3: zib Laaj, zyepg Mmd uaq Nxi, tovb siaj mcvg zipq Ga'haaq uaq Nxi, i-saa-laa-en myenb yem laa-maa-setg txv Jyenq i-yipq myenb puvj laavg Eei Zwrtq Jauq mivb.
33.43: yem pu-non swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem o-Botg.
33.50: yem mo-apg Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib Len, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang, zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se,
33.14: yem aa-lutq swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem le-fi-Dim. yem uaq maiq maaib uam pun pc'g fivj hopq.
33.48: yem aa-Baa-lim Bov swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem mo-apg Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib Len, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang.
33.34: yem yotq-Baa-Taa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem apg-lo-naa.
33.2: ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag, mo-se fiaq Jyenq yetg Kav Jiaj yetg Kav Navq naaiq.
33.36: yem e-si-on-ke-Be swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem sin teib puvb Waav, se Kaa-Detg uaq.
33.35: yem apg-lo-naa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem e-si-on-ke-Be.
33.24: yem se-fe Bov swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem haa-laa-Daa.
33.7: ninb Bua Zwrtq e-Taam, taauj sin Rwrnj Tauj pi-haa-hi-lotq, yem Baa-an-se-fon tov puv mcvj, cvj lyepg Zyavq yem mikq-Don uaq.
33.17: yem Kipg-lotq-hatg-taa-aa-waa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem haa-se-lotq.
33.49: ninb Bua Zxv Dopg liub zweib Jx-Dcn Daaib Len yem Betg-ye-si-motq mivb Tauj aa-Ben-sitq-Tim.
33.11: yem Kxib si'q Len swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem sinj teib puvb Waav.
33.33: yem ho-hakq-kitg-kaatg swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem yotq-Baa-Taa.
33.16: yem si-naai teib puvb Waav swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Kipg-lotq-hatg-taa-aa-waa.
33.40: Kaa-naa-an myenb, aa-laatq zivb Eei huvb, tovb yem ne-kepg uaq nxm txvj, haid kxvq i-saa-laa-en myenb Tauj a'q.
33.37: yem Kaa-Detg swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem ho-aa Bov, e-Dom teig Eei kapg Jaaij.
33.4: uaq zang i-yipq myenb tev Jyenq pyopq ninb Bua Eei zwavj txnb la'kauq. naaiq se zyruq yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj taij uaq teij, weig zu'g zyruq tivg ninb Bua Eei zyenb Eei zwid.
33.51: xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, “meib Bua Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv uaq zang,
33.12: yem sinj teib puvb Waav swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Do-faa-Kaa.
33.46: yem Di-Bon-kaatg swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem an-mon-Dipg-laa-Taa-im.
33.13: yem Do-faa-Kaa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem aa-lutq.
33.26: yem makq-he-lotq swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Taa-hatg.
33.28: yem Te-laa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem mitq-Kaa.
33.54: xij zu'g ziuj meib Bua Eei fivj tivg mcvg mavg, zx'q Dau Paaiq pun Gxi. haiq fivj Zamq, xij zu'g Paaiq pun ninb Bua Ripg Javq. haiq fivj zo'g, pun ninb Bua Ripg kaub hepg. haiq taub Dxtq zu'g haiq teij Dau, uaq taub xij zu'g lovg uaq teij. xij zu'g ziuj meib Bua ovb Taaij Eei fivj Paaiq.
33.8: ninb Bua Zwrtq pi-haa-hi-lotq yavb Kxiq Bu'Dovj Jiaj Tauj teib puvb Waav, yavb e-Taam teib puvb Waav pua Nxi Eei Jauq, cvj lyepg Zyavq yem maa-laa.
33.9: ninb Bua Zwrtq maa-laa swiq mivb Tauj e-lim lyepg Zyavq. yem naaig maaib zyepg Eeig nxm uamb zivq Zauj Zyetq zyepg zuvb taau.
33.32: yem Be-ne-yaa-aa-Kan swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem ho-hakq-kitg-kaatg.
33.21: yem lipq-naa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem litq-saaj.
33.23: yem Ke-he-laa-Taa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem se-fe Bov.
33.6: ninb Bua Zwrtq sukg-Kotq cvj swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem teib puvb Waav Eei ka'Len, e-Taam uaq.
33.55: “sij kxvq meib Bua maiq zung pwrnb teig myenb Zwrtq, meib Bua Zxg lyrub Jyenq uaq teij zyrug zruj Fimq yem meib Bua Eei mziv yaag zruj Zeij yem meib Bua Eei la'Eaapq. meib Bua pia'g mivb yem uaq nxm teib puv Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua xij zanb zang la'Eauq meib Bua.
33.44: yem o-Botg swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem i-ye-aa-Baa-lim, mo-apg Eei kapg Jaaij.
33.20: yem lim-mon-pe-letq swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem lipq-naa.
33.5: i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq laa-maa-setg swiq mivb Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq yem sukg-Kotq.
33.56: yia zyrug zruj pun meib Bua Navq yia tivg zruj pun ninb Bua nx.”
33.53: kunq pia'g mivb lovg naaiq nxm teib puv lyepg meib Bua Eei vwaab kxn, weig zu'g yia Jiu pun meib Bua Ripg mig a'q.
33.19: yem litq-maa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem lim-mon-pe-letq.
33.38: aa-lon sai myenb ziuj zyruq Eei waag faauj ho-aa Bov, yem uaq kwei seij mig a'q. naaiq se txij i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Ga'haaq feij zyepg Havj uaq Havj, Mmd Laaj, scvb yetq.
33.31: yem mo-sej-lotq swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Be-ne-yaa-aa-Kan.
33.52: xij zu'g zung yem uaq Eei pwrnb teig myenb Zwrtq Revg, myetg ninb Bua zu'g taaib Eei la'pyeib favj Zauj lovg zxvb toj taaib Eei miub favj. yetg zuvq yem Lav paaij zyenb Eei txvj yaag xij zu'g myetg Revg.
33.27: yem Taa-hatg swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Te-laa.
33.41: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem ho-aa Bov swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem sanj-mo-naa.
33.1: naaiq se i-saa-laa-en myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei kwanb yem mo-se Zauj aa-lon Eei puab Diaq Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv, yetg Kav Jiaj yetg Kav Eei Jaub lrug.
33.39: aa-lon yem ho-aa Bov kwei seij uaq zang, ninb Eei Havb Jeiq tu'q yetg pc'q Eig zyepg faam Havj.
33.47: yem an-mon-Dipg-laa-Taa-im swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem aa-Baa-lim Bov, nitq ne-Bo Bov.
33.10: yem e-lim swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Kxib si'q Len.
33.25: yem haa-laa-Daa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem makq-he-lotq.
33.22: yem litq-saaj swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem Ke-he-laa-Taa.
33.42: yem sanj-mo-naa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem pu-non.
33.15: yem le-fi-Dim swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem si-naai teib puvb Waav.
33.29: yem mitq-Kaa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem hatq-mo-naa.
33.30: yem hatq-mo-naa swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem mo-sej-lotq.

3.18: ke-son Eei txn ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng maaib lipq-ni Zauj si-me-i myenb.
3.45: “xij zu'g zx'q le-wi myenb fuvj pun yia tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb yuvd Eei yetg zuvq txnb la'kauq, yaag lovg le-wi myenb Eei scvb Kuq tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei scvb Kuq. le-wi myenb xij zu'g penj yia Eei. yia se zyruq.
3.3: naaiq se aa-lon Eei txn Eei Buaj, tovb mo-se lovg yrub xn taaib zruj sai myenb, Paaiq zruj sai myenb Eei kov.
3.43: ziuj faauj Buaj Eei sruj mrug, maaib i waang i Zin Eig pc'q Zyetq zyepg faam taub yetg Laaj faauj mcvj Eei taaub taub txn.
3.50: yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei txnb la'kauq ninb tu'q Duab Jxib Eig zyepg Mmd luvd Eaanb ziuj sivj ting tivg taaib Eei Niab taaub.
3.14: yem si-naai teib puvb Waav, zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se,
3.48: zua'g zevg Fiag naaiq teij myenb Eei Eaanb xij zu'g Jiu pun aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua.”
3.34: yem yetg Laaj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn yetg zuvq maaib Ju'q Zin Eig pc'q taub.
3.2: aa-lon Eei txn Eei Buaj maaib Navq naaiq. txnb Lo heug naa-Dapg yaag maaib aa-Bi-hu, e-le-aa-saa, Zauj i-Taa-maa.
3.36: Paaiq pun me-laa-li myenb zruj Eei kov se xij zu'g kruj Dopg liub Eei Qxv, kuvb kavg Dyavj, tovg, Taapq, Zauj yetg zuvq zruj Qxv Eei ka'naaiq. ta'faanb naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq Qyemj lovg Eei Euvb Euvg se yem ninb Bua liug leid.
3.35: aa-Bi-haa-in Eei txn, suj-li-en, zruj me-laa-li myenb Eei puvb pwrng pyeiq zeiq. ninb Bua xij zu'g Zxv kanb Eei Dopg liub yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei pa'q puv mcvj.
3.24: laa-en Eei txn, e-li- yaa-saapg, zruj ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng pyeiq zeiq.
3.7: ninb Bua xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub weig aa-lon yaag weig zwavj pc'g fivj zruj Dopg liub Eei kov.
3.17: naaiq se le-wi Eei txn Eei Buaj. maaib ke-son, Ko-haatq Zauj me-laa-li.
3.49: mo-se zyrug syru tovb le-wi myenb tiq liud zevg Fiag uaq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zua'g myenb Eaanb.
3.33: me-laa-li Eei puvb pwrng maaib maa-li Zauj mu-si myenb. naaiq se me-laa-li myenb Eei puvb pwrng.
3.16: mo-se zyrug ei Jyenq zyruq Eei waag saauq ninb Bua, Navq zyruq Paaiq ninb zruj nx.
3.40: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “xij zu'g saauq Revg i-saa-laa-en myenb yuvd taaib pwavq Laaj faauj mcvj Eei taaub taub txn. xij zu'g fiaq Jyenq mrud taub Eei Buaj.
3.37: lyemb laatg tovg, tovg Eei Taapq, Bxv Dau Zxv laatg Dia Eei tovg Zauj Laav yaag xij zu'g kruj.
3.4: mq paag yem si-naai teib puvb Waav uaq zang, naa-Dapg Zauj aa-Bi-hu lovg maiq maaib leid lovg Eei trud ziag pun zyruq zyrug zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taig mig a'q. ninb Bua maiq maaib txnb Jweiq. Navq naaig, aa-lon zyavb Jyenq Eei zyavb hog, Kuvj maaib e-le-aa-saa Zauj i-Taa-maa zruj sai myenb Eei kov Navq.
3.51: mo-se zyrug ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag zx'q naaiq teij zua'g myenb Eei Eaanb fuvj pun aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua.
3.12: “yem i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb ka'Euad yia kinq Zwrtq le-wi myenb weig tiq i-saa-laa-en Eei yetg zuvq msia'q txn yuvd Eei taaub taub txn. le-wi myenb penj yia Eei,
3.46: i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei txnb la'kauq kaub Zamq le-wi myenb Eei Eig pc'q Zyetq zyepg faam taub. zevg Fiag naaiq teij, xij zu'g zua'g.
3.13: weig zu'g taub taub txnb la'kauq penj yia Eei. yem i-yipq teib puv yia taij mrud taub txnb la'kauq uaq zang, yia kinq Zwrtq lyemb myenb lyemb scvb Kuq Eei taaub taub txn penj Revg yia Eei. ninb Bua xij zu'g penj yia Eei. yia se zyruq. ”
3.26: weib kxmj Dopg liub Zauj ziab txvb Bc'g laatg Zauj Bc'g laatg kcvb Eei Dia. lyemb Laav cvj Zauj naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq yetg zuvq se ninb Bua xij zu'g liug leid.
3.28: yem yetg Laaj faauj mcvj Eei yetg zuvq mJavg txn maaib Yetg Zin lua'g pc'q taub. Ko-haatq myenb Eei kov se xij zu'g kruj sivj ting.
3.8: ninb Bua xij zu'g kruj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig yaag weig i-saa-laa-en myenb zruj Dopg liub Eei kov.
3.9: xij zu'g zx'q le-wi myenb Jiu pun aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua. yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj se tovb naaiq teij xij zu'g Jiu Revg pun aa-lon.
3.32: maaib aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, zruj le-wi myenb kaub Lo Jiaj Eei pyeiq zeiq yaag kunq kruj sivj ting uaq teij myenb.
3.21: ke-son Eei puvb pwrng se lipq-ni Zauj si-me-i myenb. naaiq se ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng.
3.23: ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng xij zu'g Zxv kanb Eei Dopg liub yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Ga'haaq mcvj, fai puv uaq.
3.6: “xij zu'g txb le-wi fivj taaib Jiu pun aa-lon sai myenb weig Tevj ninb.
3.20: me-laa-li Eei txn ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng penj maa-li Zauj mu-si myenb. naaiq se le-wi fivj ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng.
3.19: Ko-haatq Eei txn ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng maaib am-laam, itg-haa, he-Bo-lon Zauj utg-si-en myenb.
3.38: mo-se Zauj aa-lon Zauj aa-lon Eei txn Bua xij zu'g Zxv kanb Eei Dopg liub yem zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub Eei tov puv mcvj, Ba'Nxi Zwrtq uaq puv, se yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Ra'Myen. ninb Bua xij zu'g weig i-saa-laa-en myenb kruj sivj ting. Zwrtq liud naaiq teij, haiq taub mivb fatq sivj ting, xij zu'g taij taig.
3.31: ninb Bua xij zu'g kruj lcvd vcvg waag faav, tiab, tavb Jaaj, ziab txvb Zauj puaq huv tiab, cvj Zauj yetg zuvq yem sivj ting lovg Eei Jaab sig, lyemb Bc'g kcvb Dia. ta'faanb naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq Qyemj lovg Eei yetg zuvq se yem ninb Bua liug leid Revg.
3.27: Ko-haatq Eei puvb pwrng maaib am-laam, itg-haa, he-Bo-lon Zauj utg-si-en myenb. naaiq se Ko-haatq myenb Eei puvb pwrng.
3.41: meib Bua xij zu'g kinq le-wi myenb pun yia weig tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb yuvd Eei yetg zuvq taaub taub txn. le-wi myenb Eei scvb Kuq yaag xij zu'g lovg tiq i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei yetg zuvq scvb Kuq Fiag Eei taaub Txi txn. yia se zyruq. ”
3.1: naaiq se aa-lon Zauj mo-se Eei ziaj txig myenb, txij mo-se yem si-naai Bov, zyruq Zauj ninb kxvq waag Eei zyavb hog.
3.39: mo-se Zauj aa-lon ei zyruq Paaiq Eei waag saauq le-wi myenb. ziuj puvb pwrng taub taub pwavq Laaj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn yetg zuvq maaib i waang i Zin taub.
3.47: yetg taub xij zu'g Zwrtq yetg luvd faamb zinb Eaanb ziuj sivj ting tivg taaib Eei Niab taaub.
3.10: xij zu'g xn aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua zruj sai myenb Eei kov. Zwrtq liud naaiq teij, maaib haiq taub mivb fatq sivj ting, uaq taub xij zu'g taij taig.”
3.25: yem wig pwavb Dopg liub, ke-son myenb xij zu'g kruj komq Dopg liub ka'Euad uaq yemg Zauj ka'Eiag uaq yemg, cvj kruj komq kub vwaaig Eei Dopq, pia'g wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei Bc'g kcvb Dia,
3.22: yem yetg Laaj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn yetg zuvq maaib siag Zin Mmd pc'q taub.
3.42: mo-se zyrug ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag saauq Revg i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb yuvd Eei taaub taub txn.
3.15: “xij zu'g saauq le-wi myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, ziuj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng. ta'faanb pwavq Laaj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn, xij zu'g saauq Revg.”
3.29: Ko-haatq myenb Eei puvb pwrng xij zu'g Zxv kanb Eei Dopg liub yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei naamb puv mcvj.
3.30: utg-si-en Eei txn, e-li-saa-faan, zruj Ko-haatq myenb Eei puvb pwrng pyeiq zeiq.

32.18: yia Bua maiq Rwrnj pyauq, zuaq Tauj mrud taub i-saa-laa-en myenb tu'q zipq ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
32.8: zinb Daavg yem Kaa-Detg-Baa-nia uaq zang, yia Paaiq meib Bua Eei tia mivb zaab uaq nxm teib puv Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua Navq naaiq nx zruj.
32.33: mo-se zyrug Jiu naaiq teij teib puv pun kaatg fivj Zauj lu-Ben fivj cvj Zauj yo-sepq Eei txn, maa-natq-sej, Eei Daamb fivj. ninb zx'q aa-mo-lai myenb Eei si-honj huvb Eei kua'q, Zauj Baa-saan Eei huvb, okg, Eei kua'q, lyemb uaq nxm teib puv Eei nxmb nxm zivb Zauj weib kxmj Eei teig Jiu pun ninb Bua.
32.9: mivb Tauj etg-Ko hxvd, zaab liud uaq nxm teib puv Rwrnj taaib uaq zang, ninb Bua zruj pun zwavj pc'g fivj Hruq mau, maiq pia'g zyruq Zeij pun Eei teib puv.
32.32: yia Bua xij txb ua'g king yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen pia'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv, mq paag yia Bua tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng se yem naaiq puv Jx-Dcn Daaib.”
32.21: meib Bua yetg zuvq txb ua'g king Eei myenb yaag yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Jiaj Jx-Dcn Daaib zuaq zyruq zung ninb Eei winb wavq Twij Zwrtq,
32.14: “ib zang mavg kaaj! meib Bua Ripg Jyenq meib Bua Eei tia penj kanb paan zwib myenb, xij zruj pun zyruq kaub fatq Qiaj Jiad i-saa-laa-en myenb.
32.23: “mq paag sij kxvq meib Bua maiq ei Jyenq meib Bua lcvd Eei waag zruj, meib Bua zyrug paamd zwid txvg zyruq, yaag weig kanb zruj Eei Dovg haaij zuvq zu'g tivg zwid.
32.6: mo-se tau kaatg fivj Zauj lu-Ben fivj, “xij pun meib Bua Eei kxb yrud Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj mq paag meib Bua kanb Kuvj zweid Jyenq naaiq?
32.34: kaatg fivj cvj Zeij Di-Bon zivb, aa-Taa-lotq, aa-lo-e,
32.2: zyrug mivb Buaj mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj pc'g fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq,
32.36: Betg-nim-laa Zauj Betg-haa-laan, zruj zivb laatg wrnq Eei weib kxmj zivb. ninb Bua cvj zruj yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb Eei laanb.
32.20: mo-se zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “sij kxvq meib Bua za'kevb ei meib Bua Eei waag zruj, yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen txb Jyenq ua'g king Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj,
32.24: kunq Zeij zivb weig meib Bua Eei aub Jweiq yaag zruj laatg wrnj Jyenq meib Bua Eei yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb. mq paag xij zu'g ei Jyenq meib Bua lcvd liud Eei waag zruj.”
32.28: mo-se weig naaiq teij myenb Paaiq waag Buaj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, Zauj fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
32.7: meib Bua weig haiq tiug xij pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Hruq mau zyrug maiq Jiaj uaq vaang pia'g zyruq Zeij pun meib Bua uaq nxm teib puv?
32.29: ninb kxvq, “sij kxvq kaatg fivj Zauj lu-Ben fivj, yetg zuvq mJavg txn, txb Jyenq Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king, Zauj Jyenq meib Bua yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib, uaq nxm teib puv yaag kwei Revg meib Bua, meib Bua xij zu'g zx'q ki-le-aatg teig zruj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
32.19: yia Bua maiq Zauj ninb Bua yem uaq puv Jx-Dcn Daaib Ripg haiq Euvg weig zu'g yia Bua tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng se yem naaiq puv Jx-Dcn Daaib tov puv mcvj.”
32.17: yia Bua kanb c'q, xij txb Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king mivb Daavg i-saa-laa-en myenb, zuaq ninb Bua yetg zuvq Tauj ninb Bua Eei txvj. mq paag yia Bua Eei aub Jweiq xij zu'g yem naaiq weib wrnq Eei zivb weig Buvb naaiq nxm teib puv Eei myenb.
32.38: yaag kanb Zeij Jiad ne-Bo Zauj Baa-an-me-on, (naaiq teij Buaj Ga'haaq Tiuq mig a'q), Zauj sipg-maa. ninb Bua cvj weig ninb Bua lyepg taaib Eei zivb Zwrtq Buaj.
32.31: kaatg Zauj lu-Ben myenb tau, “zyruq Tinb huvb Navq haiq nx Buaj yia Bua, meib Eei pru, yia Bua zyrug Navq uaq nx zruj.
32.30: mq paag sij kxvq ninb Bua maiq txb ua'g king Zauj Jyenq meib Bua Jiaj uaq vaang, ninb Bua tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng xij zu'g Zauj meib Bua yem Kaa-naa-an teig.”
32.27: mq paag yia Bua, meib Eei pru, taub taub mJavg txn, xij txb Jyenq Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Jiaj Daaib Bx'q Jaaj, Navq meib, yia Bua Eei zyruq, kxvq nx.”
32.11: ‘ta'faanb yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq Eei myenb, Havb Jeiq Eig zyepg Havj faauj mcvj Eei mJavg txn, laaij ninb Bua maiq lovg Revg Hruq kan yia, Navq haaij zuvq maiq maaib yetg taub tu'q pwatg yia lcvd vcvg waag pun apg-laa-ham, i-sakg Zauj yaa-Kopq uaq nxm teib puv.
32.5: ninb Bua cvj kxvq, “sij kxvq yia Bua hxpg meib Eei Hruq, Toq pun naaiq nxm teib puv penj yia Bua Eei pwrng. Toq maiq tuvq txb yia Bua Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib yem.”
32.16: ninb Bua zyrug mivb fatq teij mo-se yaag kxvq, “yia Bua xij yem naaiq zruj laatg weib yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb, yaag Zeij zivb laatg weig peu Jyenq yia Bua Eei aub Jweiq.
32.40: mo-se zyrug zx'q ki-le-aatg teig pun maa-natq-sej Eei zeib fun, maa-Ki-le myenb. ninb Bua zyrug yem uaq nxm teib puv a'q.
32.41: maa-natq-sej Eei zeib fun, Jaa-i, cvj Zaavq ki-le-aatg Eei fiub laavd yaag weig naaiq teij fiub laavd Zwrtq Buaj heug haau-wotq-Jaa-i.
32.12: Kuvj maaib Ke-natq myenb, ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq, Zauj nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, tu'q pwatg, weig zu'g ninb Bua i taub lovg Revg Hruq kan yia.’
32.37: lu-Ben fivj cvj kanb Zeij Jiad hetq-Bon zivb, e-le-aa-le Zauj Ki-li-yaa-Taa-im,
32.39: maa-natq-sej Eei txn, maa-Ki-le, Eei funb fa'q mivb Zaavq ki-le-aatg teib puv, cvj zung Zwrtq yem uaq Eei aa-mo-lai myenb.
32.4: “zyruq Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb Zaavq taaib Eei teib puv maaib aa-Taa-lotq zivb, Di-Bon, yaa-se, nim-laa, hetq-Bon, e-le-aa-le, sej-Baam, ne-Bo, Zauj Be-on zivb. se Kub yuvd scvb Kuq haig. yia Bua, meib Eei pru, yaag maaib vovb maaib pa'ki yuvb Zamq haig.”
32.10: tovb uaq Nxi zyruq Qiaj Jiad haig zyrug hruq Jyenq kxvq,
32.22: uaq nxm teib puv yaag kwei Revg zyruq, Ga'haaq meib Bua haib Rwrnj taaib. lcvd pun zyruq Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei waag yaag suv mig a'q. naaiq nxm teib puv yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen penj meib Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.
32.42: no-Baa Zaavq Ke-naatq Zauj weib kxmj Eei laavd, cvj Tevj uaq nxm txvj Zwrtq Buaj nitq ninb kanb Eei Buaj, no-Baa.
32.15: sij kxvq meib Bua Win Gaav, maiq kan ninb, ninb xij pun naaiq teij zwavj myenb cvj zu'g yem teib puvb Waav, yaag laaij meib Bua pun ninb Bua zu'g myetg Revg.”
32.13: zyruq zyrug Qiaj Jiad haig i-saa-laa-en myenb, pun ninb Bua yrub mivb yrub taaib yem uaq teib puvb Waav feij zyepg Havj, zuaq yem ninb Eei Ra'Myen zruj waaig uaq txig myenb yetg zuvq taig Revg.
32.1: lu-Ben fivj Zauj kaatg fivj maaib vovb, maaib pa'ki yuvb Zamq haig. ninb Bua pwatg yaa-se Zauj ki-le-aatg teig Kub yuvd scvb Kuq haig,
32.26: yia Bua Eei aub Jweiq, vovb, yuvb Zauj pa'ki yuvb, xij zu'g yem naaiq ki-le-aatg teig Eei nxmb nxm zivb.
32.25: kaatg fivj Zauj lu-Ben fivj Eei myenb kxvq Buaj mo-se, “yia Bua, meib Eei pru, xij ei Jyenq meib, yia Bua Eei zyruq, Buaj Eei waag zruj.

21.18: se pyeiq zeiq wetq Eei uamb Kwrtq, pc'g fivj Eei Jyen lov Zwrtq taaib Eei, lovg huvb pyaaq Zauj pyaab Byaag lov.” ninb Bua cvj Zwrtq teib puvb Waav mivb Tauj matq-Taa-naa,
21.8: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “xij zu'g zruj tiub naavb to'g an uaq tovg kub vwaaig. ta'faanb zu'g naav Ex'q Eei myenb mavg yem tovg uaq tiub tovb si'q naav, uaq taub zyrug tu'q zyavb Jyenq.”
21.33: Jiaj taaib, i-saa-laa-en myenb Win mivb huvj Jyenq Baa-saan teib puv mivb. Baa-saan Eei okg huvb Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv zyrug Zwrtq taaib Tauj e-Den-i zivb Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj.
21.3: zyruq haid i-saa-laa-en myenb Toq Eei waag zyrug zx'q Kaa-naa-an myenb Jiu pun ninb Bua. ninb Bua zyrug myetg Revg Kaa-naa-an myenb Zauj uaq nxm teib puv Eei zivb yetg zuvq. uaq nxm hxvg ninb Bua yaag Zwrtq Buaj heug “ho-maa.”
21.32: mo-se Paaiq myenb mivb zaab liud yaa-se zivb, Ga'haaq i-saa-laa-en myenb mivb Bx'q, cvj zx'q yaa-se zivb Zauj Wiv Rwrnj Eei fiub laavd yaag zung aa-mo-lai myenb Zwrtq Revg.
21.21: i-saa-laa-en myenb Paaiq myenb mivb Buaj aa-mo-lai myenb Eei huvb, si-honj.
21.35: Navq naaig, i-saa-laa-en myenb taij okg huvb, Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv. yetg taub yaag maiq lyrub. ninb Bua zyrug zx'q ninb Eei teib puv penj ninb Bua Eei pwrng.
21.14: weig naaiq yem zyruq Eei Bx'q Jaaj sru  kxvq, “...su-faa teig Eei waa-hepq zivb, Zauj aan-non Daaib Eei yetg zuvq hxvd,
21.23: mq paag si-honj huvb maiq Kavq pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Jiaj ninb Eei teig. ninb heug ninb Eei zwavj pcv taaib zunq cvj Zwrtq mivb teib puvb Waav Bx'q i-saa-laa-en myenb. ninb Tauj yaa-haatq zyrug Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bx'q Jaaj.
21.6: zyruq zyrug pun naavb to'g yem zwavj pc'g fivj Eei Bu'Dovj. naav Ex'q myenb zyrug maaib i-saa-laa-en myenb taig Zamq haig.
21.34: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb, weig zu'g yia zx'q ninb Zauj ninb Eei zwavj pcv, Zauj ninb Eei teib puv, Jiu yem meib Eei puab Diaq. xij zu'g zruj pun ninb Navq meib Bua zruj pun yem hetq-Bon zivb, uaq taub aa-mo-lai myenb Eei si-honj huvb uaq nx.”
21.2: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Zauj zyruq lcvd Jiad vcvg waag. ninb Bua kxvq, “sij kxvq zyruq zx'q naaiq teij myenb Jiu pun yem yia Bua Eei puab Diaq, yia Bua zyrug myetg Revg ninb Bua Eei zivb a'q.”
21.20: Zwrtq Baa-motq ninb Bua cvj mivb mo-apg teig Eei hxvd, se mavg Fiag teib puvb Waav Eei pitg-kaa Bovb nivq ka'Len.
21.24: mq paag i-saa-laa-en myenb lovg Ru'g Daauq taij ninb, cvj Zaavq ninb Eei teib puv yem aan-non Daaib Tauj yapq-Bxkg Daaib, mq paag Kuvj Zaavq Tauj am-mon myenb Eei kapg Jaaij Len, weig zu'g am-mon myenb Eei kapg Jaaij se wrnq haig.
21.28: maaib trud yem hetq-Bon zivb Zwrtq, trub Byetg yem si-honj Eei zivb Fopg taaib puaq Qwi mo-apg teib puv Eei aan zivb, Zauj Wiv aan-non Daaib keb zxv Eei pc'g fivj.
21.7: pc'g fivj taaib lxd mo-se yaag kxvq, “yia Bua paamd zwid weig zu'g yia Bua vopq zyruq yaag vopq meib. ib zang Toq Tevj tauj kauj Toq zyruq txb naaiq teij naav Zwrtq yia Bua Bu'Dovj mivb.” mo-se zyrug weig ninb Bua tauj kauj.
21.29: o mo-apg myenb aag, meib zu'g Kruq a'q. o zavg Ke-motq Eei myenb aag, meib Bua zu'g myetg aaq lo'b! Ke-motq zyenb pun ninb Eei txn zu'g penj pyauj sig Eei myenb, yaag pun ninb Eei sia'q zu'g Zaavq mivb Jiu pun aa-mo-lai myenb Eei si-honj huvb Zaavq.
21.19: yem matq-Taa-naa mivb Tauj naa-haa-li-en hxvg. yem naa-haa-li-en cvj swiq mivb Tauj Baa-motq.
21.17: uaq zang i-saa-laa-en myenb paauj naaiq tiub Ruv, “uamb Kwrtq aag, pun uam pctq Zwrtq taaib, yia Bua lomb Rxib paauj Ruv hrug.
21.31: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug yem Fiag aa-mo-lai myenb Eei teib puv.
21.30: mq paag yia Bua pun ninb Bua Eei zeib fun zu'g myetg, yem hetq-Bon zivb zu'g myetg Tauj Di-Bon. yia Bua paaig Revg ninb Bua Tauj no-faa, se Tauj me-De-Baa uaq nxm txvj.”
21.27: weig naaiq zog Ruv Eei myenb kxvq, “taaib Tauj hetq-Bon zivb, pun naaiq nxm zivb cvj tu'q lyepg Jiad, pun si-honj huvb Eei tomb zivb cvj Zeij Jiad taaib.
21.11: yem o-Botg ninb Bua Zwrtq Jauq mivb lyepg Dopg liub Zyavq yem i-ye-aa-Baa-lim, se yem teib puvb Waav, mo-apg txib vaang, Win Ba'Nxi Zwrtq uaq puv.
21.5: ninb Bua zyrug vopq Tinb huvb Zauj mo-se, “meib Bua weig haiq tiug txb yia Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv pun yia Bua yem naaiq teib puvb Waav taig? yem naaiq maiq maaib Eang Eei ka'naaiq. maiq maaib uam hopq. yia Bua yruj! haig ib zang Eang Jyenq naaiq teij maiq penj Eang Eei ka'naaiq.”
21.9: mo-se zyrug lovg tovb si'q zruj tiub naav an Jyenq tovg kub vwaaig. haiq taub zu'g naavb to'g Ex'q yaag mavg naaiq tiub tovb si'q naav, uaq taub zyrug tu'q mcvg Zwrtq.
21.16: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem naaig cvj mivb trug Tauj Be-e. yem Be-e maaib nxm uamb Kwrtq, tovb zinb Daavg zyruq Buaj mo-se, “heug zwavj pc'g fivj taaib zunq, yia zyrug pun uam ninb Bua hopq,” uaq nxm txvj.
21.4: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem ho-aa Bov Zwrtq Jauq yavb mivb Kxib si'q uaq tiub Jauq weig wivg e-Dom teib puv. yem Jauq zavg zwavj myenb haid maiq nxig faanb.
21.10: i-saa-laa-en myenb cvj swiq mivb Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq yem o-Botg.
21.22: “Toq pun yia Bua Jiaj meib Eei teib puv og. yia Bua maiq yavb Pyen pia'g Deig fai a'vung Wivj, yaag maiq hopq haiq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei uam. yia Bua Kuvj kan huvb tiaj Eei tomb Jauq Tauj Jiaj Jomg meib Eei teib puv Navq.”
21.12: yem naaig ninb Bua cvj swiq mivb lyepg Zyavq yem ze-letq hxvd.
21.15: Zauj Zcvj faauj Tauj aan zivb uaq teij hxvd Eei Baiq, yaag Romd mivb mo-apg teib puv Eei kapg Jaaij.”
21.13: ninb Bua cvj Zwrtq Jauq yem aan-non Daaib Len pa'q puv mcvj. aan-non Daaib yem teib puvb Waav Zcvj pia'g aa-mo-lai myenb Eei teig, yaag zruj mo-apg teib puv Zauj aa-mo-lai myenb Eei kapg Jaaij.
21.1: Kaa-naa-an myenb, aa-laatq zivb Eei huvb, tovb yem ne-kepg haid kxvq i-saa-laa-en myenb kan aa-Taa-lim uaq tiub Jauq taaib, ninb zyrug Zwrtq mivb Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Bx'q Jaaj, Zaavq tu'q teij ninb Bua Eei myenb.
21.26: hetq-Bon zruj aa-mo-lai myenb Eei si-honj huvb Eei tomb zivb. si-honj huvb Zauj zinb Daavg uaq taub mo-apg myenb Eei huvb Bx'q Jaaj Zaavq Revg yem mo-apg huvb Eei puab Diaq Eei yetg zuvq teib puv Tauj aan-non Daaib.
21.25: i-saa-laa-en myenb Zaavq Revg aa-mo-lai myenb Eei nxmb nxm zivb, lyemb hetq-Bon zivb Zauj weib kxmj Eei fiub laavd, zyrug pia'g mivb yem Jyenq.

35.18: fai sij kxvq haiq taub lovg haib Bx'q myenb taig Eei Dyavb Jaab sig Bx'q myenb, myenb zyrug taig, uaq taub se zruj taij myenb Eei myenb. xij zu'g taij ninb a'q.
35.8: ziuj fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Ripg Eei pwrng xij zu'g mc'q teij pun le-wi myenb. haiq fivj tu'q Zamq xij zu'g pun Zamq. haiq fivj tu'q zo'g xij zu'g pun zo'g.”
35.33: “+‘maiq tuvq pun meib Bua yem Eei teib puv maaib wij. laaij taij myenb, Ryaamq lyrug Fiag Dau, se pun teib puv maaib wij. yaag maiq maaib haiq Euvg haib saaj tu'q Revg lyrug Zwrtq Eei Ryaamq Eei wij, Zwrtq liud pun Ryaamq lyrug Zwrtq uaq taub Eei Ryaamq.
35.3: Navq naaiq le-wi myenb zyrug maaib zivb yem yaag maaib miab Zyavq yuvd ninb Bua Eei vovb, yuvb Zauj Euvb Euvg scvb Kuq.
35.32: “+‘yaag maiq tuvq zipq pyauj mivb yem siaj mcvg zivb Eei myenb xij zua'g mcvg Eei Eaanb weig pun ninb tu'q Rwrnj kanb Eei pyauq, maiq zuaq tomb sai myenb kwei seij Daavg.
35.21: fai laaij maaib win lovg puab Jwrnb Bx'q myenb, myenb zyrug taig, taij myenb uaq taub zyrug xij zu'g taig a'q, weig zu'g ninb se taij myenb Eei myenb. Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub haiq zang pwatg xij zu'g taij ninb a'q.
35.14: yem naaiq Jx-Dcn Daaib tov puv xij zu'g zx'q Zwrtq pua nxm. yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv cvj zx'q Zwrtq pua nxm.
35.23: fai mavg maiq pwatg myenb zyrug puvj haib Bx'q tu'q myenb taig Eei la'pyeiq cvj Bx'q zu'g myenb, myenb zyrug taig, weig zu'g Zauj zu'g taig uaq taub maiq maaib win yaag maiq maaib Hruq hxig ninb,
35.6: “meib Bua pun le-wi myenb Eei zivb xij zu'g kanb Za'levg pun Ju'q nxm weig zruj siaj mcvg zivb, pun taij myenb Eei myenb pyauj mivb yem. xij zu'g cvj Zamq feij zyepg Eeig nxm zivb Jiu pun ninb Bua.
35.34: maiq tuvq pun meib Bua yem Jyenq Eei teib puv maaib wij. se yia yem Eei txvj, weig zu'g yia, zyruq, yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Bu'Dovj.’+”
35.2: “xij zu'g Paaiq i-saa-laa-en myenb yem ninb Bua tu'q Ripg Eei Dau zx'q teij zivb Jiu pun le-wi myenb yem. yaag xij zu'g pun teij Wiv kxmj zivb Eei miab Zyavq.
35.20: haiq taub hang myenb zyrug fovq ninb fai paab paag lovg ka'naaiq zxi ninb, ninb zyrug taig,
35.24: kapq zunq Eei myenb xij zu'g yem taij myenb taig uaq taub Zauj Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub Bu'Dovj ziuj naaiq teij leid syemq.
35.28: taij myenb Eei myenb xij zu'g yem ninb Eei siaj mcvg zivb zuaq tomb sai myenb kwei seij, Ga'haaq Rwrnj ninb kanb Eei pyauq tu'q a'q.
35.7: Jiu pun le-wi myenb Eei zivb yetg zuvq maaib feij zyepg petq nxm, lyemb zivb Eei miab Zyavq.
35.29: “+‘maiq kunq yem haaij, naaiq se meib Bua txig Jiaj txig xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
35.19: Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub kanb xij zu'g taij tovb taij myenb uaq taub. haiq zang pwatg zyrug taij ninb a'q.
35.17: fai sij kxvq haiq taub lovg haib Bx'q myenb taig Eei la'pyeiq zov myenb, myenb zyrug taig, uaq taub se zruj taij myenb Eei myenb. xij zu'g taij ninb a'q.
35.31: “+‘laaij taij myenb txvg zwid zig tu'q taig Eei myenb, zuvq xij zu'g taig. maiq tuvq zipq ninb xij maaid mcvg Eei ka'naaiq.
35.30: “+‘haiq taub taij myenb xij zu'g maaib i ziaj taub zruj zxvb zevj Zivj taij tu'q uaq taub taij myenb Eei myenb. Kuvj maaib Du'g taub zruj zxvb zevj Navq, maiq tuvq taij.
35.27: Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub pwatg ninb yem zivb ka'Eiag zyrug taij, Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub yaag maiq maaib zwid.
35.11: xij zu'g kinq teij zivb zruj meib Bua siaj mcvg zivb weig pun Za'g prug taij myenb Eei myenb pyauj mivb yem uaq.
35.5: zivb ka'Eiag xij zu'g Dx'g tov puv i Zin Dx'g, naamb puv i Zin Dx'g, fai puv i Zin Dx'g, pa'q puv i Zin Dx'g, pun zivb yem zyavj Bu'Dovj. ninb Bua zyrug maaib naaiq teij Dau zruj zivb Eei miab Zyavq.
35.16: “+‘sij kxvq maaib haiq taub lovg Lia'q zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq Bx'q myenb, myenb zyrug taig, uaq taub se zruj taij myenb Eei myenb. xij zu'g taij ninb a'q.
35.4: “Jiu pun le-wi myenb uaq teij zivb xij zu'g maaib miab Zyavq yem puvb puv zivb laatg Zwrtq mivb yetg Zin Dx'g ko.
35.10: “xij zu'g kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘meib Bua Jiaj uaq vaang zi'g Jx-Dcn Daaib pia'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv,
35.22: “+‘haiq taub maiq hang myenb mq paag Za'g prug fovq zu'g fai zxi ka'naaiq zov zu'g myenb,
35.12: naaiq teij zivb se zruj siaj mcvg Eei txvj pun taij myenb Eei myenb pyauj Jaauq myenb mcvg win Eei myenb, zyrug maiq zu'g taig Daavg tu'q yem kapq zunq Eei myenb Eei Ra'Myen zu'g syemq.
35.15: naaiq teij Ju'q nxm zivb zyrug zruj siaj mcvg Eei txvj weig pun i-saa-laa-en myenb fai kanb fivj myenb, maiq kunq yetg liud Zauj ninb Bua yem fai yem trug paaq Navq, ta'faanb haiq taub Za'g prug taij myenb haib pyauj mivb yem uaq.
35.13: meib Bua pun Eei naaiq teij Ju'q nxm zivb xij zu'g zruj siaj mcvg zivb.
35.1: yem mo-apg Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib Len, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang, zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se,
35.26: “+‘mq paag sij kxvq taij myenb uaq taub, maiq kunq haiq zang, ta'faanb Zwrtq ninb pyauj mivb yem uaq nxm siaj mcvg zivb ka'Eiag,
35.25: kapq zunq Eei zwavj myenb xij zu'g Fruj taij myenb uaq taub pyauj Dutq Jaauq myenb mcvg win uaq taub Eei puab Diaq, cvj fuvj ninb Rwrnj ninb pyauj mivb yem uaq nxm siaj mcvg zivb. ninb xij zu'g yem uaq Tauj tovb lovg Zivb Revg yrub xn taaib uaq taub tomb sai myenb kwei seij.

14.18: meib kxvq, ‘zyruq maiq Qiaj Jiad syepq, zyepg zua'q Eei Namq myenb, kwavg myenb Eei zwid Zauj myenb vcvg zyruq Eei sig. mq paag maiq zeid maiq pun zu'g tivg zwid, zuvq tivg tiaj maag Eei zwid Fiag Tauj pua pyei txig funb fa'q.’
14.45: yem uaq Bov Eei aa-maa-lekq myenb Zauj Kaa-naa-an myenb zyrug Fiag taaib Bx'q hivb, zung ninb Bua Tauj ho-maa teig.
14.3: zyruq weig haiq tiug txb yia Bua Tauj naaiq nxm teib puv zu'g Ru'g Daauq taij? lyemb yia Bua Eei aub Jweiq yaag xij zu'g Zaavq mivb. yia Bua Rwrnj i-yipq teib puv zuvq kaub lovj maiq zeid?”
14.43: weig zu'g aa-maa-lekq myenb Zauj Kaa-naa-an myenb yem meib Bua Eei uaq Daavg mcvj. meib Bua xij zu'g ninb Bua Eei Ru'g Daauq taij. zyruq maiq Zauj meib Bua yem weig zu'g meib Bua Win Gaav, maiq kan Jyenq zyruq. ”
14.14: ninb Bua zyrug Buaj yem Jyenq naaiq nxm teib puv Eei myenb. o zyruq aag, naaiq nxm teib puv Eei myenb zuvq haid kxvq meib Zauj naaiq teij myenb yem. meib Myen txij Myen pun myenb pwatg Jiaj. meib Eei Bwrnj yem Jyenq ninb Bua kub vwaaig. luvb Nxi zang zyruq yem Bwrnb Dyrub txb ninb Bua. luvb mwrnd zang yem trub Dyrub.
14.34: meib Bua xij zu'g syrug meib Bua kanb Eei zwid pwavq feij zyepg Havj. ziuj mivb zaab teib puv uaq teij feij zyepg Nxi, xij zu'g yetg Havj tiq yetg Nxi. meib Bua zyrug hiuq tu'q yia maiq hxpg Hruq meib Bua se Navq haiq nx.”+’
14.2: i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb vopq mo-se Zauj aa-lon. ninb Bua kxvq, “feij tu'q yia Bua yem i-yipq teib puv taig, fai yem naaiq teib puvb Waav taig maiq zei!
14.36: mo-se Paaiq mivb zaab teib puv Eei myenb Rwrnj taaib kxvq to'g teib puv Eei Jaub lrug Duaq zwavj myenb kwaij ninb,
14.35: yia, zyruq, kxvq liud a'q. yia Dovg haaij zuvq xij Navq naaiq nx zruj pun naaiq teij waaig haig Eei zwavj myenb, tovb kapq Hruq Zauj yia txib tekg Eei myenb. ninb Bua xij zu'g yem naaiq teib puvb Waav pwavb zu'g ninb Bua Eei setq mweid Nxi. xij zu'g yem naaiq taig Revg a'q.”
14.24: mq paag yia Eei pru, Kaa-lepq, Eei Hruq Zauj uaq teij maiq fib Navq. ninb yaag kan Revg yia. yia zyrug xij txb ninb pia'g ninb zaab liud uaq nxm teib puv. ninb Eei zeib fun yaag xij tu'q Ripg.
14.7: yaag kxvq Buaj zwavj myenb, “yia Bua mivb yrub zaab kxmj uaq nxm teib puv, pwatg teib puv za'kevb! lovj haig.
14.17: “zyruq aag, ib zang Toq pun meib Eei tomb Qa'q piuj mevb Zwrtq taaib ziuj meib kxvq Jiaj Eei waag.
14.11: zyruq Buaj mo-se, “naaiq teij myenb xij mavg Piaj yia Tauj haiq zang? maiq kunq yia yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj zruj Bua'g hxvb Eei Javb hog Dovg naaig Zamq, ninb Bua Zxg xij vcvg Jyenq maiq syenj yia Tauj haiq zang?
14.33: meib Bua Eei fu'Jweiq xij zu'g yem naaiq zruj mavg yuvb Eei myenb. se laaij meib Bua maiq zyepg zua'q, ninb Bua Zivj zu'g syrug Kruq pwavq feij zyepg Havj, zuaq Tauj meib Bua taub taub taig Revg.
14.16: ‘zyruq maiq maaib panb zeig txb naaiq teij myenb pia'g ninb hruq pun ninb Bua uaq nxm teib puv, zyrug yem uaq teib puvb Waav taij Revg ninb Bua.’
14.40: ta'Eeig Dxm Ryruq Eei, ninb Bua faauj Bov Lav teij Eei txvj mivb kxvq, “yia Bua ib zang xij mivb pia'g zyruq lcvd pun Eei txvj. yia Bua paamd zwid mig a'q.”
14.37: se Rwrnj taaib zunb waaig Eei fyenj kxvq to'g uaq nxm teib puv uaq teij, zu'g zyruq pun ninb Bua putq tomb wrnb pcvg taig Revg mig a'q.
14.4: laanb yaag Buaj laanb, “Bua kinq taub zruj pyeiq zeiq txb Bua Rwrnj i-yipq teib puv x'g?”
14.12: yia xij pun ninb Bua putq tomb wrnb pcvg myetg ninb Bua, pun ninb Bua maiq tu'q Ripg uaq nxm teib puv. mq paag yia xij pun meib zruj yetg fivj Eei ovb Taaij. uaq fivj xij zruj kaub Lo, kaub henq ninb Bua Eei fivj.”
14.13: mo-se kxvq Buaj zyruq, “meib lovg meib Eei tomb Qa'q txb naaiq teij myenb yem i-yipq myenb Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib. i-yipq myenb haid meib taij meib Eei myenb,
14.26: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
14.28: weig naaiq xij zu'g Buaj ninb Bua, ‘zyruq kxvq, “yia zyavb Jyenq yia kanb Eei mcvg kxvq, ziuj haid meib Bua kxvq Eei waag yia zuvq xij zruj pun meib Bua a'q.
14.8: sij kxvq zyruq hxpg Hruq Bua nx, ninb haib txb Bua pia'g uaq nxm teib puv, yaag zx'q uaq nxm teib puv pun Bua. se Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv.
14.9: mq paag maiq tuvq vcvg zyruq, yaag maiq tuvq kamb Riaj yem uaq nxm teib puv Eei myenb. Bua huvb heg Bx'q hivb ninb Bua. Ria ninb Bua uaq Euvg Qa'q zitg mig a'q. zyruq yaag Zauj Bua yem. maiq tuvq kamb Riaj ninb Bua maa'b!”
14.32: mq paag meib Bua c'q, xij zu'g yem naaiq teib puvb Waav Dxtq Revg.
14.21: mq paag yia za'kevb zyavb Jyenq, yia Eei Favb laavg yaag xij pwavq Revg luvb Diaq. naaiq i Euvg se zyen haig. Dovg naaiq teij zyen
14.23: ninb Bua zyrug yetg liud maiq tu'q pia'g yia lcvd pun ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij Eei teib puv. mavg Piaj yia uaq teij maiq maaib yetg taub tu'q pwatg.
14.6: nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, Zauj ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq, tovb mivb zaab teib puv Eei i taub, Raub haig zyrug petq kanb Eei lwi,
14.44: mq paag zwavj myenb kaamq faauj Bov Lav teij Eei txvj mivb maiq kunq mo-se Zauj zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav maiq Zwrtq Dopg liub Zyavq.
14.20: zyruq tau, “ziuj meib Toq Eei waag yia kwavg ninb Bua Eei zwid.
14.5: mo-se Zauj aa-lon zyrug Baapq Fiag i-saa-laa-en zwavj myenb kapq zunq Eei txvj Ra'Myen.
14.19: zyruq aag, ziuj meib zyepg zua'q Eei Namq haig myenb, Toq kwavg Gxi naaiq teij myenb Eei zwid, Navq ninb Bua yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib Tauj ib zang meib kwavg ninb Bua Eei zwid uaq nx.”
14.38: mivb zaab teib puv Eei myenb Kuvj maaib nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, Zauj ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq, maaib mcvg zyavb Navq.
14.31: mq paag meib Bua Eei fu'Jweiq, tovb meib Bua kxvq xij zu'g Zaavq mivb, yia xij txb pia'g meib Bua Gemb uaq nxm teib puv. uaq nxm teib puv zyrug penj ninb Bua Eei mig a'q.
14.27: “naaiq teij x'q haig Eei zwavj myenb xij vopq yia Tauj haiq zang? yia haid naaiq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb vopq yia, kwaij yia.
14.41: mq paag mo-se kxvq, “meib Bua weig haiq tiug vcvg zyruq Eei livg? meib Bua maiq haib zruj maiq zyavb sig.
14.1: uaq mwrnd zwavj myenb Qa'q Eyemq Bwi Eei.
14.39: mo-se kxvq naaiq teij Jaub lrug pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mwavj. pc'g fivj zyrug Raub haig, Qa'q Eyemq.
14.10: zwavj myenb zyrug kxvq xij zx'q la'pyeiq zov taig ninb Bua. uaq zang, zyruq Eei Favb laavg hing Zwrtq taaib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub, pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb pwatg.
14.25: weig zu'g aa-maa-lekq myenb Zauj Kaa-naa-an myenb yem uaq teij hxvg zavg Eei txvj, Fav Nxi meib Bua xij zu'g taauj sin Zwrtq Jauq huvj Jyenq teib puvb Waav, kan Kxib si'q uaq tiub Jauq mivb.”
14.22: se yia hruq Jyenq naaiq teij myenb, maiq maaib yetg taub tu'q zyavb Jyenq Tauj pia'g uaq nxm teib puv. ninb Bua pwatg Jiaj yia Eei Favb laavg, yaag pwatg Jiaj yia yem i-yipq teib puv Zauj teib puvb Waav zruj Bua'g hxvb Eei Javb hog, mq paag ninb Bua seij yia zyepg Rung, yaag maiq mwavj yia Eei waag.
14.42: maiq tuvq mivb weig zu'g zyruq maiq Zauj meib Bua yem. meib Bua zyrug zu'g winb wavq taij meib Bua,
14.15: sij kxvq zyruq zruj yetg Rung taij Revg naaiq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb, peiq taij yetg taub myenb, fivb fivj haid meib Navq naaiq nx zruj ninb Bua zyrug kxvq,
14.29: ei saauq myenb uaq zang, yem Eig zyepg Havj faauj mcvj Eei myenb, tovb vopq yia uaq teij, zuvq xij zu'g yem naaiq teib puvb Waav Dxtq Revg.
14.30: Zwrtq liud ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq, Zauj nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, maiq maaib yetg taub haib tu'q pia'g yia hruq pun ninb Bua yem uaq nxm teib puv.

23.18: Baa-laa-am cvj kxvq Zwrtq ninb trug Eei waag, “sipg-po Eei txn, Baa-laakq, taaib mwavj maa'b! mwavj yia xij kxvq Eei waag.
23.8: Tinb huvb maiq zyruj uaq teij, yia Navq haiq nx haib zyruj?   zyruq maiq zevj Eei, yia Navq haiq nx haib zevj?
23.3: Baa-laa-am kxvq Buaj Baa-laakq, “meib sruq Jyenq naaiq meib puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq ka'Len, yia kanb mivb Pyen teij. Riaj zyruq taaib pwavb yia. ninb Buaj haiq Euvg yia, yia zuvq Buaj meib.” Baa-laa-am zyrug faauj nxm txvj Lav Eei, Fav Eei.
23.21: “maiq pwatg yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun xij maaib haiq Euvg Raub Kruq. maiq pwatg i-saa-laa-en myenb maaib haiq Euvg Kwrnj naanb.   zyruq, ninb Bua Eei Tinb huvb, Zauj ninb Bua yem, hrug huvb Eei Qiaj yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj.
23.14: Baa-laakq zyrug txb Baa-laa-am Tauj soj-fim Eei Deig, yem pitg-kaa Bovb nivq. yem uaq ninb cvj Zeij siag nxm ziab txvb, mrud nxm ziab txvb ziag taub vovb kruq Zauj taub pa'ki yuvb kruq.
23.23: maiq haib puvj haiq Euvg faatq hxig yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun. maiq haib puvj tiv puvj Jyemj hxig i-saa-laa-en myenb. ib zang myenb xij kxvq Tauj yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun, i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘mavg kaaj Tinb huvb Navq haiq nx zruj!’
23.6: Baa-laa-am zyrug Rwrnj, pwatg Baa-laakq Zauj mo-apg uaq teij yetq zuvq Jyen Zxg sruq Jyenq ninb ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ka'Len.
23.2: Baa-laakq zyrug ei Jyenq Baa-laa-am Eei waag zruj. ninb Bua i taub yem mrud nxm ziab txvb, yetg nxm ziab txvb ziag yetg taub vovb kruq Zauj yetg taub pa'ki yuvb kruq.
23.20: yia zipq livg pwav waag, Tinb huvb Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua, yia yaag maiq haib kxiq Rwrnj.
23.24: naaiq fivj myenb Jiad sin Navq taub syenb Eeid nx, sruq Jyenq Navq taub syenb kruq. ninb maiq pweij Tauj Eang Revg ninb zx'q Eei xq, cvj hopq Revg ninb taij taaib Eei Ryaamq.”
23.28: Baa-laakq zyrug txb Baa-laa-am Tauj pe-o Bovb nivq. yem naaig haib mavg Fiag pwatg teib puvb Waav.
23.7: Baa-laa-am zyrug kxvq Zwrtq ninb trug Eei waag. ninb kxvq, “mo-apg huvb, Baa-laakq, txb yia Zwrtq aa-lam, se txb yia yem tov puv mcvj Eei Bov taaib. ninb kxvq, ‘taaib maa'b! Tevj yia zyruj yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun. taaib maa'b! Tevj yia zevj i-saa-laa-en myenb.’
23.29: Baa-laa-am kxvq Buaj Baa-laakq, “yem naaiq xij zu'g Zeij siag nxm ziab txvb weig yia, cvj liug leid siag taub vovb kruq, siag taub pa'ki yuvb kruq.”
23.19: Tinb huvb maiq zeid myenb, ninb maiq kxvb pc'g. ninb yaag maiq zeid paamb myenb, zyrug maiq zu'g kxiq za'eij. kxvq liud Eei waag, ninb maiq zeid xij ei Jyenq zruj fai? ninb lcvd Eei waag, ninb maiq zeid xij zruj zyavj?
23.17: Baa-laa-am Rwrnj mivb, pwatg Baa-laakq Zauj mo-apg myenb Eei Jyen sruq Jyenq ninb ziag Eei ka'naaiq Eei ka'Len. Baa-laakq naaig ninb, “zyruq Navq haiq nx kxvq?”
23.30: Baa-laakq zyrug ei Jyenq Baa-laa-am Eei waag zruj. yem mrud nxm ziab txvb ziag taub vovb kruq Zauj taub pa'ki yuvb kruq.
23.27: Baa-laakq kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “taaib maa'b! yia txb meib mivb kanb nxm txvj. Riaj Tinb huvb hxpg Hruq pun meib yem uaq nxm txvj Tevj yia zyruj ninb Bua.”
23.11: Baa-laakq kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “meib zruj haiq Euvg pun yia? yia txb meib taaib naaiq weig zyruj yia Eei winb wavq, mq paag meib Kuvj pwav waag pun ninb Bua Navq.”
23.5: zyruq Buaj Baa-laa-am Navq haiq nx kxvq, yaag heug ninb, “Rwrnj Baa-laakq uaq zx'q naaiq teij waag Buaj ninb.”
23.9: yia yem Bcvb nivq pwatg ninb Bua. yia yem Lav Eei txvj mavg Jyenq ninb Bua, se yetg fivj maiq zxpg kanb fivj Eei myenb, peiq zwavj kua'q Eei pc'g fivj, ninb Bua funj kanb levg Jeiq Eei myenb.
23.16: zyruq taaib pwavb Baa-laa-am, Buaj ninb hxpg zu'g Navq haiq nx kxvq, yaag heug ninb, “Rwrnj Baa-laakq uaq trug naaiq teij waag Buaj ninb.”
23.4: Tinb huvb pwavb Baa-laa-am, Baa-laa-am zyrug kxvq, “yia liug leid zyavj siag nxm ziab txvb. mrud nxm ziab txvb yia ziag taub vovb kruq Zauj taub pa'ki yuvb kruq.”
23.10: yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun Dovg niab Buv Zamq, haiq taub haib saauq tu'q zyend? haiq taub haib funj i-saa-laa-en myenb pyei kruq Eei yetg kruq? Toq pun yia kwei seij Navq Kuq myenb, yaag pun yia Eei setq mweid Nxi Navq ninb Eei nx.”
23.22: Tinb huvb txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv, ninb Bua maaib Qa'q Navq Yiab vovb nx.
23.12: Baa-laa-am tau, “yia xij zu'g kxvq zyruq pun yia kxvq uaq teij waag maiq zeid?”
23.15: Baa-laa-am kxvq Buaj Baa-laakq, “meib sruq Jyenq naaiq meib ziag Eei ka'naaiq ka'Len, zuaq yia mivb uaq mcvj pwavb zyruq. ”
23.13: Baa-laakq cvj kxvq Buaj ninb, “Zauj yia mivb kanb nxm txvj og. yem uaq meib haib mavg tu'q pwatg teij i-saa-laa-en myenb mq paag pwatg maiq Revg. meib yem uaq nxm txvj Tevj yia zyruj ninb Bua.”
23.1: Baa-laa-am kxvq Buaj Baa-laakq, “xij zu'g Zeij siag nxm ziab txvb weig yia, cvj liug leid siag taub vovb kruq, siag taub pa'ki yuvb kruq pun yia.”
23.26: Baa-laa-am tau, “yia Buaj Jiaj meib, zyruq kxvq haiq Euvg, yia xij zu'g ei Jyenq zruj maiq zeid?”
23.25: Baa-laakq kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “meib maiq zyruj yetg teij ninb Bua, yaag maiq tuvq pwav waag ninb Bua maa'b!”

6.18: “+‘naa-sij myenb xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg Teij Revg tovb zruj Javb hog pun Ziv ninb zx'q kanb fuvj pun zyruq Eei Ba'pyei Zauj syaam. xij zu'g zx'q uaq teij Ba'pyei taaib tapq ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq teij ka'naaiq ka'Diaq mcvj Eei trud.
6.8: ta'faanb yem fuvj kanb pun zyruq Eei Nxib Eia'g, ninb penj zyruq Eei Zivb Revg myenb.
6.3: uaq taub xij zu'g keg, maiq tuvq hopq a'vung tiuq fai haiq Euvg tiuq. yaag maiq tuvq hopq lovg a'vung tiuq fai haiq Euvg tiuq zruj taaib Eei uamb swi. maiq tuvq hopq a'vung pyruq Eei uam fai Eang a'vung pyruq, maiq kunq pyrub Eyemd fai pyrub Gaai.
6.21: “+‘naaiq se naa-sij myenb Eei leid, tovb ninb zx'q kanb fuvj pun zyruq uaq zang lcvd Jiad vcvg waag xij fovg hxg haiq Euvg pun zyruq. sij kxvq haib lcvd pun kaub Zamq naaig, ninb xij zu'g ei ninb lcvd Eei waag zruj Revg.’+”
6.14: yem naaig ninb xij zu'g zx'q ka'naaiq weig fovg hxg pun zyruq. lovg taub txij Havj, maiq waaig favj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq weig puaq ziag, Zauj taub txij Havj, maiq waaig favj Eei pa'ki yuvb zeig ziag weig fi'q zwid, Zauj taub maiq waaig favj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq ziag weig Jiu Tov.
6.23: “xij zu'g kxvq Buaj aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn, ‘meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx pwav waag i-saa-laa-en myenb. xij zu'g kxvq,
6.6: yem ninb fuvj kanb pun zyruq Eei zyavb hog maiq Kub mivb fatq Janb taig Eei sei.
6.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, haiq taub xij levg Jeiq Eei lcvd Jiad vcvg waag, zx'q kanb fuvj pun zyruq weig zruj naa-sij myenb,
6.20: naaiq teij ka'naaiq sai myenb zyrug zx'q taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen Zunq kiv weig zruj fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. naaiq teij ka'naaiq se Zivb Revg Eei, yaag penj sai myenb Eei mig a'q, lyemb Zunq kiv fovg hxg liud Eei lx'g Ywav xq Zauj fovg hxg liud Eei zwib. yem naaig mivb, naa-sij myenb hopq tu'q a'vung tiuq a'q.
6.24: “+‘+“Toq zyruq Zeij fu'q pun meib, ziuj kruj meib.
6.7: lyemb kanb Eei tia fai maa, kxj fai yrud, txg fai muag taig, maiq tuvq laaij ninb Bua pun kanb maaib wij, weig zu'g zx'q kanb fuvj pun Tinb huvb Eei Javb hog se yem ninb Eei mGxvq.
6.19: “+‘naa-sij myenb Teij liud fuvj pun zyruq Eei Ba'pyei, sai myenb zyrug zx'q nxm wrnb zua'g Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq Eei puab zwib, cvj zx'q nxm yem Daan ka'Euad maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq, Zauj nxm maiq an pivq Eei Fuab pia'g, an Jyenq naaiq taub naa-sij myenb Eei puad ka'Euad.
6.17: ninb cvj zx'q uaq taub pa'ki yuvb kruq Zauj uaq Daan maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq fovg hxg ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov, yaag maaib ziag Eei laavb zi'g Zauj Ziaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yetg Fiag ziag.
6.27: “Navq naaig, sij kxvq ninb Bua tevq yia Eei Buaj pwav waag i-saa-laa-en myenb, yia zyrug Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua.”
6.11: sai myenb zyrug zx'q nxm ziag weig fi'q zwid, cvj zx'q nxm puaq ziag weig uaq laanb myenb nitq zu'g Janb taig zyrug maaib Eei wij. tovb uaq Nxi ninb yaag xij zu'g saaj mGxvq Eei wij.
6.5: “+‘yem lcvd Jyenq zruj naa-sij myenb Eei zyavb hog maiq tuvq Teij mGxvq. xij zu'g zuaq Tauj tivg taaib Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq. ninb xij zu'g Zivb Revg, zuaq Tauj fuvj kanb pun zyruq Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq. xij zu'g lyrub Ba'pyei Zauj syaam Daauq.
6.9: “+‘sij kxvq yem ninb Eei ka'Len maaib myenb lyemb zeib taig, ninb fuvj pun zyruq Eei mGxvq zyrug maaib wij. Tauj saaj wij Eei Nxi, se ta'Zyetq Nxi uaq Nxi, xij zu'g Teij Revg mGxvq.
6.16: “+‘sai myenb zyrug zx'q naaiq teij ka'naaiq taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen ziag fi'q zwid Zauj puaq ziag.
6.4: yem zruj Jyenq naa-sij myenb Eei zyavb hog, maiq tuvq Eang yem a'vung Mei Zwrtq taaib Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq. maiq kunq a'vung Eim fai a'vung pyruq Eei Dopq, maiq tuvq Eang.
6.10: Tauj ta'petq Nxi uaq Nxi, ninb xij zu'g txb i nxm nx'g Go fai i nxm pc'g kopq lunj Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg Jiu pun sai myenb.
6.12: xij zu'g weig tivg taaib Eei Nxib Eia'g cvj zx'q kanb fuvj pun zyruq. yaag xij zu'g txb taub yetg Havj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq taaib ziag weig ninb zruj txvg Eei sig. zinb Daavg Eei Nxib Eia'g maiq funj a'q, weig zu'g fuvj kanb pun zyruq Eei zyavb hog zu'g maaib wij mig a'q.
6.15: yaag maaib ziag Eei laavb zi'g Zauj Ziaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yetg Fiag ziag. cvj maaib yetg Daan maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq, Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub Eei Fuaq, Zauj maiq an pivq Eei Fuab pia'g Raatq Jyenq ka'lanq yrub.
6.13: “+‘naa-sij myenb Eei leid, tovb ninb zx'q kanb fuvj pun zyruq Eei Nxib Eia'g pwavq, se Navq naaiq. xij zu'g txb ninb mivb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg.
6.26: Toq zyruq Win Myen mavg meib, pun meib maaib pcvb xn.”+’
6.25: Toq zyruq zruj lovj pun meib, Zeij en pun meib.

34.18: yaag xij zu'g Paaiq yetg fivj yetg taub pyeiq zeiq Tevj Jyenq.
34.8: yem ho-aa Bov mivb Tauj pia'g haa-matq Eei Jauq. cvj Jiaj Tauj sej-Datg,
34.3: “+‘naamb puv Eei kapg Jaaij se yavb sin teib puvb Waav, kan e-Dom Eei kapg Jaaij mivb. yem tov puv se yem Kxib taig Jomg Eei txvj Jiad kxn,
34.21: Ben-yaa-min fivj Qitq-lon Eei txn, e-li-Daatg
34.14: weig zu'g lu-Ben fivj Zauj kaatg fivj Zauj maa-natq-sej Eei Daamb fivj, ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng, tu'q ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng mig a'q.
34.23: maa-natq-sej fivj e-fotq Eei txn, han-ni-en
34.6: “+‘fai puv Eei kapg Jaaij se me-Di-te-le-nyen Kxiq. naaiq se meib Bua fai puv Eei kapg Jaaij.
34.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘meib Bua pia'g Kaa-naa-an teib puv, tovb yia pun weig zruj meib Bua Ripg Eei pwrng uaq nxm teib puv Eei kapg Jaaij, zyrug maaib Navq naaiq.
34.20: si-me-on fivj am-mi-hutq Eei txn, se-mu-en
34.24: e-faa-im fivj sipq-Taan Eei txn, Ke-mu-en
34.28: napq-Taa-li fivj am-mi-hutq Eei txn, pe-Daa-hen”
34.7: “+‘pa'q puv Eei kapg Jaaij xij zu'g yem me-Di-te-le-nyen Kxiq pcv za'g Eei mivb ho-aa Bov.
34.29: naaiq se zyruq Paaiq Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb yem Kaa-naa-an teib puv pun Gxi ninb Bua Ripg Eei Dau.
34.19: naaiq teij pyeiq zeiq Eei Buaj maaib Navq naaiq. yu-Daa fivj ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq
34.17: “Tevj meib Paaiq Dau pun pc'g fivj Ripg uaq teij myenb Eei Buaj maaib Navq naaiq. maaib e-le-aa-saa sai myenb, Zauj nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa.
34.27: aa-se fivj se-lo-mi Eei txn, aa-hi-hutq
34.11: yem se-faam kapg Jaaij zyrug Fiag Tauj lipq-laa zivb, yem aa-yin tov puv mcvj, cvj kan kaa-li-li Kxib txn tov puv mcvj Eei Baiq Fiag.
34.5: yem atg-mon zyrug Wiv mivb Tauj i-yipq Do'q cvj Zwrtq mivb Tauj me-Di-te-le-nyen Kxiq.
34.9: mivb Tauj si-fon, cvj mivb Jomg haa-saa-e-nan. naaiq xij zruj meib Bua pa'q puv Eei kapg Jaaij.
34.4: cvj Wiv mivb naamb puv Tauj aakg-lapq-Bim zxv, Jiaj sin teib puvb Waav, cvj huvj Jyenq naamb puv Tauj Kaa-Detg-Baa-nia. cvj Jiaj mivb Tauj haa-saa-latq-Daa, cvj Jiaj Tauj atg-mon.
34.10: “+‘tov puv Eei kapg Jaaij xij zu'g yem haa-saa-le-nan, pcv za'g Eei mivb Tauj se-faam.
34.22: Daan fivj yokq-li Eei txn, Bukg-Ki
34.12: kapg Jaaij zyrug yem naaig kan Jx-Dcn Daaib Fiag, mivb Tauj Jomg Kxib taig. “+‘naaiq zyrug penj meib Bua Eei teib puv ziuj puvb puv Eei kapg Jaaij Wiv Jyenq.’+”
34.15: naaiq teij i fivj Zauj Daamb fivj tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng yem Jx-Dcn Daaib tov puv mcvj, Ba'Nxi Zwrtq uaq puv, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang.”
34.13: mo-se Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, “naaiq se meib Bua xij zu'g tivg mcvg mavg, Paaiq pun Gxi Eei Dau weig zruj meib Bua Ripg Eei pwrng. se zyruq Paaiq pun Duab fivj Zauj Daamb fivj Eei Dau,
34.26: itg-saaj-Kaa fivj atg-saan Eei txn, pan-Ti-en
34.25: sej-Bu-lun fivj paa-naakq Eei txn, e-li-saa-faan

2.18: yem fai puv mcvj, e-faa-im fivj Eei kwanb kwanb xij zu'g Zxv ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq. e-faa-im fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib am-mi-hutq Eei txn, e-li-saa-maa.
2.8: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyaa waang siag Zin feij pc'q taub.
2.33: mq paag le-wi myenb maiq tu'q saauq pia'g uaq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb Navq zyruq Paaiq mo-se nx.
2.3: yem tov puv mcvj, Ba'Nxi Zwrtq uaq puv, yu-Daa fivj Eei kwanb kwanb xij zu'g Zxv ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq. yu-Daa fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib am-mi-naa-Dapg Eei txn, naa-son.
2.32: naaiq se i-saa-laa-en myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei myenb hrud saauq. yem Dopg liub Zyavq ziuj ninb Bua Eei kwanb saauq taaib yetg zuvq maaib Ju'q sinj pua Zin Mmd pc'q Mmd zyepg taub myenb.
2.21: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pua waang i Zin Eig pc'q taub.
2.14: Jiaj mivb, kaatg fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq. kaatg fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib De-u-en Eei txn, e-li-yaa-saapg.
2.23: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pua waang pyaa Zin feij pc'q taub.
2.6: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyaa waang pyei Zin feij pc'q taub.
2.34: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug zruj Revg ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se Eei waag. ninb Bua Navq naaiq nx yem ninb Bua Eei keb ka'Diaq Zxv Dopg liub. kx'g myenb yaag ziuj kx'g myenb Eei fivj Navq uaq nx Zwrtq Jauq.
2.2: “i-saa-laa-en myenb xij zu'g Zxv kanb Eei Dopg liub Wiv kxmj yaag Win mivb wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub uaq puv, kx'g myenb yem kx'g myenb Eei pwrnb fivj keb Zauj puvb pwrng keb ka'Diaq.”
2.20: maa-natq-sej fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq e-faa-im fivj. maa-natq-sej fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib pe-Daa-su Eei txn, kaa-maa-li-en.
2.24: pia'g e-faa-im uaq puv Eei kwanb kwanb yetg zuvq maaib yetg sinj Yetg Zin yetg pc'q taub. Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog naaiq kwanb zruj ta'faam kwanb.
2.28: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyei waang yetg Zin Mmd pc'q taub.
2.7: Jiaj mivb, sej-Bu-lun fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq. sej-Bu-lun fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib he-lon Eei txn, e-li-apg.
2.29: Jiaj mivb, napq-Taa-li fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq. napq-Taa-li fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib e-nan Eei txn, aa-hi-laa.
2.19: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyei waang Mmd pc'q taub.
2.17: Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog, mivb Daavg uaq teij i kwanb Zauj Ga'haaq mivb uaq teij i kwanb Bu'Dovj, xij zu'g maaib le-wi myenb txb Jyenq wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub mivb. xij zu'g zweib yetq zweib Eeig Zwrtq Jauq ziuj kwanb kwanb Zxv ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub. kwanb kwanb xij zu'g yem kanb Eei txvj yaag yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq.
2.31: pia'g Daan fivj uaq puv yetg zuvq maaib yetg sinj pyaa waang siag Zin lua'g pc'q taub. Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog ninb Bua zruj Ga'haaq laai uaq kwanb yaag yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq.
2.30: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyaa waang pua Zin feij pc'q taub.
2.27: aa-se fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq Daan fivj. aa-se fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib o-Kaan Eei txn, paa-ki-en.
2.11: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyei waang Ju'q Zin Mmd pc'q taub.
2.5: itg-saaj-Kaa fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq yu-Daa fivj. itg-saaj-Kaa fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib zu-aa Eei txn, ne-Tan-en.
2.9: pia'g yu-Daa uaq puv Eei kwanb kwanb yetg zuvq maaib yetg sinj Yetg waang Ju'q Zin feij pc'q taub. Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog naaiq teij xij zu'g mivb Daavg.
2.16: pia'g lu-Ben uaq puv Eei kwanb kwanb yetg zuvq maaib yetg sinj pyaa waang yetg Zin feij pc'q Mmd zyepg taub. Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog naaiq teij zruj ta'Eeig kwanb.
2.4: ninb Eei kwanb maaib siag waang pyei Zin lua'g pc'q taub.
2.10: yem naamb puv mcvj, lu-Ben fivj Eei kwanb kwanb xij zu'g Zxv ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq. lu-Ben fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib se-De-e Eei txn, e-li-su.
2.22: Jiaj mivb, Ben-yaa-min fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq. Ben-yaa-min fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib ki-De-o-ni Eei txn, aa-Bi-Dan.
2.12: si-me-on fivj xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub nitq Jyenq lu-Ben fivj. si-me-on fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib suj-li-satq-Dai Eei txn, se-lu-mi-en.
2.15: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyei waang pyaa Zin lua'g pc'q Mmd zyepg taub.
2.13: ninb Eei kwanb maaib pyaa waang Duab Zin faamb pc'q taub.
2.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
2.26: ninb Eei kwanb maaib Ju'q waang i Zin Zyetq pc'q taub.
2.25: yem pa'q puv mcvj, Daan fivj Eei kwanb kwanb xij zu'g Zxv ninb Bua Eei Dopg liub yem kanb Eei keb ka'Diaq. Daan fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib am-mi-Qatq-Dai Eei txn, aa-hi-ye-se.

36.3: sij kxvq naaiq teij sia'q Zauj kanb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb txv Jaa, ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng zyrug yem yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij Ripg Eei pwrng zx'q Zwrtq mig a'q, Tim pia'g ninb Bua Eei Goj uaq puv. yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij Ripg Eei pwrng zyrug zo'g Fiag a'q.
36.8: maiq kunq haiq fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb, haiq taub sia'q tu'q Ripg Dau, xij zu'g lovg tia uaq fivj myenb txv Jaa weig pun mrud taub i-saa-laa-en myenb tu'q syrug yem ovb Taaij Ripg Eei pwrng.
36.9: Navq naaiq, meib Bua Ripg Eei maiq maaib yem naaiq fivj swiq pia'g kanb fivj, weig zu'g fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb xij zu'g kruj ninb Bua Ripg Eei pwrng.”
36.7: Navq naaig, i-saa-laa-en myenb Ripg Eei pwrng maiq zu'g yem yetg fivj swiq mivb yem kanb fivj, weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en myenb taub taub xij zu'g kx'g myenb kruj Jyenq kx'g myenb yem ovb Taaij tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng Dau.
36.5: mo-se zyrug ziuj zyruq Eei waag Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, “yo-sepq Eei puvb pwrng kxvq tu'q hxpg a'q.
36.4: Tauj i-saa-laa-en myenb hrug Eei Havj uaq Havj, sia'q Ripg Eei pwrng zyrug Tim pia'g ninb txv Jaa uaq fivj mig a'q. Navq naaig ninb Bua tu'q Eei pwrng zyrug yem yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij Ripg Eei pwrng zx'q Zwrtq mivb.”
36.2: ninb Bua kxvq, “zyruq Paaiq meib, yia Bua Eei zyruq, tivg mcvg mavg pun Gxi Dau i-saa-laa-en myenb Ripg uaq zang, ninb heug meib zx'q yia Bua Eei kxb yrud, sej-lo-fe-hatg, Eei pwrng pun ninb Eei zwavj sia'q Ripg.
36.6: zyruq Navq naaiq nx Paaiq sej-lo-fe-hatg Eei zwavj sia'q. ninb Bua sweib ping Zauj haiq taub txv Jaa yaag tu'q, mq paag Kuvj xij zu'g lovg tia uaq fivj myenb Navq.
36.13: naaiq se zyruq yem mo-apg Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib Len, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang lovg mo-se hatg Eei livg Zauj leib latg.
36.12: ninb Bua lovg yo-sepq Eei txn, maa-natq-sej Eei funb fa'q uaq fivj Eei myenb. Navq naaig ninb Bua tu'q Ripg Eei pwrng Zxg yem ninb Bua Eei tia uaq fivj ka'Euad.
36.11: sej-lo-fe-hatg Eei sia'q, maa-haa-laa, Ti-laa-saa, hokq-laa, min-Kaa Zauj no-yaa, yetg zuvq Zauj ninb Bua Eei pc'g muad txig txv Jaa.
36.1: ki-le-aatg se maa-Ki-le Eei txn, maa-Ki-le se maa-natq-sej Eei txn, maa-natq-sej se yo-sepq Eei txn. ki-le-aatg Eei puvb pwrng pyeiq zeiq taaib lxd mo-se Zauj zwavj pyeiq zeiq, tovb fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
36.10: zyruq Navq haiq nx Buaj mo-se, sej-lo-fe-hatg Eei sia'q zyrug Navq uaq nx zruj.

20.18: mq paag e-Dom huvb tau, “yia Bua maiq pun meib Bua yavb yia Bua Eei teib puv Jiaj. sij kxvq meib Bua vcvg Jyenq Jiaj nx, yia Bua zyrug Zwrtq mivb lovg Ru'g Daauq Zauj meib Bua Bx'q Jaaj.”
20.8: “zx'q pyaab Byaag taaib. meib Zauj meib Eei kxj, aa-lon, xij zu'g heug zwavj myenb kapq zunq, txv Jyenq ninb Bua Buaj uaq nxm la'pyeiq Zwrtq uam taaib. uam zyrug yem la'pyeiq lyrug Zwrtq taaib. Navq naaiq meib zyrug pun uam yem la'pyeiq Zwrtq taaib pun zwavj myenb Zauj ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq tu'q hopq.”
20.3: ninb Bua Zauj mo-se Rcv Jaaj kxvq, “yia Bua Eei kxb yrud yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taig uaq zang, feij tu'q yia Bua tu'q Zauj Jyenq taig kaub lovj.
20.21: laaij e-Dom myenb maiq pun ninb Bua yavb teib puv Jiaj, i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug taauj sin yavb kanb tiub Jauq mivb a'q.
20.14: mo-se Paaiq teij myenb yem Kaa-Detg zivb mivb lxd e-Dom teib puv Eei huvb tiaj kxvq, “meib Eei yrud, i-saa-laa-en myenb, Navq naaiq kxvq. meib hiuq tu'q yia Bua pwavb Jiaj Eei Kruq naang.
20.23: yem nitq e-Dom teib puv, ho-aa Bov uaq, zyruq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
20.6: mo-se Zauj aa-lon leib Gxi zwavj myenb mivb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, Baapq Fiag Dau. zyruq Eei Favb laavg hing Zwrtq taaib pun ninb Bua pwatg.
20.2: yem uaq nxm txvj maiq maaib uam pun zwavj pc'g fivj hopq. ninb Bua zyrug kapq zunq taaib kwaij mo-se Zauj aa-lon.
20.20: huvb tiaj cvj tau, “yia Bua Navq haaij yaag maiq pun meib Bua Jiaj.” e-Dom myenb Eei Junb pcv Zamq! Eei zyrug Zwrtq taaib xij Bx'q ninb Bua.
20.24: “aa-lon xij zu'g kwei seij. ninb maiq tu'q pia'g yia Jiu pun i-saa-laa-en myenb uaq nxm teib puv, weig zu'g yem me-li-Baa uam meib Bua i taub vcvg Jyenq yia Buaj Eei waag.
20.28: mo-se Jaiq aa-lon Eei zruj sai lwi pun aa-lon Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, zu'q Jyenq. aa-lon zyrug yem uaq Bovb nivq kwei seij mig a'q. mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa zyrug yem Bov Fiag taaib.
20.29: zwavj myenb hiuq tu'q aa-lon taig mig a'q, i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug weig ninb Raub Eyemq faab zyepg Nxi.
20.19: i-saa-laa-en myenb tau, “yia Bua Kuvj kan tomb Jauq mivb. sij kxvq yia Bua fai yia Bua Eei scvb Kuq hopq meib Bua Eei uam, yia Bua zyrug Zwrtq Eaanb maaid pun. yia Bua Kuvj Toq yavb Jauq Jiaj Navq. kanb Euvg maiq Toq a'q.”
20.17: Toq pun yia Bua Jiaj meib Eei teib puv. yia Bua maiq yavb Deig, maiq yavb a'vung Wivj Jiaj, yaag maiq hopq haiq nxm uamb Kwrtq Eei uam. yia Bua Kuvj yavb huvb tiaj Eei tomb Jauq mivb Navq, maiq mivb zaaij yaag maiq mivb Byaaug Tauj Jiaj Jomg meib Eei kapg Jaaij.”
20.27: mo-se ei Jyenq zyruq Eei waag zruj. ninb Bua pua taub txv Jyenq zwavj myenb faauj ho-aa Bov.
20.11: mo-se zyrug suv puad, lovg ninb Eei pyaab Byaag Bx'q i pyaaq la'pyeiq. uam pctq Zwrtq Zamq haig. zwavj myenb Zauj ninb Bua Eei scvb Kuq zyrug tu'q hopq uam a'q.
20.5: meib weig haiq tiug txb yia Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv Tauj naaiq nxm waaig haig Eei teib puv? yem naaiq maiq maaib Byaub, maiq maaib vovb Exj pyruq, maiq maaib a'vung Mei, maiq maaib zi'g lyrub pyruq. lyemb uam yaag maiq maaib hopq!”
20.9: mo-se zyrug mivb zx'q yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen uaq tiub pyaab Byaag taaib Navq zyruq Buaj ninb zruj nx.
20.16: mq paag yia Bua Qa'q heug zyruq, Toq ninb Tevj. ninb yaag haid mig a'q, zyrug Paaiq taub finb myenb txb yia Bua Zwrtq i-yipq taaib. “ib zang yia Bua yem naaiq meib Eei kapg Jaaij ka'Len, Kaa-Detg zivb.
20.4: meib weig haiq tiug txb zyruq Eei zwavj myenb taaib naaiq teib puvb Waav weig pun yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei scvb Kuq taig Revg?
20.10: mo-se Zauj aa-lon heug zwavj pc'g fivj taaib zunq yem uaq nxm la'pyeiq Eei Ra'Myen. mo-se zyrug kxvq Buaj ninb Bua, “meib Bua Hruq vcvg Eei myenb mwavj maa'b! yia Bua xij zu'g pun naaiq nxm la'pyeiq Zwrtq uam weig meib Bua fai?”
20.22: zwavj i-saa-laa-en myenb yem Kaa-Detg zivb Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj ho-aa Bov.
20.12: mq paag zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon, “weig zu'g meib Bua syenj yia maiq Tauj taaub Zivj maiq txv Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb Taaib yia weib Zivb Revg, meib Bua zyrug maiq tu'q txb naaiq teij zwavj myenb pia'g yia lcvd Zeij pun Eei teib puv.”
20.15: yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij mivb i-yipq teib puv yaag yem uaq laub Eei. i-yipq myenb zruj to'g yia Bua Zauj yia Bua Eei ovb Taaij.
20.13: naaiq teij uam ninb Bua heug me-li-Baa weig zu'g yem naaig i-saa-laa-en myenb Zauj zyruq Rcv Jaaj. yem uaq nxm txvj, zyruq yaag yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj piuj mevb ninb Zivb Revg.
20.1: yem zib Laaj, i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mivb Tauj sin teib puvb Waav, tivb Jyenq yem Kaa-Detg. mi-lyem yem naaig kwei seij yaag zavj Jyenq uaq.
20.26: cvj Jaiq aa-lon Eei zruj sai lwi taaib Tevj ninb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, zu'q Jyenq. aa-lon zyrug yem uaq taig, kwei seij mig a'q.”
20.25: xij zu'g txb aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, faauj ho-aa Bov.

24.18: e-Dom xij zu'g swei penj kanb taub Eei. ninb Eei winb wavq, sej-i, yaag xij zu'g myenb hivb. mq paag i-saa-laa-en myenb xij henq Jyenq faauj.
24.8: “Tinb huvb txb ninb Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv, ninb Bua maaib Qa'q Navq Yiab vovb nx. ninb Bua na'q Revg winb wavq Eei kua'q, wrtq winb wavq Eei Buvq nauq Revg, lovg fxvb Zav pwrnq Tov ninb Bua.
24.3: ninb zyrug trug naaiq teij waag, “naaiq se Be-o Eei txn, Baa-laa-am, trug Eei waag. se mziv Tov Eei myenb trug waag kxvq,
24.21: ninb cvj pwatg Ke-nai myenb zyrug trug waag kxvq, “meib yem Eei txvj se wrnq haig, meib Eei laud yem Bcvb vaamb ka'Euad.
24.14: ib zang yia Rwrnj yia Eei pwrnb fivj myenb uaq mq paag taaib maa'b! yia Buaj meib Ga'haaq hivq naaiq fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb xij Navq haiq nx zruj pun meib Eei pc'g fivj.”
24.23: Baa-laa-am cvj trug waag kxvq, “Kruq aaq lo'b! Tinb huvb Navq naaiq zruj, haiq taub haib maaib mcvg zyavb?
24.6: “meib Bua Navq hxvd Zwrtq mivb Javq Eei nx, Navq yem Daaib Len Eei Wivj. Navq zyruq zwavj Eei aa-lo miab Daav, Navq yem uamb Len Eei sij-Daa zovb Dyavj.
24.2: pwatg i-saa-laa-en myenb ziuj yetg fivj yetg fivj Zxv Dopg liub yem ninb Bua Eei Zyavq. Tinb huvb Eei sivj livb Fiag taaib yem Jyenq ninb,
24.20: yem Baa-laa-am pwatg hing yaavb Eei sig ninb pwatg aa-maa-lekq myenb zyrug trug naaiq teij waag, “yem maang kua'q aa-maa-lekq zruj ta'yetq, mq paag setq mweid ninb zuvq zu'g paaig Revg.”
24.24: maaib myenb Rcv Ravq yem Kitq-Tim kua'q taaib zruj pun atg-su Zauj e-Be zu'g paaig, mq paag ninb Bua kanb yaag xij zu'g myetg.”
24.7: uam xij lyrug Zwrtq ninb Bua Eei Tovq, ninb Bua Eei zeib fun xij yem maaib uam Zamq Eei txvj. “ninb Bua Eei huvb xij kaub Lo Jiaj aa-kakg huvb, ninb Bua Eei kua'q yaag xij tu'q Favb laavg.
24.19: maaib taub yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun xij Zwrtq taaib kunq. ninb xij myetg Revg yem zivb Bx'q liud Jaaj zevg Fiag Eei myenb.”
24.17: “yia pwatg ninb mq paag maiq zeid ib zang. yia mavg ninb mq paag maiq zeid fatq Eei. xij maaib nxm Leij yem yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun Zwrtq taaib, maaib huvb Eei Daavb vau yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq. ninb xij Bx'q huq mo-apg myenb Eei pyxvb, yaag paaig Revg setq Eei zeib fun.
24.11: ib zang meib pyauj Rwrnj meib Eei txvj a'q. yia kxvq xij pun zivb Eeig Lo Eei, mq paag zyruq tavq Jyenq pun meib maiq tu'q zipq.”
24.5: “o yaa-Kopq Eei zeib fun aag, meib Bua Eei Dopg liub Rweig haig. o i-saa-laa-en myenb aag, meib Bua Eei Zyavq za'kevb Kub mavg.
24.9: ninb Bua Baapq Fiag pweij Jyenq Navq syenb kruq, yaag Navq syenb Eeid, haiq taub kaamq mivb heug ninb Bua Jiad sin? “haiq taub pwav waag meib Bua, Toq pun uaq taub tu'q fu'q. haiq taub zyruj meib Bua, Toq pun uaq taub zu'g zyruj.”
24.16: tovb haid Tinb huvb Eei waag uaq taub trug Eei waag, se yem Lav Jiaj uaq taub pun hiuq Eei Jauq. yia Eei mziv Tov haib mavg tu'q pwatg nrnb Jiaj Eei Tinb huvb hing yaavb Eei sig.

28.18: taaub Nxi xij zu'g kapq zunq zruj leib paaij yaag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg Nxib Nxi zruj Eei kov.

7.83: ninb Bua Navq naaiq nx yetg fivj yetg fivj Eei txb ka'naaiq taaib fovg hxg. ta'yetq Nxi yu-Daa fivj am-mi-naa-Dapg Eei txn, naa-son ta'Eeig Nxi itg-saaj-Kaa fivj zu-aa Eei txn, ne-Tan-en ta'faam Nxi sej-Bu-lun fivj he-lon Eei txn, e-li-apg ta'feij Nxi lu-Ben fivj se-De-e Eei txn, e-li-su ta'Mmd Nxi si-me-on fivj suj-li-satq-Dai Eei txn, se-lu-mi-en ta'lua'g Nxi kaatg fivj De-u-en Eei txn, e-li-yaa-saapg ta'Zyetq Nxi e-faa-im fivj am-mi-hutq Eei txn, e-li-saa-maa ta'petq Nxi maa-natq-sej fivj pe-Daa-su Eei txn, kaa-maa-li-en ta'Juaq Nxi Ben-yaa-min fivj ki-De-o-ni Eei txn, aa-Bi-Dan ta'zyepg Nxi Daan fivj am-mi-Qatq-Dai Eei txn, aa-hi-ye-se zyepg yetq uaq Nxi aa-se fivj o-Kaan Eei txn, paa-ki-en zyepg Eeig uaq Nxi napq-Taa-li fivj e-nan Eei txn, aa-hi-laa taub taub txb taaib fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq fib Navq Revg. yetg taub yetg taub Eei maaib Navq naaiq. maaib yetg nxm Eaanb pyenb, Niab taaub faab zyepg petq luvd, maaib yetg nxm Eaanb Rxmg, Niab taaub Eig zyepg yetq luvd, ziuj sivj ting tivg taaib Eei Niab taaub. i nxm zuvq zaavb pwavq zxpg Jyenq yrub Eei Bwrnb mwrng weig zruj fovg hxg ziag Eei laavb zi'g. cvj maaib nxm Jyemb huvb lrub, Niab taaub faamb luvd, zaavb pwavq huv. cvj maaib yetg taub vovb kruq Zaan, yetg taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, Zauj yetg taub txij Havj Eei pa'ki yuvb txn weig zruj puaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq. maaib taub yuvb kruq weig ziag fi'q zwid, maaib i taub vovb kruq, pyaa taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, pyaa taub yuvb kruq Zauj pyaa taub txij Havj Eei pa'ki yuvb kruq ziag weig Jiu Tov.
7.3: ninb Bua txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq Eei zivb Eeig maaib Ju'q Jaaj vovb Zia komq Jyenq liub Eei, Zauj zyepg Eeig taub yavb vovb kruq. i taub pyeiq zeiq fovg hxg yetg Jaaj vovb Zia. yetg taub pyeiq zeiq fovg hxg yetg taub vovb. naaiq teij ka'naaiq ninb Bua txb Tauj zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub taaib fovg hxg.

7.8: cvj zx'q pyei Jaaj Zia Zauj Yetg taub vovb pun me-laa-li myenb ziuj ninb Bua zruj Eei kov Qyemj lovg Eei. ninb Bua yetg zuvq yem aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, i-Taa-maa, Eei puab Diaq.
7.89: mo-se pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Zauj zyruq kxvq waag uaq zang, ninb haid Qiaj yem lcvd vcvg waag Eei faavb Gaaij, uaq teij i taub Ke-lu-Bim Bu'Dovj, Zauj ninb kxvq waag.

29.16: cvj lovg taub yuvb kruq ziag weig fi'q zwid. Zxg maaib Nxib Nxi puaq Eei Zauj Jyenq yetg Fiag ziag Eei laavb zi'g Zauj Ziaq ziag Eei a'vung tiuq.

29.1: “+‘Zyetq Laaj, scvb yetq, xij zu'g kapq zunq zruj leib paaij, yaag maiq tuvq zruj haiq Euvg Nxib Nxi zruj Eei kov. naaiq se meib Bua pyomq Ratg Eei Nxi.

19.18: xij zu'g maaib taub maiq maaib wij Eei myenb lovg hu-sopg miaq zyemj uaq nxm pcvb Eei uam fu'q Dopg liub Zauj Dopg liub ka'Euad Eei Jaab txvj Zauj yem uaq Eei myenb. ninb yaag xij zu'g fu'q mua'q zu'g Janb taig Eei Buvq, fai Janb taig zruq, fai zu'g Ru'g Daauq taij Eei, fai myenb kanb taig Eei uaq teij myenb.
19.8: puaq vovb Eeid Eei myenb yaag xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj kanb Eei sin yaag fib Navq Eei maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
19.3: xij zu'g Jiu pun e-le-aa-saa sai myenb. yaag xij zu'g txb Zwrtq zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq pun myenb txv Jyenq e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Eei Ra'Myen taij.
19.21: naaiq se ninb Bua xij zu'g yetg liud kan Eei leid. “Tevj myenb fu'q saaj wij Eei uam uaq laanb myenb yaag xij zu'g Roj kanb Eei lwib hruj. haiq taub mua'q zu'g saaj wij Eei uam, uaq taub zyrug maaib wij Tauj Mwavj.
19.14: “naaiq se myenb yem Dopg liub ka'Euad taig Eei leid. myenb taig yem Dopg liub ka'Euad, haiq taub pia'g Dopg liub Zauj yem Dopg liub Eei myenb zyrug maaib wij siag Nxi.
19.6: sai myenb xij zu'g cvj zx'q teij sij-Daa zovb Dyavj Zauj hu-sopg miaq, cvj Zauj tiub pa'ki swib si'q, zxi pia'g puaq vovb Eei trud ka'Euad.
19.2: “ziuj zyruq Fiag Eei livg xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb txb taub vovb Eeib si'q taaib pun meib, se maiq waaig favj, maiq maaib txvj Gemb, yaag maiq kaad Jiaj Dyavb kaad Eei vovb.
19.20: “haiq taub maiq saaj kanb Eei wij, uaq taub yem zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj xij zu'g Pai kwavg, weig zu'g ninb pun zyruq Eei sivj ting maaib wij. ninb maiq tu'q saaj wij Eei uam fu'q ninb, ninb zyrug maaib wij a'q.
19.7: Ga'haaq sai myenb xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj liud kanb Eei sin Zivj taaib pia'g Dopg liub Zyavq. mq paag ninb Zxg maaib wij Tauj luvb Mwavj.
19.19: Tauj ta'faam Nxi Zauj ta'Zyetq Nxi, maiq maaib wij Eei myenb xij zu'g lovg naaiq teij uam fu'q maaib wij Eei myenb. ta'Zyetq Nxi xij zu'g Tevj ninb saaj wij. uaq laanb myenb yaag xij zu'g Roj lwib hruj, lovg uam Raauj sin. Tauj Mwavj ninb zyrug Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij a'q.
19.17: “weig maaib wij Eei myenb, xij zu'g zx'q teij puaq weig Raauj zwid uaq taub vovb Eeid Eei saaiq, tapq Jyenq pcvb, cvj zaavb uamb taaib tapq Jyenq.
19.11: “haiq taub mua'q zu'g Janb taig Eei sei zyrug maaib wij pwavq siag Nxi.
19.5: xij zu'g maaib taub myenb yem sai myenb Eei Ra'Myen puaq naaiq taub vovb. lyemb Dopq, xq, Ryaamq Zauj Jaavb xij zu'g puaq Revg.
19.9: “xij zu'g maaib taub maiq maaib wij Eei myenb syru naaiq taub vovb Eei saaiq, an Jyenq ka'Eiag Dopg liub Zyavq, Zivb Revg, maiq maaib wij Eei txvj. xij zu'g weig i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb lyrub Jyenq zruj saaj wij Eei uam Raauj zwid.
19.16: “haiq taub yem uaq naab haiq Dau yaag mua'q zu'g Janb taig Eei sei, tovb zu'g Ru'g Daauq taij Eei, fai myenb kanb taig, fai Janb taig Eei Buvq, fai Janb taig zruq, uaq taub zyrug maaib wij siag Nxi.
19.4: e-le-aa-saa zyrug lovg puab Do'q Zo'q vovb Eeid Ryaamq cvj huvj mivb wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Ra'Myen mcvj Tiu siag Rung.
19.10: syru vovb Eeid Eei saaiq uaq laanb myenb yaag xij zu'g Roj ninb Eei lwib hruj. ninb fib Navq Eei maaib wij Tauj luvb Mwavj. naaiq se weig i-saa-laa-en myenb Zauj yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj Eei kanb fivj myenb yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.

17.3: yem le-wi fivj Eei pyaab Byaag xij zu'g fiaq aa-lon Eei Buaj. fivb fivj xij zu'g weig ovb Taaij lyepg uaq fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq maaib yetg tiub pyaab Byaag.
