17.4: txb naaiq teij pyaab Byaag pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub ka'Euad, an Jyenq lcvd vcvg waag faav Ra'Myen mcvj, tovb yia Zauj meib Bua kapq zunq Eei txvj.
17.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb ziuj ovb Taaij Bua lyepg taaib Eei fivj, yetg fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq xij zu'g txb yetg tiub pyaab Byaag taaib, yetg zuvq maaib zyepg Eeig tiub. kx'g myenb xij zu'g fiaq kx'g myenb Eei Buaj yem kx'g myenb Eei pyaab Byaag.
17.6: mo-se zyrug Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb. ninb Bua Eei pyeiq zeiq zyrug zx'q pyaab Byaag, ziuj ovb Taaij Bua lyepg Eei fivj, mrud fivj, yetg fivj yetg tiub. yetg zuvq maaib zyepg Eeig tiub. aa-lon Eei pyaab Byaag yaag tovb uaq teij Eei yetg tiub.
17.13: haiq taub lyemb mivb nitq fatq zyruq Eei Dopg liub zuvq xij zu'g taig a'q. yia Bua yetg zuvq xij zu'g taig Revg fai?”
17.12: i-saa-laa-en myenb kxvq Buaj mo-se, “yia Bua zuvq xij zu'g taig a'q. yia Bua zu'g myetg Revg, xij zu'g myetg Revg aaq lo'b!
17.11: mo-se zyrug ziuj zyruq Eei waag zruj Revg.
17.10: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “txb aa-lon Eei pyaab Byaag Rwrnj, an Jyenq lcvd vcvg waag faav Eei Ra'Myen zruj Javb hog pun uaq teij vcvg yia Eei myenb. Navq naaiq zyrug pun ninb Bua tivb Fiag, maiq vopq yia, ninb Bua Zivj taaib maiq zu'g taig.”

31.34: lxb, Ju'q waang yetg Zin taub,

31.7: ninb Bua ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei waag Bx'q mi-Dyen myenb, yaag taij Revg ninb Bua Eei taub taub mJavg txn.
31.17: weig naaiq xij zu'g taij Revg naaiq teij yetg zuvq txn Zauj pweij Jiaj mJavg txn Eei msia'q txn.
31.49: kxvq Buaj ninb, “yia Bua, meib Eei pru, saauq Revg yem yia Bua Eei puab Diaq Eei pcv, yaag maiq zitg yetg taub.
31.11: ninb Bua zx'q Revg ninb Bua Zaavq taaib luq taaib Eei ka'naaiq, lyemb myenb, lyemb scvb Kuq,
31.33: vovb, siag waang i Zin taub,
31.16: se tovb naaiq teij msia'q txn mwavj Baa-laa-am Eei waag, yem pe-o uaq zang txb i-saa-laa-en myenb leib Tinb huvb zyrug maaib tomb wrnb pcvg hxig zyruq Eei myenb.
31.40: myenb, tu'q yetg waang Ju'q Zin taub. fuvj pun penj zyruq Eei pwrng maaib faab zyepg Eeig taub.
31.37: fuvj pun penj zyruq Eei pwrng maaib lua'g pc'q Zyetq zyepg Mmd taub.
31.4: fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb, yetg fivj xij zu'g Paaiq yetg Zin taub.”
31.51: mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb zyrug zipq ninb Bua Jiu pun Eei Jyem, se taaq taaib Eei syrub setq.
31.12: txb Tauj mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj i-saa-laa-en zwavj myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq uaq, yem mo-apg Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib Len, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang.
31.46: myenb, yetg waang Ju'q Zin taub.
31.13: mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj zwavj myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq Zwrtq Dopg liub Zyavq mivb pwavb ninb Bua.
31.26: “meib Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj pc'g fivj Eei zwavj pyeiq zeiq xij zu'g saauq Revg Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq, lyemb myenb lyemb scvb Kuq.
31.28: mivb Bx'q Jaaj Eei pcv tu'q Eei pwrng, maiq kunq myenb, vovb, lxb, pa'ki yuvb fai yuvb, Mmd pc'q taub xij zu'g mc'q Zwrtq taub weig fuvj pun zyruq.
31.54: mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb zyrug zipq kunq yetg Zin taub pcv Zauj yetg pc'q taub pcv Eei pyeiq Jiu pun Eei Jyem, txb pia'g wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub an Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen weig pun zyruq Javj i-saa-laa-en myenb.

31.9: i-saa-laa-en myenb zx'q mi-Dyen msia'q txn Zauj fu'Jweiq yaag kwaatq Revg mi-Dyen myenb Eei scvb Kuq, vovb kwanb yuvb kwanb, yaag luq Revg ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq.
31.32: Zib Zwrtq pcv kanb lovg Eei, Zaavq taaib zevg Fiag Eei pa'ki yuvb maaib Ju'q sinj siag waang pyaa Zin taub,
31.21: e-le-aa-saa sai myenb yaag Buaj mivb Bx'q Jaaj Rwrnj taaib Eei pcv, “naaiq se ziuj zyruq Jiu pun mo-se Eei leid.
31.23: ta'faanb haib zu'g tu'q trud Eei yetg zuvq xij zu'g Jiaj trud, zyrug Zivb Revg a'q. mq paag Zxg xij zu'g lovg saaj wij Eei uam saaj. zu'g maiq tu'q trud Eei, xij zu'g Jiaj uam.
31.6: mo-se zyrug Paaiq ninb Bua Zwrtq mivb Bx'q Jaaj, yetg fivj yetg Zin taub. cvj maaib e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Eei txn, fi-ne-hatg, txb Jyenq sivj ting Eei Jaab sig yaag nanq Jyenq Ratg pyomq weig zruj Javb hog.
31.44: vovb, pua waang Ju'q Zin taub,
31.20: yaag xij zu'g saaj teib teij lwib hruj Zauj yetg zuvq lovg Dopq, yuvb pyei fai Dyavj zruj taaib Eei ka'naaiq.”
31.5: Navq naaig, mrud fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb kinq Zwrtq yetg Zin taub. yetg zuvq maaib yetg waang i Zin taub txb Jyenq Bx'q Jaaj Eei ua'g king.
31.53: (naaiq teij Bx'q Jaaj Eei pcv, kx'g myenb Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq kx'g myenb kanb lovg.)
31.19: “ta'faanb taij myenb fai mua'q zu'g Janb taig uaq teij, xij zu'g yem ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq pwavq siag Nxi. ta'faam Nxi Zauj ta'Zyetq Nxi xij zu'g saaj Revg kanb Eei wij Zauj Zaavq taaib uaq teij myenb Eei wij.
31.38: vovb, tu'q pua waang Ju'q Zin taub. fuvj pun penj zyruq Eei pwrng maaib Zyetq zyepg Eeig taub.
31.31: mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb zyrug ei Jyenq zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei waag zruj.
31.52: kunq yetg Zin taub pcv Zauj yetg pc'q taub pcv Eei pcvb pyeiq Jiu pun mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa weib fovg hxg pun zyruq, Eei yetg zuvq Jyem, Ryav taaib maaib yetg pc'q zyepg Juaq Jxib.
31.27: xij zu'g pun Gxi zruj i kruq. pun yetg kruq mivb Bx'q Jaaj Eei pcv. pun yetg kruq zwavj myenb.
31.41: mo-se zx'q mc'q taaib fuvj pun zyruq Eei pwrng Jiu pun e-le-aa-saa sai myenb ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se Eei waag.
31.39: lxb, tu'q pua waang Mmd pc'q taub. fuvj pun penj zyruq Eei pwrng maaib lua'g zyepg yetq taub.
31.47: ziuj zyruq Eei waag, yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pwrng, lyemb myenb, lyemb scvb Kuq, Mmd zyepg taub mc'q Zwrtq taub Jiu pun le-wi myenb, tovb kruj zavg zyruq Eei Dopg liub Eei myenb.
31.10: i-saa-laa-en myenb yaag puaq Revg mi-Dyen myenb Eei zivb Zauj yetg zuvq Dopg liub Zyavq.
31.22: Jyem, Eaanb, tovb si'q, Lia'q, yavb Tiag, Zauj Juvd,
31.42: mo-se zx'q mivb Bx'q Jaaj Zaavq taaib Eei ka'naaiq mc'q taaib pun yetg pwrng i-saa-laa-en myenb.
31.15: mo-se naaig ninb Bua, “meib Bua weig haiq tiug lyrub Jyenq naaiq teij msia'q txn Eei mcvg?
31.29: yem pcv Eei pwrng mc'q Zwrtq naaiq teij, xij zu'g Jiu pun e-le-aa-saa sai myenb penj zyruq Eei pwrng.
31.30: yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pwrng, lyemb myenb, vovb, lxb, pa'ki yuvb, yuvb Zauj Euvb Euvg scvb Kuq, Mmd zyepg taub xij zu'g mc'q Zwrtq yetg taub pun le-wi myenb, tovb kruj zyruq Eei Dopg liub Eei myenb.”

30.3: “sij kxvq haiq taub sia'q Zxg yem Jyenq ninb Eei tia Eei pyauq uaq zang lcvd vcvg waag pun zyruq fai hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg,
30.8: mq paag sij kxvq ninb Eei Goj haid Eei zyavb hog laanb Jyenq, maiq pun ninb zruj, ninb lcvd Eei fai hruq Eei, maiq kunq za'kevb lcvd fai la'kwaib lcvd Eei waag, yetg zuvq zyrug paag mig a'q. zyruq yaag xij kwavg pun ninb.
30.9: “haiq taub aub kwaaq fai aub leib lcvd vcvg waag fai hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg, ninb xij zu'g ei Jyenq uaq teij waag zruj Revg.
30.7: ninb Eei Goj haid ninb Navq naaiq lcvd yaag maiq kxvq haiq Euvg nx, ninb lcvd Eei fai hruq Eei waag Zxg yem Eei.
30.5: mq paag sij kxvq ninb Eei tia yetq haid uaq zang laanb Jyenq, maiq pun ninb zruj, ninb lcvd Eei Zauj hruq Eei waag yetg zuvq zyrug paag mig a'q. zyruq zyrug kwavg pun ninb a'q, weig zu'g ninb Eei tia maiq Kavq pun ninb ei Jyenq zruj.
30.16: naaiq se zyruq Jiu pun mo-se Eei leid kxvq maiq maaib Jaa Eei sia'q Zxg yem tia Eei pyauq fai maaib Jaa Eei msia'q txn lcvd vcvg waag Eei Jauq.
30.14: mq paag sij kxvq Nxi Jiaj Nxi Goj maiq kxvq haiq Euvg, se funj tivg pun ninb ei ninb lcvd Eei waag zruj. weig zu'g Goj haid uaq Nxi yaag maiq kxvq haiq Euvg Zivj funj ninb tivg pun ninb Eei auq ei Jyenq zruj.
30.4: ninb Eei tia yetq haid Tauj ninb lcvd Eei fai hruq Eei waag yaag maiq kxvq haiq Euvg, ninb lcvd Eei Zauj hruq Eei Jrub Jruj waag zyrug yem Jyenq a'q.
30.2: sij kxvq haiq taub lcvd vcvg waag pun zyruq fai hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg, ninb yaag maiq tuvq pun ninb Eei waag Dxtq. xij zu'g ei Revg ninb lcvd Eei Jrub Jruj waag zruj.
30.6: “sij kxvq sia'q maiq kcvb txv Jaa Eei zyavb hog lcvd vcvg waag, maiq kunq za'kevb lcvd fai la'kwaib lcvd, fai ninb hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg, Ga'haaq ninb txv Jaa,
30.13: maiq kunq auq lcvd haiq Euvg fai hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg yaag zeid, ninb Eei Goj maaib leid tivg pun ninb ei Jyenq zruj fai maiq pun ninb zruj.
30.12: mq paag sij kxvq Goj yetq haid ninb Navq uaq nx lcvd yaag laanb Jyenq, maiq pun ninb ei Jyenq zruj, ninb lcvd Eei Zauj hruq Eei zyrug paag mig a'q. weig zu'g ninb Eei Goj laanb Jyenq maiq pun ninb zruj, zyruq zyrug kwavg pun ninb mig a'q.
30.15: sij kxvq Goj haid liud mq paag Ga'haaq Zivj taaib laanb Jyenq, maiq pun auq ei ninb lcvd Eei waag zruj, Goj kanb xij zu'g Daam auq Eei zwid.”
30.11: ninb Eei Goj haid yaag maiq kxvq haiq Euvg, maiq laanb ninb, ninb lcvd Eei Zauj hruq Eei yetg zuvq zyrug yem Eei.
30.1: mo-se kxvq Buaj fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq, “naaiq se zyruq Paaiq Eei waag.
30.10: “sij kxvq maaib Jaa Eei msia'q txn lcvd vcvg waag fai hruq kanb zruj yetg Euvg,

27.18: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “txb nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, taaib. ninb maaib sivj livb yem Hruq Eei. meib xij zu'g txb puad maan Jyenq ninb.
27.8: “Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb ‘sij kxvq maaib taub mJavg txn taig mig a'q, ninb yaag maiq maaib txn, xij zu'g zx'q ninb Ripg Eei pwrng Jiu pun ninb Eei sia'q Ripg.
27.3: “yia Bua Eei tia yem uaq teib puvb Waav taig mig a'q. ninb yaag maiq maaib txn. ninb maiq Zauj kan Ko-laa uaq teij kapq zunq vcvg zyruq. ninb taig se weig ninb kanb Eei zwid.
27.21: ninb xij zu'g sruq Jyenq e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Eei Ra'Myen, sai myenb zyrug yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen lovg u-lim naaig weig Tevj tivg Navq haiq nx zruj. yo-su-waa Zauj i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb xij zu'g ei Jyenq e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Eei waag pia'g Zwrtq.”
27.14: weig zu'g yem sin teib puvb Waav, uam Zwrtq Eei txvj, zwavj myenb vcvg yia uaq zang, meib Bua i taub maiq ei Jyenq yia Buaj Eei waag txv zwavj pun myenb Taaib yia Zivb Revg.” (naaiq nxm uam Zwrtq Eei txvj se me-li-Baa uam, yem sin teib puvb Waav, Kaa-Detg teig.)
27.23: ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, mo-se yaag txb puad maan Jyenq yo-su-waa Paaiq ninb.
27.2: naaiq teij pyaa muab sia'q mivb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, sruq Jyenq mo-se Zauj e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj zwavj pyeiq zeiq Zauj kapq zunq Eei zwavj myenb Eei Ra'Myen kxvq,
27.20: xij zu'g Jiu teij meib Eei hatg maad pun ninb weig pun i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb mwavj ninb Eei waag.
27.7: “sej-lo-fe-hatg Eei sia'q kxvq tu'q hxpg Eei. meib zuvq xij zu'g yem ninb Bua Eei tia Eei muab txig Bu'Dovj Paaiq Dau pun ninb Bua Ripg. zx'q ninb Bua Eei tia Ripg Eei pwrng Jiu pun ninb Bua.
27.19: yaag pun ninb sruq Jyenq e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj kapq zunq Eei zwavj myenb Eei Ra'Myen, txv Jyenq ninb Bua Paaiq ninb.
27.17: pun ninb haib yem ninb Bua Eei Ra'Myen pia'g pia'g Zwrtg Zwrtq, yaag haib txb ninb Bua pia'g Zwrtq, weig pun zyruq Eei pc'g fivj maiq Navq maiq maaib zyruq kruj Eei pa'ki yuvb kwanb nx.”
27.11: sij kxvq ninb Eei tia maiq maaib kxj, maiq maaib yrud, xij zu'g zx'q ninb Ripg Eei pwrng Jiu pun Zauj ninb Jwavg fivj kaub Zyen Jiaj uaq taub, penj uaq taub Ripg Eei pwrng. naaiq se i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei leib latg Zauj leid ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se nx.’+”
27.5: mo-se zyrug txb ninb Bua Eei Jaub lrug Buaj zyruq.
27.9: sij kxvq ninb maiq maaib sia'q, xij zu'g zx'q ninb Ripg Eei pwrng Jiu pun ninb Eei kxj fai yrud Ripg.
27.16: “zyruq, maang myenb Eei livb wrnb Eei Tinb huvb aag, Toq xn taub myenb kunq naaiq teij zwavj myenb,
27.4: laaij yia Bua Eei tia maiq maaib txn, weig haiq tiug pun ninb Eei Buaj yem ninb Eei fivj Dxtq mivb? Toq pun yia Bua yem yia Bua Eei Zyenb Ze'q Bu'Dovj maaib yia Bua Ripg Eei pwrng maa'b!”
27.10: sij kxvq maiq maaib kxj, maiq maaib yrud, xij zu'g Jiu pun ninb Eei pc'q fai tia Eei yrud Ripg.
27.22: mo-se ei Jyenq zyruq Buaj Eei waag zruj. ninb txb yo-su-waa taaib pun ninb sruq Jyenq e-le-aa-saa sai myenb Zauj kapq zunq Eei zwavj myenb Eei Ra'Myen.
27.12: zyruq Buaj mo-se, “xij zu'g faauj naaiq aa-Baa-lim keb zxv mavg yia Jiu pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei teib puv.
27.13: mavg liud, Ga'haaq xij zu'g kwei seij a'q, Navq meib Eei kxj aa-lon uaq nx.
27.1: sej-lo-fe-hatg Eei pyaa taub sia'q Eei Buaj maaib Navq naaiq, maa-haa-laa, no-yaa, hokq-laa, min-Kaa Zauj Ti-laa-saa. sej-lo-fe-hatg se he-fe Eei txn, he-fe se ki-le-aatg Eei txn, ki-le-aatg se maa-Ki-le Eei txn, maa-Ki-le se maa-natq-sej Eei txn, zruj maa-natq-sej fivj. maa-natq-sej zruj yo-sepq Eei txn.

11.18: “xij zu'g Buaj pc'g fivj, ‘meib Bua xij zu'g saaj Revg wij, liug leid zyavj weig Fav Nxi, meib Bua zyrug tu'q xq Eang a'q. weig zu'g meib Bua Eyemq, zyruq yaag haid mig a'q. meib Bua kxvq, “feij tu'q yia Bua maaib xq Eang. yem i-yipq teib puv yia Bua zuvq tu'q kaub lovj.” weig naaiq zyruq xij pun xq meib Bua Eang, meib Bua zyrug tu'q Eang a'q.
11.8: pc'g fivj Zwrtq mivb Jiaj naaiq Jiaj uaq syru taaib mxg fai zov, cvj tapq Zcv zruq fai zruj penj Fuaq yetg nxm, yetg nxm Eei. mweij se Navq yetg Euvg ka'naaiq zxpg Jyenq ka'lanq yrub nx.
11.33: nx'g xq Zxg yem ninb Bua Eei Eaab Bu'Dovj, maiq kcvb tu'q Riug, zyruq za'kevb! Qiaj Jiad haig zwavj myenb, zyrug pun putq tomb wrnb pcvg taij ninb Bua.
11.3: uaq nxm txvj zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug Taa-Be-laa, weig zu'g yem uaq zyruq Eei trud zia'g Jyenq ninb Bua Bu'Dovj.
11.32: uaq Nxi myenb Zwrtq mivb zyavb Nxi zyavb mwrnd zx'q nx'g Bunb, cvj zx'q Tauj ta'Eeig Nxi Mwavj. zxij zo'g yetg taub myenb tu'q yetg pc'q Tovq. syru taaib ninb Bua yaag Pwi pwavq Dopg liub Zyavq.
11.21: mo-se kxvq, “Zauj yia yavb Jauq Eei mJavg txn maaib Ju'q sinj taub. zyruq yaag kxvq yia xij pun xq ninb Bua Eang kauj yetg Laaj Eia'g.
11.35: pc'g fivj yem Kipg-lotq-hatg-taa-aa-waa Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj haa-se-lotq zyrug yem naaig a'q.
11.14: yia kanb Du'g laanb myenb Navq, Daam maiq tovd naaiq teij myenb Zamq. yia haid pa'la'g Niaq haig.
11.23: zyruq tau mo-se, “zyruq Eei puad navq haig fai? ib zang meib xij tu'q pwatg yia Zauj meib kxvq Eei waag weig meib Zwrtq taaib zyen fai maiq zyen.”
11.6: ib zang haid sin zavg mau Revg, maiq maaib Qa'q a'q. Zwrtq liud naaiq maa-naa, maiq maaib kanb Euvg mavg.”
11.34: uaq nxm txvj zyrug Zwrtq Buaj heug Kipg-lotq-hatg-taa-aa-waa, weig zu'g uaq nxm txvj ninb Bua pyopq Zei kanb Euvg ka'naaiq uaq teij yetg zuvq myenb.
11.2: pc'g fivj Qa'q heug mo-se Tevj. mo-se tauj kauj Toq zyruq, trud zyrug taig mig a'q.
11.20: Eang Tauj pwavq yetg Laaj Eia'g, Tauj xq zuvq yavb meib Bua Eei Ba'zxvb Kwrtq pctq Zwrtq, meib Bua yaag yruj Revg a'q. weig zu'g meib Bua Gemb zyruq, tovb yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj uaq taub, yaag txv Jyenq zyruq Eyemq Jyenq kxvq, “yia Bua weig haiq tiug Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv?”+’+”
11.24: mo-se zyrug Zwrtq mivb zyav zyruq Eei waag Buaj pc'g fivj. ninb txb Zyetq zyepg taub ninb Bua Eei myenb koj taaib kapq zunq pun ninb Bua sruq Jyenq Wiv kxmj wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub.
11.28: nun Eei txn, yo-su-waa, yem ninb lunj Eei zyavb hog zruj mo-se Eei pxvb puad myenb. yo-su-waa kxvq, “yia Eei zyruq, mo-se aa'b! tavq Jyenq ninb Bua maa'b!”
11.7: maa-naa se Navq yenb si Eim, setq zeiq Navq Dyavb zuv.
11.29: mq paag mo-se tau, “meib weig yia mweig Jia'q fai? feij tu'q zyruq Eei myenb yetg zuvq haib zruj trug waag myenb. yaag feij tu'q zyruq pun ninb Eei sivj livb yem ninb Bua yetg zuvq.”
11.19: maiq taan Eang yetg Nxi Navq, fai i Nxi, fai pyaa Nxi, fai zyepg Nxi, fai Eig zyepg Nxi.
11.17: yia zyrug Fiag taaib Zauj meib yem naaig kxvq waag. yia xij zx'q teij yem meib uaq taub sivj livb pun yem ninb Bua. ninb Bua zyrug Tevj meib Daam naaiq teij myenb weig pun meib kanb Du'g taub Navq maiq zu'g Daam Niaq.
11.31: zyruq pun Ryaauj pwrng nx'g Bunb yem Kxiq uaq puv taaib Fiag Wiv kxmj Dopg liub Zyavq, zuvq Tauj puvb puv Zwrtq mivb yetg Nxi Eei Jauq. nx'g Daij Jyenq Daub peib kub vwaaig i Dx'g Lav.
11.30: mo-se Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei myenb koj zyrug Rwrnj Dopg liub Zyavq mig a'q.
11.27: maaib taub myenb lunj myenb Tiuj Jyenq mivb Buaj mo-se, “en-Daatg Zauj me-Daatg yem uaq Zyavq trug zyruq Eei waag cj!”
11.11: mo-se kxvq Buaj zyruq, “zyruq weig haiq tiug pun yia, meib Eei pru, zu'g Dovg naaiq Kruq? yia zruj haiq Euvg maiq hxpg meib Eei Hruq meib Zivj taaib zx'q naaiq teij myenb pun yia Daam Dovg naaiq Niaq?
11.5: Javj zu'g yem i-yipq teib puv uaq zang tu'q Eang Eei Byaud yaag maiq zu'g Dxtq Eaanb. yaag Javj zu'g kwaab uam, kwaab tomj, Janb Kc'q funj, Zov Zauj funj.
11.9: luvb mwrnd zang Byuvb swiq Fiag Dopg liub Zyavq Eei zyavb hog, maa-naa yaag Fiag a'q.
11.16: zyruq Buaj mo-se, “xij zu'g heug Zyetq zyepg taub i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei myenb koj, tovb meib hiuq tu'q yem pc'g fivj Bu'Dovj zruj myenb koj yaag zruj Jyen uaq teij. txb ninb Bua taaib Tauj wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub pun ninb Bua Zauj meib sruq Jyenq naaig.
11.4: maaib teij Janj zxpg Jyenq i-saa-laa-en myenb mivb yaag Jiad kxn Zei xij Eang kanb Euvg ka'naaiq. lyemb i-saa-laa-en myenb cvj Eyemq Jyenq kxvq, “feij tu'q yia Bua maaib xq Eang.
11.10: mo-se haid pwrnb pwrng myenb, kx'g myenb yem kx'g myenb Eei Dopg liub kcvb Daavg Eyemq. zyruq zyrug Qiaj Jiad! haig a'q. mo-se yaag maiq a'Neiq ninb Bua.
11.22: zx'q yuvb kwanb, vovb kwanb, taij pun ninb Bua maaib kauj Eei fai? zx'q Revg yetg zuvq Kxiq Eei Byaud maaib kauj ninb Bua Eang fai?”
11.12: naaiq teij zwavj myenb yia kanb maaib taaib fai? se yia kanb yuvd taaib fai? zyruq weig haiq tiug heug yia Lxpq Jyenq ninb Bua Navq maa Lxpq Jyenq hopq Exj Eei kub vwaad nx, txb mivb Tauj meib lcvd Jiad vcvg waag xij pun ninb Bua Eei ovb Taaij uaq nxm teib puv?
11.15: sij kxvq zyruq xij Navq naaiq nx zruj pun yia, yaag sij kxvq zyruq pwavq eij yia, Toq pun yia ib zang zu'g taig, yia zyrug maiq zu'g pwatg yia kanb Eei Krub zivb.”
11.13: yia xij zu'g mivb haaij tu'q xq kauj pun naaiq teij zwavj myenb Eang? ninb Bua txv Jyenq yia Eyemq Jyenq kxvq, ‘pun xq yia Bua Eang maa'b!’
11.1: zwavj pc'g fivj vopq ninb Bua zu'g tiaq Eei Kruq naang. zyruq yaag haid mig a'q, zyrug Qiaj Jiad haig, puvj trud Fiag taaib yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj zia'g Jyenq. Dopg liub Zyavq ka'Len maaib teij txvj zuvq puaq Qwi Revg.
11.26: mq paag maaib i taub myenb, Buaj heug en-Daatg Zauj me-Daatg, Zxg yem uaq Dopg liub Zyavq. ninb Bua mtaaib Zauj uaq teij myenb koj faauj Buaj, mq paag maiq Zwrtq mivb yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub. sivj livb Zxg taaib zepq Jyenq ninb Bua, ninb Bua yaag yem uaq Zyavq ka'Euad trug zyruq Eei waag.
11.25: zyruq zyrug yem uaq txq Bwrnj Fiag taaib Zauj mo-se kxvq waag yaag zx'q teij yem mo-se uaq taub sivj livb, pun sivj livb yem uaq teij Zyetq zyepg taub myenb koj. sivj livb taaib zepq ninb Bua Eei sin Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua trug zyruq Eei waag. Ga'haaq maiq trug a'q.

5.18: sai myenb zyrug pun uaq taub msia'q txn sruq Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen yaag Jaiq Gxi ninb Eei Ba'pyei, cvj zx'q weig Rcvb pwav Eei Jauq, weig Javj myenb zruj txvg Eei sig uaq teij ziag Eei Bwrnq, pun ninb prub Jyenq. sai myenb kanb prub Jyenq hruq myenb Eei uamb im,
5.8: mq paag sij kxvq zu'g myenb zruj txvg uaq taub taig yaag maiq maaib Zyenb Ze'q lcvd uaq teij pwib Eei ka'naaiq, xij zu'g pun sai myenb weib fuvj pun zyruq. lyemb weig fi'q ninb Eei zwid uaq taub pa'ki yuvb kruq xij zu'g pun.
5.3: maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, xij zu'g hatg Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq weig maiq pun ninb Bua Eei Zyavq, tovb yia yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj Eei txvj, maaib wij.”
5.21: (Tauj naaiq nxm txvj, sai myenb pun naaiq taub msia'q txn ziuj ninb lcvd vcvg waag zu'g hruq. sai myenb cvj kxvq), “Toq zyruq pun meib Eei ka'sia omj, Zamb zwib Jaig, Eauj Revg, zyrug yem meib Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zruj zu'g myenb hruq, zu'g myenb zyruj Eei myenb.
5.14: yaag sij kxvq Goj Rcvb pwav, laaig ninb Eei auq maaib Jauq, auq yaag za'kevb zruj maiq Zivb Revg, xij zu'g txb ninb Eei auq mivb sai myenb uaq. fai sij kxvq Goj Rcvb pwav ninb Eei auq, laaig ninb Eei auq maaib Jauq, maiq kunq ninb Eei auq maiq maaib, ninb Zivb Revg Eei,
5.23: “+‘sai myenb zyrug fiaq naaiq teij hruq Eei waag yem srub Fung, cvj Raauj naaiq teij Ravg pia'g uaq teij uamb im.
5.6: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, maiq kunq mJavg msia'q, haiq taub zruj haiq Euvg txvg haiq taub, uaq taub maiq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj pun zyruq, ninb zyrug txvg mig a'q.
5.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb hatg putq komb huq pcvg Eei myenb Zauj sin zavg Zwrtq maiq hxpg zu'g Zwrtq Eei haiq Euvg uam, cvj Zauj laaij mua'q zu'g Janb taig maaib wij Eei myenb, Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq.
5.20: mq paag sij kxvq meib yem Goj Eei puab Diaq cvj yavb Pyen zaub Biag zyrug zruj maiq Zivb Revg, Zauj kanb taub mJavg txn pweij, maiq zeid kanb Eei Goj,”
5.24: ninb zyrug pun uaq taub msia'q txn hopq naaiq hruq Eei uamb im. uam zyrug pia'g ninb Eei sin hxig ninb tiaq Kruq.
5.28: mq paag sij kxvq uaq taub myenb Zivb Revg Eei, maiq yavb Pyen zaub Biag, zyrug pun Ziv ninb maiq txvg, yaag haib maaib kub vwaad Eei.
5.7: ninb xij zu'g Eyemg ninb zruj txvg Eei zwid, yaag xij zu'g zx'q ninb zruj txvg Eei yetg zuvq Twij Rwrnj pun ninb txvg uaq taub, cvj pwib pyaa kruq Eei yetg kruq.
5.29: “+‘naaiq se Rcvb pwav Eei leib latg, tovb msia'q txn yavb Pyen zaub Biag, yem Goj Eei puab Diaq mivb zruj maiq Zivb Revg Eei sig.
5.19: zyrug heug uaq taub msia'q txn lcvd Jiad vcvg waag. sai myenb kxvq Buaj ninb, “sij kxvq maiq maaib kanb taub mJavg txn Zauj meib pweij, meib yaag maiq yavb Pyen zaub Biag, yem Jyenq Goj Eei puab Diaq maiq zruj maiq Zivb Revg Eei sig, Toq pun naaiq teij hruq Eei uam hxig maiq zu'g meib.
5.17: zyrug zx'q teij Zivb Revg Eei uam taaib tapq niab pcvb, cvj Eau teij zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub Eei Dau Eei niab Buv tapq Jyenq.
5.31: Goj yaag maiq maaib zwid a'q. mq paag uaq taub msia'q txn ziuj ninb zruj Eei, xij zu'g tivg zwid.’+”
5.30: fai myenb laaig ninb Eei auq maaib Jauq zyrug hang ninb Eei auq. sai myenb xij zu'g pun uaq taub msia'q txn yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen yaag ei Jyenq naaiq Euvg leib latg Eei tiub tiub leid zruj.
5.27: sij kxvq ninb zruj maiq Zivb Revg Eei sig, maiq zyepg zua'q zruj pun ninb Eei Goj, yavb Pyen zaub Biag, ninb hopq liud naaiq teij uam pia'g mivb, ninb zyrug zu'g tiaq Kruq. ninb Eei ka'sia omj, Zamb zwib Jaig, Eauj Revg. ninb yaag yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zu'g myenb zyruj, zu'g myenb hruq.
5.9: i-saa-laa-en myenb txb taaib fuvj pun sai myenb Eei yetg zuvq Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq zyrug penj sai myenb Eei.
5.16: “+‘sai myenb zyrug txb naaiq taub msia'q txn taaib sruq Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen,
5.4: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Navq naaiq nx zruj, hatg ninb Bua Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq. zyruq Navq haiq nx Buaj mo-se, i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Navq uaq nx zruj.
5.10: kx'g myenb Eei Zivb Revg ka'naaiq se kx'g myenb kanb Eei, mq paag ninb fuvj haiq Euvg pun sai myenb, uaq Euvg zyrug penj sai myenb Eei.”
5.22: Toq pun naaiq teij hruq myenb Eei uamb im pia'g meib Eei ka'sia, pun meib Eei ka'sia omj, Zamb zwib Jaig, Eauj Revg.” “+‘uaq taub msia'q txn xij zu'g tau, “aa-men. aa-men.”
5.12: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘sij kxvq haiq taub myenb Eei auq yavb Pyen zaub Biag, maiq zyepg zua'q Eei zruj pun ninb Eei Goj,
5.15: Goj xij zu'g txb ninb Eei auq mivb sai myenb uaq. yaag xij zu'g weig ninb Eei auq txb Jyenq i mx'q Baa-li Byaub Bwrnq. yaag maiq tuvq toj ka'lanq yrub, maiq tuvq zx'q huv an kub vwaaig, weig zu'g naaiq teij ziag Eei ka'naaiq se weig Rcvb pwav Eei Jauq, weig Javj myenb zruj txvg Eei sig.
5.13: zyrug Zauj kanb taub mJavg txn pweij peig ninb Eei Goj, maiq kunq ninb zruj maiq Zivb Revg, maiq maaib haiq taub zruj zxvb zevj, (weig zu'g pweij Eei zyavb hog myenb zx'q maiq tu'q),
5.26: ninb cvj zx'q yetg Eau weig Javj myenb zruj txvg Eei sig ziag Eei Bwrnq Yetq ziab txvb puaq. puaq liud, zyrug heug uaq taub msia'q txn hopq naaiq teij uam.
5.25: sai myenb cvj zx'q yem msia'q txn Eei puad weig Rcvb pwav Eei sig fovg hxg Eei Bwrnq, yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen prub Jyenq Zunq kiv fovg hxg liud, zyrug txb mivb Tauj ziab txvb.

9.18: ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq Jauq. yaag ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, ninb Bua Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq. ta'faanb Bwrnj Zxg yem zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub kub vwaaig, ninb Bua Zxg Zxv Jyenq yem uaq Eei.
9.8: mo-se tau, “zuaq mwavj kaaj zyruq xij Navq haiq nx Paaiq meib Bua Eei sig.”
9.3: naaiq nxm Laaj, zyepg feij uaq Nxi, Ba'Nxi Dxtq Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g ziuj tivg taaib Eei Nxib Eia'g ei Jyenq zipq Eei leib Eeig Zauj tiub tiub leib latg Jiaj zipq.”
9.21: maaib teij zyavb hog Bwrnj yem luvb Mwavj Tauj luvb Dxm Navq. luvb Dxm Bwrnj faauj Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Jauq a'q. maiq kunq luvb Nxi fai luvb mwrnd zang, ta'faanb Bwrnj faauj, ninb Bua Zwrtq Jauq a'q.
9.14: “+‘sij kxvq yem meib Bua ka'Euad maaib kanb fivj myenb xij Jiaj zyruq Eei siaj mcvg zipq, ninb xij zu'g ziuj zipq Eei leib Eeig Zauj tiub tiub leib latg zruj. maiq kunq Janj fai pwrnb fivj myenb, xij zu'g maaib Du'g Euvg leid Navq.’+”
9.23: ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, ninb Bua Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq. yaag ziuj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, ninb Bua Zwrtq Jauq. ninb Bua ei Revg zyruq Eei waag ziuj zyruq lovg mo-se Buaj ninb Bua.
9.6: mq paag maaib teij myenb laaij mua'q zu'g Janb taig maaib wij. txij uaq nxm Nxi maiq haib Jiaj siaj mcvg zipq. tovb uaq Nxi ninb Bua taaib Tauj mo-se Zauj aa-lon Bua uaq,
9.2: “Tauj tivg taaib Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Jiaj siaj mcvg zipq.
9.20: maaib zyavb hog Bwrnj yem uaq nxm Dopg liub kub vwaaig i ziaj Nxi Navq. ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag, ninb Bua Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq. yaag ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag, ninb Bua Zwrtq Jauq.
9.7: kxvq Buaj mo-se, “yia Bua laaij mua'q zu'g Janb taig maaib wij, mq paag weig haiq tiug maiq pun yia Bua Tauj tivg taaib Eei zyavb hog tu'q Zauj uaq teij i-saa-laa-en myenb txb ka'naaiq fovg hxg zyruq?”
9.19: Bwrnj haiq zang yem zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub kub vwaaig laub Eei, i-saa-laa-en myenb mwavj zyruq Buaj Eei waag, maiq Zwrtq Jauq a'q.
9.17: Bwrnj haiq zang yem Dopg liub kub vwaaig faauj, i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Zwrtq Jauq. Bwrnj tivb Fiag haaij, i-saa-laa-en myenb cvj Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq yem uaq.
9.11: Tauj Eeig Laaj, zyepg feij uaq Nxi, Ba'Nxi Dxtq Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua xij zu'g Jiaj zipq. xij zu'g Eang Jiaj zipq Eei pa'ki yuvb txn Zauj maiq an pivq Eei Fuaq Zauj im Eei ka'naaib Daav.
9.5: zib Laaj, zyepg feij uaq Nxi, Ryemb yaavb Eei zyavb hog, ninb Bua yem si-naai teib puvb Waav Jiaj zipq. ziuj zyruq Paaiq mo-se, i-saa-laa-en myenb ei Jyenq zruj Revg.
9.16: yaag zanb zang Navq naaiq nx. uaq txq Bwrnj om Jyenq, luvb mwrnd zang pwatg Navq trud.
9.4: mo-se zyrug Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb Jiaj siaj mcvg zipq.
9.10: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘sij kxvq meib Bua haiq taub fai meib Bua Eei funb fa'q laaij mua'q zu'g Janb taig maaib wij, fai maaib myenb Zwrtq Jauq mivb ko Eei txvj, ninb Bua Zxg haib Jiaj zyruq Eei siaj mcvg zipq.
9.22: maiq kunq Bwrnj yem zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub kub vwaaig i Nxi, fai yetg Laaj, fai yetg Havj, ninb Bua Zxg Zxv Jyenq Dopg liub Zyavq yem uaq Eei, maiq Zwrtq Jauq. mq paag Bwrnj haiq zang faauj, ninb Bua zyrug Zwrtq Jauq a'q.
9.12: ninb Bua maiq tuvq lyrub yetg teij Tauj Fav Nxi Dxm. yaag maiq tuvq pun yuvb Eei Buvq nauq yetg tiub. Jiaj siaj mcvg zipq ninb Bua xij zu'g kan Revg tiub tiub leid.
9.15: lyepg Jiad zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub uaq Nxi, se lcvd vcvg waag Eei Dopg liub, maaib txq Bwrnj taaib om Jyenq. luvb maanb Mwavj Tauj luvb Fav pwatg Bwrnj Navq trud nx.
9.13: mq paag sij kxvq maaib myenb Zivb Revg Eei, maiq maaib wij, yaag maiq Zwrtq Jauq mivb ko Eei txvj, yrug maiq Jiaj siaj mcvg zipq nx, uaq taub yem ninb Eei myenb ka'Euad xij zu'g Pai kwavg, weig zu'g tivg taaib Eei zyavb hog ninb maiq txb ka'naaiq fovg hxg zyruq. ninb zruj Eei zwid ninb kanb xij zu'g Daamb txv.
9.1: i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv liud, ta'Eeig Havj zib Laaj, yem si-naai teib puvb Waav, zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se,

16.18: kx'g myenb zyrug txb kx'g myenb Eei huvb lrub, zx'q trud Zauj huv Yetq Jyenq ka'Euad, mivb Zauj mo-se Zauj aa-lon sruq Jyenq wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg.
16.45: “simq Gxi naaiq teij zwavj myenb a'q. Dovg Ryepq tavb mziv yia xij myetg Revg ninb Bua.” ninb Bua i taub zyrug Baapq Fiag Dau.
16.3: ninb Bua kapq zunq taaib yem mo-se Zauj aa-lon Eei Ra'Myen Rcv kxvq, “meib Bua zruj Jiaj Jaaj mig a'q. zwavj pc'g fivj taub taub zuvq Zivb Revg Eei. zyruq yaag Zauj ninb Bua yem. Navq naaig, meib Bua weig haiq tiug Taaib kanb zruj kaub Lo Jiaj zwavj pc'g fivj?”
16.43: mo-se Zauj aa-lon zyrug mivb Tauj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei Ra'Myen.
16.50: wrnb pcvg tivb Revg, aa-lon zyrug Rwrnj wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg, mo-se uaq.
16.14: maiq taan Bua'g naaiq! meib zuvq maiq txb yia Bua pia'g nxm Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv, yaag maiq pun yia Bua tu'q Ripg livb teig Zauj a'vung pyruq Eei Wivj. meib Zxg xij kweij naaiq teij myenb Eei mziv Zwrtq fai? yia Bua za'kevb maiq mivb a'q.”
16.48: ninb sruq Jyenq zyavb Eei Zauj taig mivb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj, tomb wrnb pcvg zyrug tivb mig a'q.
16.34: yem weib kxmj Eei i-saa-laa-en myenb yetg zuvq haid ninb Bua heug zyrug kaanq pyauj, heug Jyenq kxvq, “Riaj Dau xij lyemb yia Bua na'q aaq lo'b!”
16.2: cvj maaib Eig pc'q Mmd zyepg taub, tovb zwavj pc'g fivj kinq taaib, maaib mevb taub Eei pyeiq zeiq.
16.35: cvj maaib trud yem zyruq Zwrtq taaib puaq Qwi Revg txb huv mivb fovg hxg uaq teij Eig pc'q Mmd zyepg taub myenb.
16.24: “Buaj zwavj pc'g fivj simq Gxi Ko-laa, Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam Eei Dopg liub maa'b!”
16.7: Fav Nxi xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen zx'q trud Zauj huv an Jyenq huvb lrub. zyruq kinq haiq taub, tovb uaq taub Zivb Revg. le-wi myenb aa'b! meib Bua zruj Jiaj Jaaj mig a'q.”
16.17: kx'g myenb xij zu'g txb kx'g myenb Eei huvb lrub, cvj zx'q huv Yetq Jyenq ka'Euad fuvj pun zyruq. yetg zuvq maaib Eig pc'q Mmd zyepg nxm huvb lrub. meib Zauj aa-lon yaag xij zu'g txb kanb Eei huvb lrub taaib.”
16.49: zu'g wrnb pcvg taig Eei myenb maaib yetg waang pyei Zin Zyetq pc'q taub, maiq funj laaij Ko-laa Eei Jauq zu'g taig uaq teij.
16.11: Navq naaiq, meib Zauj kan meib Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq taaib Zauj zyruq txib tekg. aa-lon Navq haiq nx meib Bua Zivj vopq ninb?”
16.33: ninb Bua lyemb navb Zauj Jyenq ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq zyrug Dxtq Fiag yemb ken. Dau zyrug kapq Jyenq Dipg, vatq Jyenq ninb Bua. ninb Bua zu'g myetg, maiq tu'q Zauj zwavj myenb yem a'q.
16.16: mo-se Buaj Ko-laa, “Fav Nxi meib Zauj kan meib uaq teij myenb xij zu'g taaib yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen. meib kanb Zauj uaq teij myenb cvj Zauj aa-lon xij zu'g taaib.
16.40: Navq zyruq lovg mo-se Buaj e-le-aa-saa zruj nx. naaiq se weig Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb Javj zu'g, Zwrtq liud aa-lon Eei zeib fun, maiq maaib haiq taub tu'q yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen puaq huv. Riaj haib zu'g Navq Ko-laa Zauj kan Ko-laa uaq teij myenb.
16.37: “xij zu'g Buaj aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, mivb zx'q yem uaq trud ka'Euad uaq teij huvb lrub. cvj txb yem huvb lrub Eei trub Taanj mivb kwavg ko teij Eei txvj weig zu'g naaiq teij huvb lrub Zivb Revg Eei.
16.4: mo-se haid naaiq teij waag ninb Baapq Fiag Dau
16.12: mo-se Paaiq myenb mivb heug e-li-apg Eei txn, Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam taaib. mq paag ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua maiq mivb a'q.
16.46: mo-se kxvq Buaj aa-lon, “zx'q meib Eei huvb lrub taaib, zx'q ziab txvb Eei trud Zauj Jyenq huv tapq Jyenq, kaanq mivb zwavj myenb uaq Tevj ninb Bua fi'q zwid. zyruq nrud haig myenb zyrug pun tomb wrnb pcvg Jiad kxn putq Zwrtq a'q.”
16.13: meib txb yia Bua yem Daub Truq lovj Eei teib puv Zwrtq taaib yem teib puvb Waav taij yia Bua. naaiq Zxg maiq kcvb kauj? meib zuvq xij zruj Lo kunq yia Bua?
16.26: ninb Kwinj zwavj myenb, “simq Gxi naaiq teij myenb waaig myenb Eei Dopg liub. maiq tuvq mua'q ninb Bua Eei haiq Euvg ka'naaiq. Riaj meib Bua laaij ninb Bua Eei zwid zu'g kwaatq mivb.”
16.28: mo-se kxvq, “meib Bua xij Navq naaiq nx hiuq tu'q zyruq Paaiq yia taaib zruj naaiq teij yetg zuvq sig, maiq zeid yia ei kanb Eei Hruq Namq Zwrtq taaib zruj.
16.8: mo-se cvj kxvq Buaj Ko-laa, “meib Bua le-wi myenb mwavj maa'b!
16.9: i-saa-laa-en Eei Tinb huvb kinq meib Bua yem i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib, txb meib Bua taaib nitq fatq ninb, pun meib Bua yem zavg zyruq Eei Dopg liub zruj kov fub suj, yaag yem zwavj pc'g fivj Eei Ra'Myen fub suj ninb Bua. naaiq meib Bua haid se faib fiuq sig fai?
16.32: Dau Gxi Navq mxvj Gxi Rwib, na'q ninb Bua Zauj ninb Bua Eei Jaab tivb, Zauj Ko-laa Eei yetg zuvq myenb, cvj Zauj ninb Bua Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq.
16.21: “meib Bua xij zu'g simq Gxi naaiq teij zwavj myenb. Dovg Ryepq tavb mziv yia zyrug myetg Revg ninb Bua.”
16.6: Ko-laa aa'b! xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx zruj. meib Zauj kan meib Eei myenb xij zu'g txb huvb lrub taaib.
16.20: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
16.5: yaag kxvq Buaj Ko-laa Zauj kan Ko-laa taaib uaq teij, “Fav Dxm zyruq xij piuj mevb haiq taub penj ninb Eei myenb, haiq taub Zivb Revg, yaag xij pun uaq taub taaib nitq fatq ninb. ninb xij kinq haiq taub zyrug pun uaq taub taaib nitq fatq ninb.
16.19: Ko-laa Zauj kan ninb Eei myenb zyrug kapq zunq Zauj mo-se Zauj aa-lon sruq Jyenq Myen txij Myen yem Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg. zyruq Eei Favb laavg zyrug hing Zwrtq pun zwavj pc'g fivj pwatg.
16.38: se tovb paamd zwid zyrug zu'g kwavg mcvg uaq teij myenb Eei huvb lrub. xij zu'g zx'q naaiq teij huvb lrub taaq taaib penj yetg Kwaaiq yetg Kwaaiq pwav Jyenq ziab txvb, weig zu'g naaiq teij huvb lrub fovg hxg Jiaj pun zyruq zyrug Zivb Revg Eei. Navq naaiq se zruj Javb hog pun i-saa-laa-en myenb.”
16.31: mo-se kxvq setq naaiq teij waag, yem aa-Bi-lam Bua Eei zaub Diaq Eei Dau Baaij.
16.27: myenb zyrug simq Gxi Ko-laa, Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam Eei Dopg liub. Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam Zwrtq taaib Zauj aub Jweiq Zauj fu'Jweib faij sruq Jyenq kanb Eei Dopg liub kcvb Daavg.
16.41: ta'Eeig Nxi zwavj pc'g fivj vopq mo-se Zauj aa-lon. ninb Bua kxvq, “meib Bua taij zyruq Eei myenb mig a'q.”
16.1: Ko-laa, Daa-Taan, aa-Bi-lam Zauj on Jiad kxn txib tekg vcvg Jyenq mo-se. Ko-laa se itg-haa Eei txn, itg-haa se Ko-haatq Eei txn, Ko-haatq se le-wi Eei txn. Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam zruj e-li-apg Eei txn, on zruj pe-letg Eei txn. naaiq teij pua taub se lu-Ben fivj.
16.39: e-le-aa-saa sai myenb zyrug zx'q Revg zu'g trud puaq uaq teij myenb txb taaib fovg hxg Eei tovb si'q huvb lrub, yaag pun myenb taaq taaib pwav Jyenq ziab txvb,
16.47: aa-lon zyrug ei mo-se Eei waag zruj, Tiuj pia'g zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj. myenb Jiad kxn zu'g tomb wrnb pcvg, mq paag aa-lon zx'q huv Tevj pc'g fivj fi'q zwid.
16.10: ninb txb meib Zauj meib Eei zwavj kxb yrud, le-wi myenb, taaib nitq fatq ninb. mq paag meib Bua Zxg xij Rcv zruj sai myenb?
16.25: mo-se zyrug mivb Tauj Daa-Taan Zauj aa-Bi-lam uaq. i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei myenb koj yaag kan Jyenq ninb mivb.
16.22: mo-se Zauj aa-lon zyrug Baapq Fiag Dau kxvq, “o Tinb huvb aag, maang myenb Eei livb wrnb Eei Tinb huvb! Du'g taub myenb paamd zwid, meib xij nrud zwavj pc'g fivj fai?”
16.42: zwavj myenb kapq zunq txij mo-se Zauj aa-lon uaq zang, ninb Bua Win mivb wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub uaq. lyemb zeib maaib mrug taaib om Jyenq Dopg liub. zyruq Eei Favb laavg yaag hing Zwrtq taaib.
16.15: mo-se Qiaj Jiad! haig zyrug kxvq Buaj zyruq, “Toq maiq tuvq zipq ninb Bua fovg hxg Eei ka'naaiq. yia zuvq maiq zx'q Jiaj ninb Bua Eei yetg taub lxb. yaag maiq hxig Jiaj ninb Bua Eei haiq taub myenb.”
16.29: sij kxvq naaiq teij myenb taig Navq Prub Tov Eei myenb taig, fai zu'g sig Navq Prub Tov myenb haib zu'g Eei sig nx, se pun Ziv maiq zeid zyruq Paaiq yia taaib.
16.30: mq paag sij kxvq zyruq zruj syavb sig, Dau Gxi, na'q Revg naaiq teij myenb Zauj ninb Bua maaib Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq, pun ninb Bua lyemb navb Dxtq Fiag Tauj yemb ken, meib Bua zyrug hiuq tu'q naaiq teij myenb mavg Piaj zyruq. ”

4.18: “maiq tuvq pun Ko-haatq Eei puvb pwrng myenb yem le-wi myenb ka'Euad zu'g Pai kwavg.
4.45: naaiq se me-laa-li myenb Eei puvb pwrng. mo-se Zauj aa-lon saauq Revg ninb Bua ziuj zyruq lovg mo-se Paaiq Eei waag.
4.3: yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj Eei mJavg txn, tovb haib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub fub suj zruj kov uaq teij.
4.43: yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj, haib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub fub suj, zruj kov Eei yetg zuvq mJavg txn,
4.14: zx'q weig ziab txvb lovg Eei Jaab sig, lyemb syru trud Eei Jei, Eaapq, ka'naaib Zenq, Zauj punb, an ziab txvb kub vwaaig. cvj lovg fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq komq Jyenq, zx'q kcv ziab txvb Eei Dyavj Zunj Jyenq.
4.48: maaib Yetg Zin Mmd pc'q petq zyepg taub.
4.34: mo-se, aa-lon Zauj zwavj myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq saauq Revg Ko-haatq myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng.
4.2: “xij zu'g saauq Revg le-wi myenb pun Fiag Eei Ko-haatq myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng,
4.36: ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng maaib i Zin Zyetq pc'q Mmd zyepg taub.
4.35: yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj, haib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub fub suj, zruj kov Eei yetg zuvq mJavg txn
4.24: “naaiq se ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng xij zu'g zruj kov fub suj yaag xij zu'g pyenb ka'naaiq.
4.7: “xij zu'g zx'q Kwaaiq Diab Buaq timg kevj Tinb huvb Eei Fuaq uaq nxm tiab. cvj zx'q pyenb, pa'ken, Rxmg Zauj Ziaq ziag a'vung tiuq Eei vwaab pcvb an Jyenq. tiab kub vwaaig yaag xij zu'g maaib zanb zang kevj Eei Fuaq.
4.17: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
4.49: ziuj zyruq Buaj mo-se, ninb Bua Paaiq zyavj kx'g myenb Eei kov, kx'g myenb xij zu'g pyenb haiq Euvg. Navq naaiq nx, ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag, mo-se saauq Revg ninb Bua.
4.11: “ninb Bua xij zu'g lovg Kwaaiq Diab Buaq komq Jyenq puaq huv Eei Jyemb tiab, cvj lovg fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq komq Jyenq, zx'q kcv tiab Eei Dyavj Zunj Jyenq.
4.33: naaiq se me-laa-li myenb Eei puvb pwrng xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Dopg liub zruj Eei kov, yaag yem aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, i-Taa-maa, Eei puab Diaq.”
4.16: “aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, e-le-aa-saa, xij zu'g kruj puaq tav Eei yrub Zauj huv, ziag Eei laavb zi'g, Zauj xn myenb Eei Zivb Revg yrub. ninb xij zu'g kruj wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub Zauj yem Dopg liub ka'Euad Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq, se kruj Revg sivj ting Zauj sivj ting Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig.”
4.40: ziuj puvb pwrng Zauj myenb pwrng maaib i Zin lua'g pc'q faab zyepg taub.
4.37: naaiq se Ko-haatq myenb Eei puvb pwrng, se yetg zuvq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub fub suj Eei myenb. mo-se Zauj aa-lon saauq Revg ninb Bua ziuj zyruq lovg mo-se Paaiq Eei waag.
4.4: “naaiq se Ko-haatq myenb xij zu'g yem wig pwavb Dopg liub zruj Eei kov. ninb Bua xij zu'g kruj kaub Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq.
4.12: “ninb Bua xij zu'g zx'q yem sivj ting lovg Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig lovg Diab Buaq peu Jyenq. cvj lovg fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq komq Jyenq an kcv ka'naaiq Eei Jaaj.
4.46: mo-se, aa-lon Zauj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq zyrug ziuj puvb pwrng, ziuj myenb pwrng, saauq Revg le-wi myenb.
4.13: “ninb Bua xij zu'g kwaaib Zwrtq tovb si'q ziab txvb Eei saaiq, cvj lovg Kwaaiq Diab lua'g komq Jyenq ziab txvb.
4.26: weib Dopg liub Zauj ziab txvb Bc'g laatg Zauj Bc'g laatg kcvb Eei Dia, Laav, Zauj yetg zuvq Qyemj lovg Eei Jaab sig. Dxtq zu'g ke-son myenb xij zu'g liug leid naaiq pua'q ka'naaiq.
4.28: naaiq se ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng yem wig pwavb Dopg liub zruj Eei kov. ninb Bua zruj Eei Euvb Euvg se yem aa-lon sai myenb Eei txn, i-Taa-maa, Eei puab Diaq.
4.8: xij zu'g lovg Kwaaiq Diab si'q komq Revg naaiq teij yetg zuvq. cvj lovg Kwaaiq fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq komq kub vwaaig Jiaj yaag zx'q kcv tiab Eei Dyavj Zunj Jyenq.
4.9: “ninb Bua xij zu'g zx'q Kwaaiq Diab Buaq komq Jyenq ziuj Fav Eei tavb Jaaj, tav Eei zaanq, Japq tavb Zoq Eei Fiuq, an Fiuq Eei pyenb, cvj Zauj yetg zuvq tapq yrub weig tinb tav Eei pcvb.
4.32: cvj Zauj weib kxmj Dopg liub Eei laatg tovg Zauj Topq tovg Eei Taapq, Bxv Dau Zxv laatg Dia Eei tovg, Laav, yetg zuvq zruj Qxv Eei ka'naaiq cvj Zauj naaiq pua'q Qyemj lovg Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq Zauj Euvb Euvg Jaab sig. xij zu'g ziuj Buaj Paaiq zyavj haiq taub xij zu'g pyenb Eei haiq Euvg.
4.23: saauq Revg faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj Eei mJavg txn, tovb haib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub fub suj zruj kov Eei yetg zuvq.
4.6: yaag xij zu'g zx'q fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq komq kub vwaaig, cvj lovg Kwaaiq Dia, setq zeiq Buaq Revg, komq kub vwaaig Jiaj. cvj zx'q kcv faav Eei Dyavj Zunj Jyenq.
4.44: ziuj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng maaib pua Zin Eig pc'q taub.
4.20: mq paag Ko-haatq myenb Zinb maang maiq tuvq pia'g mivb mavg naaiq teij Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq, yetg tavb yaag maiq tuvq mavg. maiq zei c'q, xij zu'g taig a'q.”
4.5: xij swiq txvj Eei zyavb hog, aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn xij zu'g pia'g mivb Zc'q Bc'g kcvb Dia Fiag, lovg komq lcvd vcvg waag faav.
4.19: weig pun naaiq teij myenb haib mivb nitq fatq naaiq teij Zivb Revg Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq yaag maiq zu'g taig, maaib mcvg zyavb Jyenq Eei, xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx Tevj ninb Bua. aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua xij zu'g pia'g sivj ting Paaiq zyavj haiq taub xij zu'g zruj haiq Euvg kov, haiq taub xij zu'g kcv haiq Euvg.
4.38: ninb Bua yaag saauq Revg ke-son myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj myenb pwrng.
4.31: ninb Bua yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub xij zu'g fub suj Eei maaib Navq naaiq. xij zu'g pyenb zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub Eei Qxv, kuvb kavg Dyavj, tovg, Zauj Topq tovg Eei Taapq,
4.27: ninb Bua fub suj zruj Eei yetg zuvq kov, maiq kunq kcv Dopg liub Eei ka'naaiq fai zruj haiq Euvg kov, se yem aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua Eei puab Diaq. meib kanb xij zu'g Paaiq zyavj ninb Bua xij zu'g pyenb Eei Euvb Euvg.
4.41: naaiq se ke-son myenb Eei puvb pwrng, se yetg zuvq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub fub suj Eei myenb. mo-se Zauj aa-lon saauq Revg ninb Bua ziuj zyruq Paaiq Eei waag.
4.1: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon,
4.39: yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj, haib yem wig pwavb Dopg liub fub suj, zruj kov Eei yetg zuvq mJavg txn,
4.47: yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj, haib yem wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub zruj kov fub suj yaag Tevj pyenb Dopg liub uaq teij yetg zuvq mJavg txn,
4.10: zx'q tavb Jaaj Zauj tav Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig, lovg fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq peu Jyenq, an kcv ka'naaiq Eei Jaaj kub vwaaig.
4.25: ninb Bua xij pyenb Zxv zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub Eei Dia, se Zxv wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei Dia, tovb komq Eei ka'naaiq Zauj komq kub vwaaig fua'q taaib lovj Eei scvb Kuq Dopq, Zauj pia'g wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei Bc'g kcvb Dia,
4.22: “xij zu'g saauq Revg ke-son myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng.
4.42: ninb Bua yaag saauq Revg me-laa-li myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj myenb pwrng.
4.15: “aa-lon Zauj ninb Eei txn Bua zx'q sivj ting Zauj sivj ting Eei yetg zuvq Jaab sig komq liud, Tauj swiq Dopg liub Zyavq Eei zyavb hog, Ko-haatq myenb xij zu'g taaib kcv. mq paag ninb Bua Zinb maang maiq tuvq mua'q naaiq teij Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq. mua'q nx, xij zu'g taig a'q. se tovb Ko-haatq myenb xij zu'g kcv naaiq teij wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei ka'naaiq.
4.29: “xij zu'g saauq me-laa-li myenb ziuj ninb Bua Eei puvb pwrng Zauj ninb Bua Eei myenb pwrng.
4.30: saauq Revg yem faab zyepg Havj Tauj Mmd zyepg Havj Eei mJavg txn, tovb haib pia'g taaib fub suj, yem wig pwavb Dopg liub zruj kov Eei taub taub.

10.18: Jiaj taaib, yem lu-Ben myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq Eei kwanb kwanb Zwrtq Jauq, yaag yem ninb Bua Eei keb ka'Diaq. maaib se-De-e Eei txn, e-li-su, kunq ninb Bua.
10.8: “se tovb aa-lon Eei txn Bua uaq teij sai myenb xij zu'g pyomq Ratg. naaiq se meib Bua txig Jiaj txig, yetg liud xij zu'g kan Eei leid.
10.33: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Zwrtq zyruq Eei Bov mivb pua Nxi Eei Jauq. uaq teij pua Nxi ka'Euad zyruq Eei lcvd vcvg waag faav mivb Daavg Tevj ninb Bua lxd txvj hitq.
10.3: pyomq i nxm Ratg Eei zyavb hog, zwavj myenb xij zu'g taaib Zauj meib kapq zunq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg.
10.32: sij kxvq meib Zauj yia Bua mivb nx, zyruq Zeij haiq Euvg lovj Eei pun yia Bua, yia Bua yaag pun meib Zauj Jyenq maaib pwrng.”
10.21: Jiaj taaib, Ko-haatq myenb Zwrtq Jauq yaag kcv Jyenq Zivb Revg Eei ka'naaiq mivb. ninb Bua Tauj txvj, zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub zuvq Zxv zyavj a'q.
10.35: kcv lcvd vcvg waag faav Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog, mo-se kxvq, “o zyruq aa'b! Jiad taaib maa'b! Toq pun meib Eei winb wavq faatq Raanj Revg. Toq pun Rxv meib uaq teij myenb yem meib Eei Ra'Myen pyauj Gxi.”
10.14: yem yu-Daa myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq Eei kwanb kwanb Zwrtq Jauq mivb Daavg. ninb Bua yaag yem ninb Bua Eei keb ka'Diaq. maaib am-mi-naa-Dapg Eei txn, naa-son, kunq ninb Bua.
10.23: maaib pe-Daa-su Eei txn, kaa-maa-li-en, kunq maa-natq-sej fivj uaq kwanb.
10.6: haid pyomq ta'Eeig Rung, Zxv Dopg liub yem naamb puv mcvj uaq teij yaag xij zu'g Zwrtq Jauq. pyomq Ratg Eei Qiaj Bwi, pe'q Eei, zyrug zruj Javb hog pun hiuq tu'q xij zu'g Zwrtq Jauq.
10.34: haiq zang Zwrtq Jauq, luvb Nxi zang zyruq Eei Bwrnj yem ninb Bua kub vwaaig.
10.2: “xij zu'g lovg Eaanb taaq i nxm Ratg. pyomq uaq teij i nxm Ratg heug zwavj myenb kapq zunq, yaag pyomq heug swiq Dopg liub Zyavq.
10.36: lcvd vcvg waag faav haiq zang tivb Fiag, mo-se cvj kxvq, “o zyruq aag, Toq meib Rwrnj taaib, Zauj Zinb Zin waanb waang i-saa-laa-en myenb yem.”
10.20: yaag maaib De-u-en Eei txn, e-li-yaa-saapg, kunq kaatg fivj uaq kwanb.
10.24: yaag maaib ki-De-o-ni Eei txn, aa-Bi-Dan, kunq Ben-yaa-min fivj uaq kwanb.
10.28: kwanb kwanb i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq Jauq Eei zyavb hog, xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx ziuj ninb Bua Eei yetg Eeig mivb.
10.7: weig heug zwavj myenb taaib zunq xij zu'g pyomq Ratg, mq paag maiq tuvq pyomq Bwi Eei, pe'q Eei, uaq Euvg Qiaj.
10.29: mo-se Zauj ninb Eei ovb taa, mi-Dyen myenb, le-u-en Eei txn, ho-Bapg, kxvq, “yia Bua xij Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj zyruq kxvq, ‘yia xij Jiu pun meib Bua’ uaq nxm txvj. Toq Zauj yia Bua mivb og. yia Bua zyrug zruj lovj pun meib weig zu'g zyruq lcvd Zeij lovj Eei ka'naaiq pun i-saa-laa-en myenb.”
10.19: suj-li-satq-Dai Eei txn, se-lu-mi-en, kunq si-me-on fivj uaq kwanb.
10.17: Zc'q liud zavg Tinb huvb Eei Dopg liub, ke-son myenb Zauj me-laa-li myenb, tovb pyenb Dopg liub uaq teij, zyrug Zwrtq Jauq.
10.31: mo-se cvj kxvq, “Toq meib maiq tuvq kwavg yia Bua og. meib hiuq tu'q yem naaiq teib puvb Waav yia Bua xij zu'g Zxv Dopg liub Zyavq yem haaij. meib haib Tevj yia Bua zruj mziv.
10.30: ho-Bapg tau, “yia maiq mivb a'q. yia xij Rwrnj yia kanb Eei teib puv, yia kanb Eei myenb uaq.”
10.27: yaag maaib e-nan Eei txn, aa-hi-laa, kunq napq-Taa-li fivj uaq kwanb.
10.11: Tauj ta'Eeig Havj, Eeig Laaj, Eig zyepg uaq Nxi, yem lcvd vcvg waag Eei Dopg liub kub vwaaig uaq txq Bwrnj faauj.
10.5: haid pyomq Ratg Eei Qiaj Bwi, pe'q Eei, Zxv Dopg liub yem tov puv mcvj uaq teij xij zu'g Zwrtq Jauq.
10.9: meib Bua yem kanb Eei teib puv yaag maaib winb wavq taaib hxig zyrug Zwrtq mivb Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj, xij zu'g lovg uaq teij Ratg pyomq Qiaj Bwi Eei, pe'q Eei. zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, zyrug Javj meib Bua, Fruj meib Bua leib Dutq meib Bua Eei winb wavq.
10.16: cvj maaib he-lon Eei txn, e-li-apg, kunq sej-Bu-lun fivj uaq kwanb.
10.4: sij kxvq Kuvj pyomq yetg nxm Ratg Navq, fivb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq xij zu'g taaib zunq meib naaiq.
10.10: cvj Tauj Fyenb yrub Eei zyavb hog, Jiaj meib Bua Eei zipq Zauj syavb Laaj Eei zipq, txb ka'naaiq mivb puaq ziag, yaag ziag weig Jiu Tov uaq zang, xij zu'g pyomq naaiq teij Ratg. naaiq se weig pun meib Bua Eei zyruq Javj zu'g meib Bua. yia zruj zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.”
10.22: Jiaj taaib, cvj maaib yem e-faa-im myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq Eei kwanb kwanb Zwrtq Jauq, yaag yem ninb Bua Eei keb ka'Diaq. maaib am-mi-hutq Eei txn, e-li-saa-maa, kunq ninb Bua.
10.12: i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Zwrtq si-naai teib puvb Waav, Kav Jiaj Kav mivb Tauj Bwrnj tivb Fiag paa-laan teib puvb Waav.
10.15: zu-aa Eei txn, ne-Tan-en, kunq itg-saaj-Kaa fivj uaq kwanb.
10.13: ninb Bua Zwrtq naaiq ta'yetq Rung Jauq ziuj zyruq lovg mo-se Buaj Eei waag.
10.26: maaib o-Kaan Eei txn, paa-ki-en, kunq aa-se fivj uaq kwanb.
10.25: Ga'haaq laai, weig Tevj kwanb kwanb Buvb Jyenq Ga'haaq mcvj, maaib yem Daan myenb Eei Dopg liub Zyavq Eei kwanb kwanb Zwrtq Jauq, yaag yem ninb Bua Eei keb ka'Diaq. maaib am-mi-Qatq-Dai Eei txn, aa-hi-ye-se, kunq.

22.18: mq paag Baa-laa-am tau Baa-laakq Paaiq taaib Eei myenb, “maiq kunq Baa-laakq zx'q Revg pwavq huvb ting Eei Jyem Eaanb pun yia, yia yaag maiq haib zruj Jiaj Daavg zyruq, yia Eei Tinb huvb, Buaj Eei. tomb sig fai fiub sig maiq haib zruj.
22.8: Baa-laa-am Buaj ninb Bua, “meib Bua pweij mwrnd naaiq og. ziuj zyruq Buaj yia, yia zyrug Buaj meib Bua.” uaq teij mo-apg myenb Eei Jyen zyrug hitq Baa-laa-am uaq.
22.33: lxb pwatg yia yaag simq Pyen naaiq teij pua Rung. sij kxvq ninb maiq simq nx, yia zuvq taij meib a'q. mq paag lyrub meib Eei lxb.”
22.3: mo-apg myenb kevb! kamb Riaj haig weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en myenb Zamq! haig. mo-apg myenb kamb Riaj kau i-saa-laa-en myenb, ninb Bua zuvq Hruq waaig Revg.
22.32: zyruq Eei finb myenb naaig ninb, “meib weig haiq tiug Bx'q meib Eei lxb Tauj pua Rung? yia taaib naaiq tavq meib Eei Jauq weig zu'g meib zruj Eei se vcvg Jyenq yia zruj.
22.21: ta'Eeig Dxm, Baa-laa-am Jiad sin taaib, zx'q keb xn pwig Jyenq ninb Eei lxb, kan Jyenq uaq teij mo-apg myenb Eei Jyen mivb.
22.35: zyruq Eei finb myenb kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “kunq Zauj naaiq teij myenb mivb a'q, mq paag Kuvj ei yia Buaj Eei waag kxvq Navq.” Baa-laa-am zyrug kan Jyenq Baa-laakq Paaiq taaib uaq teij Jyen mivb mig a'q.
22.40: Baa-laakq taij vovb Zauj pa'ki yuvb ziag yaag zx'q teij xq pun Baa-laa-am Zauj kan Jyenq mivb uaq teij Jyen.
22.14: uaq teij mo-apg myenb Eei Jyen zyrug Rwrnj Baa-laakq uaq kxvq, “Baa-laa-am maiq Kavq Zauj yia Bua taaib.”
22.23: lxb pwatg zyruq Eei finb myenb sruq Jyenq uaq Jauq nanq Jyenq Ru'g Daauq. lxb zyrug simq Zwrtq Jaub Len pia'g Deig mivb. Baa-laa-am zyrug Bx'q lxb, aapq lxb cvj faauj uaq Jauq.
22.6: Toq meib ib zang taaib Tevj yia zyruj ninb Bua, weig zu'g ninb Bua kevb! kaub henq yia. Navq naaig, Riaj yia haib Bx'q hivb ninb Bua, zung ninb Bua Zwrtq teib puv mq pei. weig zu'g yia hiuq tu'q meib pwav waag haiq taub, uaq taub zyrug tu'q fu'q. meib zyruj haiq taub, uaq taub zu'g zyruj a'q.”
22.34: Baa-laa-am kxvq Buaj zyruq Eei finb myenb, “yia paamd zwid a'q. yia maiq hiuq tu'q meib yem uaq Jauq tavq Jyenq yia. sij kxvq meib maiq a'Neiq yia mivb nx, yia zyrug Rwrnj a'q.”
22.2: mo-apg teib puv Eei huvb, sipg-po Eei txn, Baa-laakq, pwatg i-saa-laa-en myenb zruj pun aa-mo-lai myenb Eei yetg zuvq sig.
22.36: Baa-laakq haid kxvq Baa-laa-am taaib, ninb zyrug mivb Tauj mo-apg teib puv Eei kapg Jaaij kaub ko Jiaj Eei yetg nxm zivb, aan-non Daaib Len uaq zipq.
22.20: uaq mwrnd Tinb huvb taaib kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “weig zu'g naaiq teij myenb taaib lxd meib, meib kunq Zauj ninb Bua mivb a'q. mq paag Kuvj ziuj yia Buaj Eei waag zruj Navq.”
22.24: zyruq Eei finb myenb cvj mivb sruq Jyenq i nxm a'vung Wivj Bu'Dovj, Jauq hepg Eei txvj. i puv Jaub Len yaag maaib la'pyeib laatg.
22.28: zyruq pun lxb haib kxvq waag Buaj Baa-laa-am, “yia zruj haiq Euvg pun meib, meib Zivj taaib Bx'q yia naaiq teij pua Rung?”
22.7: mo-apg Zauj mi-Dyen myenb Eei myenb koj zyrug Zwrtq Jauq cvj txb Jyenq Zivq zyruj Eei Eaanb mivb. Tauj Baa-laa-am uaq, ninb Bua zyav Baa-laakq Eei waag Buaj ninb.
22.29: Baa-laa-am tau lxb, “meib zruj pun yia paaig Myen. sij kxvq yia Eei puad nanq Jyenq Ru'g Daauq nx, yia ib zang zuvq taij meib a'q.”
22.19: ib zang Toq meib Bua yem mwrnd naaiq Navq zinb Daavg uaq teij nx, weig pun yia hiuq tu'q zyruq cvj xij Jaa Buaj haiq Euvg yia.”
22.17: yia xij pun meib tu'q tomb zivb Eeig. meib xij yia zruj haiq Euvg yia yaag ei Jyenq zruj. Toq! taaib Tevj yia zyruj naaiq teij myenb.’+”
22.38: Baa-laa-am tau, “ib zang yia se Tauj meib naaiq a'q. mq paag yia fuvg haib la'kwaib kxvq haiq Euvg? Tinb huvb Navq haiq nx Buaj yia, yia Kuvj haib Navq uaq nx kxvq Navq.”
22.31: uaq zang zyruq pun Baa-laa-am Eei mziv haib mavg tu'q pwatg zyruq Eei finb myenb nanq Jyenq Ru'g Daauq sruq Jyenq uaq Jauq. Baa-laa-am zyrug Baapq Fiag Dau.
22.30: lxb cvj kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “yia maiq zeid meib kanb Eei lxb, tovb meib yetg seij keb Tauj ib zang fai? yia Navq naaiq nx zruj Jiaj pun meib Eei fai?” Baa-laa-am kxvq, “maiq zruj Jiaj.”
22.27: lxb pwatg zyruq Eei finb myenb ninb zyrug Baapq Fiag. Baa-laa-am Zxg keb Jyenq Eei. Baa-laa-am Qiaj Jiad! haig, lovg pyaab Byaag Bx'q.
22.11: ‘maaib fivj myenb yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib yem pwavq luvb Diaq Eei Daub peib. ib zang Toq meib taaib zyruj ninb Bua. Navq naaig Riaj yia haib Zauj ninb Bua Bx'q Jaaj cvj zung ninb Bua pyauj nxb.’+”
22.5: ninb zyrug Paaiq myenb mivb Buaj Be-o Eei txn, Baa-laa-am, taaib. Baa-laa-am yem ninb Eei pwrnb kua'q, nitq fatq yu-fe-titg Daaib, pe-To uaq. Baa-laakq kxvq, “maaib yetg fivj myenb yem i-yipq teib puv Zwrtq taaib yem pwavq luvb Diaq Eei Daub peib. ib zang ninb Bua zuvq taaib yem Jyenq yia Eei txib vaang.
22.9: Tinb huvb taaib Tauj Baa-laa-am uaq naaig kaaj ninb, “Zauj meib yem naaiq teij myenb se haiq taub?”
22.16: ninb Bua mivb Tauj Baa-laa-am uaq kxvq, “sipg-po Eei txn, Baa-laakq, Navq naaiq nx kxvq. ‘Toq maiq tuvq pun haiq Euvg laanb Jyenq pun meib maiq tu'q Tauj yia naaiq.
22.41: ta'Eeig Dxm, Baa-laakq txb Baa-laa-am faauj Tauj Baa-motq Baa-an. yem naaig ninb mavg tu'q pwatg teij i-saa-laa-en myenb.
22.37: Baa-laakq kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “yia Paaiq myenb mivb heug meib kaanq taaib, meib zruj haiq Euvg maiq taaib? meib laaig yia maiq pun zivb Eeig kauj fai?”
22.39: Baa-laa-am zyrug Zauj Jyenq Baa-laakq mivb Ki-li-yaatq-hu-sotq zivb.
22.4: mo-apg myenb zyrug Buaj mi-Dyen myenb Eei myenb koj, “naaiq kwanb Dovg naaig Zamq Eei myenb xij na'q Biag Revg Wiv Rwrnj Eei yetg zuvq ka'naaiq, Navq vovb kruq Laij Fav Revg Zyavq Eei miaq nx.” uaq zang sipg-po Eei txn, Baa-laakq, zruj mo-apg myenb Eei huvb.
22.10: Baa-laa-am tau Tinb huvb, “mo-apg teib puv Eei huvb, sipg-po Eei txn, Baa-laakq, Paaiq myenb taaib Buaj yia,
22.22: mq paag Tinb huvb Qiaj Jiad haig weig zu'g Baa-laa-am mivb. zyruq Eei finb myenb zyrug taaib sruq Jyenq Jauq tavq Jyenq ninb. uaq zang Baa-laa-am keb Jyenq lxb, cvj maaib i taub pru kan ninb mivb.
22.12: Tinb huvb kxvq Buaj Baa-laa-am, “maiq tuvq Zauj naaiq teij myenb mivb, yaag maiq tuvq zyruj i-saa-laa-en myenb, weig zu'g yia Zeij fu'q pun ninb Bua mig a'q.”
22.15: Baa-laakq cvj Paaiq teij zruj Lo Eei myenb mivb, kaub Zamq yaag maaib mevb taub kaub Lo zinb Daavg uaq teij.
22.13: ta'Eeig Dxm, Baa-laa-am Jiad sin taaib Buaj yem Baa-laakq taaib uaq teij zruj Lo Eei myenb, “meib Bua Rwrnj meib Bua kanb Eei teib puv a'q, weig zu'g zyruq maiq pun yia Zauj meib Bua mivb.”
22.1: Ga'haaq i-saa-laa-en myenb Zwrtq Jauq mivb Tauj mo-apg Eei Daub pcvb, Jx-Dcn Daaib tov puv, ye-li-Ko zivb txib vaang.
22.26: zyruq Eei finb myenb cvj Jiaj mivb sruq Jyenq kaub hepg Jiaj Eei yetg nxm txvj. zaaij mcvj, Byaaug mcvj, maiq maaib txvj mivb a'q.
22.25: lxb pwatg zyruq Eei finb myenb zyrug Bevj Jyenq laatg Jiaj, Faapg zu'g Baa-laa-am Eei zauj. Baa-laa-am zyrug cvj Bx'q ninb Eei lxb.

12.3: mo-se Eyemg kanb zruj faij. peiq luvb Diaq zwavj myenb, maiq maaib haiq taub Dovg ninb Eyemg kanb zruj faij.
12.8: yia Zauj ninb Myen txij Myen kxvq waag, yaag kxvq mevb Eei, maiq kxvq waab meiq. lyemb yia Eei mru zeiq ninb yaag tu'q pwatg. uaq Euvg meib Bua weig haiq tiug maiq kamb Riaj taanb yia Eei pru, mo-se?”
12.9: zyruq Qiaj Jiad! haig ninb Bua, zyav naaig leib Gxi ninb Bua mig a'q.
12.7: mq paag yia Eei pru, mo-se, maiq zeid Navq naaiq nx. yem yia Eei zwavj pc'g fivj ninb zyepg zua'q Eei.
12.5: zyruq zyrug yem Bwrnb Dyrub Fiag taaib sruq Jyenq wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg heug aa-lon Zauj mi-lyem. ninb Bua i taub zyrug Zwrtq taaib.
12.16: Ga'haaq zwavj myenb Zwrtq haa-se-lotq mivb yem paa-laan teib puvb Waav lyepg Zyavq.
12.14: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “sij kxvq ninb Eei tia Twiq uamb Rwib nctq ninb Eei Myen, ninb zuvq xij zu'g tiaq Eaiq siag Nxi maiq zeid? pun ninb zu'g yem ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq pwavq siag Nxi. Ga'haaq cvj txb ninb pia'g taaib tu'q Eei.”
12.4: zyruq lyemb zeib kxvq Buaj mo-se Zauj aa-lon Zauj mi-lyem, “meib Bua pua taub Zwrtq mivb Tauj wig pwavb Eei Dopg liub uaq.” ninb Bua pua taub zyrug mivb a'q.
12.2: ninb Bua i taub kxvq, “zyruq Kuvj lovg mo-se trug ninb Eei waag Navq fai? ninb maiq zeid lovg yia Bua trug?” zyruq yaag haid mig a'q.
12.6: zyruq kxvq, “mwavj yia Eei waag maa'b! sij kxvq yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj maaib taub trug waag myenb, yia, zyruq, yem hing yaavb Eei sig hing Zwrtq pun ninb pwatg yia. yia lovg Beij Zauj ninb kxvq waag.
12.13: mo-se zyrug Qa'q Toq zyruq, “o Tinb huvb aag, Toq zxg ninb og.”
12.12: maiq tuvq pun mi-lyem Navq kub vwaad yem ka'sia taig mivb, yuvd Zwrtq taaib xq yu'g yetg pwrng uaq nx.”
12.15: mi-lyem zyrug zu'g yem ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq pwavq siag Nxi. zwavj myenb yaag maiq swiq mivb haaij, zuaq Tauj txb ninb cvj pia'g taaib.
12.11: zyrug kxvq Buaj mo-se, “yia Eei zyruq, mo-se aa'b! Toq maiq tuvq tivg yia Bua zruj Vovj Eei sig, paamd Eei zwid.
12.1: mo-se lovg Kutq myenb sia'q zruj auq. laaij ninb lovg naaiq taub Kutq myenb zruj auq, mi-lyem Zauj aa-lon taanb mo-se.
12.10: Bwrnj yem Dopg liub faauj uaq zang, pwatg mi-lyem sruq Jyenq uaq putq komb huq pcvg. Dopq Bopq pc'g Eei, Navq sxv nx. aa-lon Win mavg mi-lyem, pwatg ninb putq komb huq pcvg,

15.18: “xij zu'g kxvq Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘meib Bua pia'g tovb yia xij txb meib Bua pia'g uaq nxm teib puv,
15.8: “+‘meib Bua liug leid taub vovb kruq weig puaq ziag fai weig kanb Euvg Jauq ziag, se weig zruj suv lcvd Eei vcvg waag fai ziag pun zyruq weig Jiu Tov.
15.33: pwatg ninb uaq teij myenb zyrug txb ninb mivb Tauj mo-se Zauj aa-lon Zauj zwavj pc'g fivj uaq.
15.3: haiq zang txb vovb, yuvb, pa'ki yuvb taaib fovg hxg lovg trud puaq ziag, maiq kunq se puaq ziag Eei, fai ziag zruj suv lcvd vcvg waag Eei Jauq, fai weig Zwrtq fim ziag Eei, fai Jiaj zipq hxpg zu'g ziag Eei, naaiq se zruj Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
15.32: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem teib puvb Waav uaq zang, pwatg laanb myenb txij tivb kov Nxi mivb kc'q zaavb.
15.21: txig Jiaj txig meib Bua xij zu'g Navq naaiq zx'q mxg taaib Eei syavb laavb zi'g fovg hxg pun zyruq.
15.35: zyruq kxvq Buaj mo-se, “naaiq laanb myenb zuvq xij zu'g taig. zwavj pc'g fivj xij zu'g txb ninb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq, zx'q la'pyeiq zov taig ninb.”
15.40: Navq naaig, meib Bua zyrug Javj Jyenq, ei Revg yia Eei tiub tiub leib latg yaag penj Revg meib Bua Eei zyruq Eei myenb.
15.14: txig Jiaj txig, sij kxvq maaib Janj fai kanb fivj myenb yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj, ninb Bua yaag xij txb ka'naaiq taaib lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq, ninb Bua xij zu'g zruj Navq meib Bua zruj uaq nx.
15.23: tovb zyruq lovg mo-se Jiu pun meib Bua Eei haiq tiub leid, yem zyruq pun taaib uaq Nxi Tauj Ga'haaq hivq txig Jiaj txig,
15.6: “+‘txb yetg taub pa'ki yuvb kruq, xij zu'g liug leid pyei mx'q pyenj Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq yetg kxvg levb ka'lanq yrub weig zruj ziag Eei laavb zi'g.
15.34: ninb Bua wrnj Jyenq weig zu'g myenb maiq kcvb hiuq Ziv xij zu'g Navq haiq nx zruj pun ninb.
15.2: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘meib Bua tu'q pia'g yia xij pun meib Bua yem uaq nxm teib puv, xij zu'g ziuj naaiq teij leid zruj.
15.36: zwavj pc'g fivj zyrug txb ninb Zwrtq ka'Eiag zi'g Dopg liub Zyavq, zx'q la'pyeiq zov taig ninb, Navq zyruq Buaj mo-se uaq nx.
15.20: meib Bua mxg taaub Rung syavb laavb zi'g, xij zu'g zruj nxm Fuaq txb taaib fovg hxg pun zyruq weig zruj fovg hxg Eei laavb zi'g yem Bx'q Byaub Zyavq zx'q Zwrtq taaib.
15.24: yaag sij kxvq zwavj pc'g fivj Za'g prug zruj txvg, zwavj myenb yaag maiq hiuq, zwavj pc'g fivj xij zu'g lovg taub vovb kruq txn puaq ziag, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq. yaag xij zu'g ziuj leib latg txb ziag Eei laavb zi'g Zauj Ziaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq yetg Fiag ziag. cvj lovg taub yuvb kruq ziag fi'q zwid.
15.28: sai myenb xij zu'g yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen weig Za'g prug zruj txvg uaq laanb myenb fi'q zwid. fi'q liud, uaq laanb myenb Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg liud a'q.
15.7: yaag lovg yetg kxvg levb a'vung tiuq Zauj Jyenq Ziaq ziag, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
15.29: maiq kunq pwrnb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb fai Janj, xij zu'g Jwavg naaiq Du'g Euvg leid lovg Navq.
15.19: Eang uaq nxm teib puv Eei laavb zi'g, meib Bua xij zu'g zx'q teij fovg hxg pun zyruq.
15.38: “xij zu'g Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb, ‘yem naaiq mivb, txig Jiaj txig xij zu'g zruj Givb Gru tivj Jyenq nxmb nxm lwib kx'q. nxmb nxm Givb Gru yaag xij zu'g lovg tiub Laav, setq pc'g Buaq, pavg lwi tivj Jyenq.
15.31: laaij ninb mavg Piaj zyruq Eei waag, paamd zyruq Eei livg, ninb Dovg haaij zuvq zu'g Pai kwavg. ninb kanb Eei zwid ninb kanb xij zu'g Daamb txv.’+”
15.30: “+‘mq paag haiq taub paab paag paamd zwid, maiq kunq pwrnb fivj myenb fai Janj, uaq taub Ki zyruq zyrug yem ninb Eei myenb Bu'Dovj zuvq zu'g Pai kwavg.
15.27: “+‘sij kxvq Kuvj maaib Du'g taub myenb Za'g prug zruj txvg, ninb xij zu'g txb taub txij Havj Eei yuvb zeig taaib ziag weig fi'q zwid.
15.11: ziag vovb kruq, pa'ki yuvb kruq, pa'ki yuvb txn, yuvb txn, mrud taub xij zu'g Navq naaiq nx liug leid.
15.5: txb mrud taub yuvb txn, pa'ki yuvb txn taaib puaq ziag fai weig kanb Euvg Jauq ziag, xij zu'g weig yetg taub yuvb liug leid yetg kxvg a'vung tiuq Zauj Jyenq Ziaq ziag.
15.9: xij zu'g lovg Ju'q mx'q pyenj Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq i kxvg ka'lanq yrub zruj ziag Eei laavb zi'g Zauj Jyenq uaq taub vovb kruq txb taaib.
15.16: meib Bua Zauj yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei Janj xij zu'g Jwavg Euvg leib latg, Jwavg Euvg leid lovg.’+”
15.41: yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb, tovb txb meib Bua Zwrtq i-yipq teib puv weig zruj meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb. yia se zyruq, meib Bua Eei Tinb huvb.’+”
15.39: meib Bua zyrug maaib naaiq teij Givb Gru mavg weig pun meib Bua Javj Jyenq zyruq pun meib Bua Eei tiub tiub leib latg zyrug ei Jyenq zruj. maiq ei kanb Eei Hruq xij Zauj mziv pwatg zyrug txb meib Bua mivb txvg Jauq.
15.4: txb scvb Kuq taaib Eei myenb, xij zu'g txb i mx'q Bwrnb mwrng zxpg Jyenq yetg kxvg ka'lanq yrub zruj ziag Eei laavb zi'g.
15.10: yaag xij zu'g txb i kxvg a'vung tiuq zruj Ziaq ziag Eei ka'naaiq. xij zu'g lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
15.22: “+‘sij kxvq meib Bua Za'g prug zruj txvg, maiq ei Jyenq zyruq Jiu pun mo-se Eei tiub tiub leid,
15.12: ziuj meib Bua liug leid taaib Eei sruj mrug, mrud taub xij zu'g Navq naaiq liug leid.
15.15: i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj xij zu'g weig kanb yaag weig yem meib Bua Bu'Dovj Eei Janj Jwavg naaiq teij leid lovg. naaiq teij leid xij zu'g txig Jiaj txig yetg liud Ripg. yem zyruq Eei Ra'Myen meib Bua Zauj Janj zyrug fib Navq.
15.13: “+‘mrud taub pwrnb fivj i-saa-laa-en myenb txb ka'naaiq taaib lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg Eei zyavb hog xij zu'g Navq naaiq zruj, weib Daav Eei Qiaj hxpg zyruq Eei Hruq.
15.26: Navq naaig i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj Zauj yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj Eei Janj Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg mig a'q, weig zu'g zwavj myenb Za'g prug zruj txvg.
15.25: sai myenb xij zu'g Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei zwavj pc'g fivj fi'q zwid, pc'g fivj Eei zwid zyrug tu'q kwavg liud, weig zu'g ninb Bua Za'g prug zruj txvg. ninb Bua yaag weig kanb zruj txvg Eei sig txb ka'naaiq lovg trud puaq ziag fovg hxg pun zyruq yaag ziag fi'q zwid.

13.18: zaab mavg kaaj, uaq nxm teib puv Navq haiq nx. mavg kaaj, yem naaig Eei myenb henq fai maiq henq, Zamq fai zo'g.
13.8: e-faa-im fivj nun Eei txn, ho-se-yaa
13.33: yem naaig yia Bua tu'q pwatg ne-fin myenb. (aa-naakq myenb se ne-fin myenb Eei zeib fun.) mavg Bua kanb nx, se lomb Jopg Eeig Navq. ei ninb Bua Eei mziv mavg Bua, taaij pwatg Bua lomb Jopg Eeig fib Navq Eei.”
13.3: mo-se ziuj zyruq Eei waag Paaiq ninb Bua Zwrtq paa-laan teib puvb Waav. ninb Bua yetg zuvq zruj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
13.32: ninb Bua zyrug kxvq to'g ninb Bua zaab liud uaq nxm teib puv Eei Jaub lrug, pun naaiq teij waag siv pwavq i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb. ninb Bua kxvq, “yia Bua zaab uaq nxm teib puv haib Eang myenb Eei. yem naaig Eei zwavj myenb yaag Lo haig, Lav haig.
13.21: uaq teij myenb zyrug yavb pa'q puv mcvj, yem sin teib puvb Waav naamb puv, zaab Truj Tauj le-hopg, nitq pia'g haa-matq zivb uaq tiub Jauq.
13.14: napq-Taa-li fivj wopq-sij Eei txn, naa-Bi
13.23: Tauj etg-Ko hxvd, ninb Bua Va'q tiub a'vung Mei Eei Gwaab, maaib yetg Jxib pyruq. i taub myenb lovg Dyavj Zunj Jyenq Daam. ninb Bua cvj kc'q teij zi'g lyrub pyruq Zauj vovb Exj pyruq txb Rwrnj.
13.6: yu-Daa fivj ye-fun-ne Eei txn, Kaa-lepq
13.2: “Paaiq teij myenb mivb zaab Kaa-naa-an teib puv, tovb yia xij Zeij pun i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei teib puv. ziuj ovb Taaij lyepg taaib Eei fivj, xij zu'g yetg fivj Paaiq taub uaq fivj Eei pyeiq zeiq.”
13.20: mavg kaaj, uaq teij Dau Navq haiq nx? Jaig fai Jung? maaib Dyavj fai maiq maaib? yaag xij zu'g zruj taamq Lo Eei, txb teij uaq nxm teib puv Eei pyruq Rwrnj.” (uaq zang txij zu'g taaub Txvj a'vung pyruq zua'g.)
13.24: uaq nxm txvj ninb Bua Zwrtq Buaj heug etg-Ko, weig zu'g i-saa-laa-en myenb yem naaig Va'q uaq Jxib a'vung pyruq.
13.28: mq paag yem naaig Eei myenb henq haig. ninb Bua Eei zivb Lo haig, maaib zivb laatg weib Jyenq. yem naaig yia Bua zuvq tu'q pwatg aa-naakq Eei zeib fun.
13.7: itg-saaj-Kaa fivj yo-sepq Eei txn, i-kaan

25.7: aa-lon sai myenb Eei fun, e-le-aa-saa Eei txn, fi-ne-hatg, pwatg, ninb zyrug yem zwavj myenb Bu'Dovj Zwrtq taaib, nanq tiub Zav
25.5: mo-se zyrug Buaj i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei syemq zwid Jyen, “ta'faanb meib Bua Eei haiq taub myenb zavg yem pe-o Eei Baa-an zyenb, meib Bua mrud taub xij zu'g zx'q ninb Bua taij Revg.”
25.17: “xij zu'g zruj pun mi-Dyen myenb penj winb wavq a'q, yaag taij ninb Bua,
25.14: Zauj mi-Dyen sia'q zu'g taij uaq taub i-saa-laa-en myenb Eei Buaj heug simj-li, se saaj-lu Eei txn. saaj-lu se si-me-on fivj Eei yetg puvb myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
25.4: zyruq Buaj mo-se, “zx'q naaiq teij myenb Eei zwavj pyeiq zeiq luvb Nxi zang, Fav Eei zyavb hog, yem Gcvg Eei txvj txv Jyenq zyruq Eei Ra'Myen taij, weig pun zyruq maiq Qiaj Jiad, nrud haig i-saa-laa-en myenb.”
25.2: ziag ninb Bua Eei zyenb Eei zyavb hog, naaiq teij msia'q txn yua'g i-saa-laa-en myenb Zauj Jyenq mivb. i-saa-laa-en myenb zyrug Eang ziag Jiaj Eei ka'naaiq, yaag kweig Fiag paaij uaq teij zyenb.
25.6: i-saa-laa-en Eei zwavj myenb kapq zunq yem wig pwavb Dopg liub Eei kcvb Daavg Eyemq uaq zang, maaib taub i-saa-laa-en myenb txv Jyenq mo-se Zauj zwavj myenb txb taub mi-Dyen sia'q taaib pia'g ninb Eei Dopg liub.
25.13: se lcvd pun ninb Zauj ninb Eei zeib fun yetg liud tu'q zruj sai myenb weig zu'g ninb Tevj ninb Eei Tinb huvb Rcv i-saa-laa-en myenb yaag Tevj i-saa-laa-en myenb fi'q zwid.”
25.12: xij zu'g Buaj ninb, yia Zauj ninb lyepg Jiad pcvb xn Eei vcvg waag,
25.15: zu'g taij uaq taub mi-Dyen sia'q heug Kotq-Bi. ninb Eei tia heug suj-aa, se yetg puvb mi-Dyen myenb Eei pyeiq zeiq.
25.11: “aa-lon sai myenb Eei fun, e-le-aa-saa Eei txn, fi-ne-hatg, pun yia maiq Qiaj Jiad i-saa-laa-en myenb weig zu'g ninb Tevj yia Rcv ninb Bua, Navq yia yem ninb Bua Bu'Dovj Rcv ninb Bua uaq nx. yia zyrug maiq myetg ninb Bua.
25.1: i-saa-laa-en myenb yem sitq-Tim teig uaq zang, maaib teij pc'g fivj Jiad kxn Yenj mo-apg myenb Eei sia'q.
